   </text:sequence-decls>
   <text:p text:style-name="P2">b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingifwa fasthet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">mod, uppmuntra:</text:span></text:span> animum pignore, Vg.; Agrippam inermum centurio quamvis f-tus animo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(modig)</text:span> ægre confecit; Drusum; milites sibi et proelio f-at <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tillit till sig och mod till drabbningen),</text:span> T.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med dom l. bewis, ord) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stadfästa; bekräfta; bestyrka; försäkra:</text:span></text:span> lex populi judicia f-vit, C.; da, pater, augurium, et hæc omina f-a; dictis foedera, Vg.; libero <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(då det war lemnadt fritt),</text:span> quid f-ret (senatus) mutaretve, T.; vetus opinio et gentium f-ta consensu; tabulis aliquid, C.; Charicles Tiberium non ultra biduum duraturum f-vit, T.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(militäriskt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Befästa, gifwa styrka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">trygghet, förswara:</text:span></text:span> aciem subsidiis, L.; turrem præsidiis, Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Firmāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fäste:</text:span></text:span> radix trunci, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Firmāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fäste, grundfäste, stöd:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> tigna, quæ f-o esse possint, Cs. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> equester ordo ceterorum f.; f. ejus constantiæ, quam in amico quærimus, fides est; falsitas parum f-i habet, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hufwudbewis:</text:span></text:span> id illi f. disciplinæ esse putant, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">techn. rhet.:</text:span> f. est firmissima argumentationis pars, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Firmātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Befästare, stadfästare:</text:span></text:span> disciplinæ militaris, Pn.; missus Drusus - paci f-or, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Affirmo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stärka, befästa:</text:span></text:span> animo alqm, Catl.; ea res Trojanis spem finiendi erroris a-vit; fidem suam apud alqm a., L. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bekräfta, -styrka, -sanna:</text:span></text:span> quæramus aliquid, quo a-etur nostra descriptio; aliquid rationibus a-re, C.; aliquid jurejurando; ea nec a-re nec refellere in animo est; opinionem, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med säkerhet yttra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">påstå, försäkra, bejaka, bedyra:</text:span></text:span> nihil possum a., præter opinionem meam; non soleo a-re temere de altero; a-o tibi nullam consolationem esse talem, C.; quis rem tam veterem pro certo a-et?, L.; me a-o nullos scribere versus, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Affirmanter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bestämdt:</text:span></text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Affirmāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med bekräftelse:</text:span></text:span> quod a. promiseris, (præstandum est), C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Affirmatio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Försäkran, bedyrande:</text:span></text:span> jusjurandum est a. religiosa, C.; multa a-e abnuere. Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumfirmo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rundtomkring </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Befästa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">stödja:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confirmĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frimodighet, oblyghet:</text:span></text:span> Pt. Mil. gl. 193 (inc. l.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confirmo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Befästa, stadga, stärka, gifwa styrka åt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> dentes, Pn.; hoc ali vires, c-ri nervos putant, Cs.; valetudo, corpus c-tum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(efter sjukdom);</text:span> se c-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(få krafter, tillfriskna),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> manum suam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(här);</text:span> non est institutis opinio (deos esse) c-ta, non legibus; amor c-atur beneficio accepto et studio perspecto; in his amicitia c-ri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(komma till stadga)</text:span> potest; spem; amicitiæ corroboratis c-tisque et ingeniis et ætatibus judicandæ sunt; postquam diuturnitas pacis otium c-vit, C.; magis prohibendo a <text:soft-page-break/>peccatis, quam vindicando exercitum brevi c-vit, Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingifwa mod, uppmuntra;</text:span></text:span> se c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fatta mod:</text:span> nunc erige te et c-a, si qua dimicatio subeunda erit; animos hominum c. et excitare, C.; milites, Cs.; territos; eos c-at, ut Romam pergerent, Sa.; c-to animo in causa consistere, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lagligen) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stadfästa, bekräfta:</text:span></text:span> aliquid populi suffragiis; acta Cæsaris, C.; pacem et amicitiam cum proximis civitatibus, Cs.; societatem, Sa.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med bewis </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bestyrka, gifwa styrka åt, besanna:</text:span></text:span> id hoc argumento c-ri potest, quod -; hanc opinionem Pherecydes maxime c-vit; id, quod intendimus, c-re, C.; hac opinione c-ta, Cs. <text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Försäkra, bedyra:</text:span></text:span> tum ille fidenter c-re, rem ita se habere; Lentulus iis (c-vit), se esse illum -; talis amicus, ut c-re possum, nemo fuit, C.; c-re, fidem publicam per sese inviolatam fore, Sa.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confirmātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stadgad; modig; wiß:</text:span></text:span> ætas, C.; exercitus c-ior, Cs.; in literis tuis idem illud erat c-ius, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confirmāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med stadga:</text:span></text:span> fluctuat (oratio) nec potest c. se expedire, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confirmātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Befästande, stärkande:</text:span></text:span> libertatis, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppmuntran:</text:span></text:span> c-e non egebat virtus tua, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bestyrkande, bewis</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för sanningen af ngt, mots.</text:span> infirmatio, refutatio): res indiget c-is; c. est, per quam argumentando nostræ causæ fidem adjungit oratio, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Försäkran:</text:span></text:span> perfugæ, Cs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confirmātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som gifwer säkerhet för ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Borgensman:</text:span></text:span> res parum firma videbatur: c. pecuniæ desiderabatur, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infirmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swag:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kroppsligen (mechaniskt l. physiskt):</text:span> telum, Ct.; arbor, Pn.; homo viribus i-is; valetudo i-sima, C.; corpus, Ov.; sapor, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om själens förmögenheter:</text:span> memoria, Qu. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i fråga om krigisk styrka):</text:span> classis i-a propter dimissionem remigum; hac legione tradita pro rep. i-or sum, C.; civitas, Cs. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till giltighet l. bewisningskraft:</text:span> vestræ cautiones i-æ sunt; res ad probandum, C. <text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till mod, tänkesätt:</text:span> terrentur i-ores, Cs.; ego sum paulo i-or (ɔ: superstitiosus), Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infirme</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swagt, klenmodigt:</text:span></text:span> animatus i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(modlös),</text:span> C.; i-ius tonitrua expavescebat, Sa.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infirmĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swaghet:</text:span></text:span> corporis, valetudinis; i. puerorum, ferocitas juvenum, gravitas constantis ætatis, senum maturitas, C.; vini, Col.; animi i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(klenmodighet),</text:span> C.; i-em Gallorum veritus, quod sunt mobiles in consiliis capiendis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sål. ostadighet),</text:span> Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infirmo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förswaga, göra kraftlös, betaga ngt deß kraft:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> legiones commeatibus, T.; unam legem tollendo ceteras i-atis, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt: om handlingar, wittnesmål och bewis: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förklara ogiltig, beröfwa ngt deß kraft</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">giltighet, wederlägga:</text:span></text:span> testamenta i. et convellere; fidem testis; ea dico, quæ tu i-re non possis; aliquid i. et diluere, C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infirmātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upphäfwande, wederläggning:</text:span></text:span> rerum judicatarum; rationis, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Pĕrinfirmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ganska swag, obetydlig:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Offirmo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">göra fast l. styf, enwis; absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Enwisas:</text:span></text:span> corium cineris inspersu, Ap.; animum, Pt.; se, Ter.; quid agimus, si pater o-bit contra nos?, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Offirmātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ståndaktig, hårdnackad:</text:span></text:span> perferam o-o animo, Pt.; in iracundia o-or, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Offirmāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fiscus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Korg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (flätad):</text:span> f-is premere oleum, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Penningekorg, -cassa:</text:span></text:span> f-i complures cum pecunia a senatore ad equitem Romanum translati, C.; f-i de imperatore rapti inter aquilas et signa vehebantur, T. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">deraf: <text:line-break/>3. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cassa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spec.</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Offentlig cassa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som ställes till en tjenstemans förfogande:</text:span> quos (numos) mihi senatus decrevit et ex ærario dedit, ego in cistam transferam de f-o, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kejserliga cassan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i mots. till</text:span> ærarium i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">statens cassa l. bank):</text:span> eadem severitate f-um, qua ærarium cohibere, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fiscālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till (kejserl.)</text:span> fiscus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hörande:</text:span> calumniæ, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fiscĭna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Korg:</text:span></text:span> texere, Vg.; ficorum, C.; in f-a uvas premere; f-æ oleariæ, Col.; frondaria, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fiscella</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten korg:</text:span> f. cum sale, Cato. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">nos-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">munkorg:</text:span></text:span> boves f-as habere, ne herbam sectentur, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confisco</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Incassera,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hafwa i cassa:</text:span> eam summam Augustus c-tam semper habuerat, Su.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indraga till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T4">fiscus,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">confiskera:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> förklara ngn egendom förlustig:</text:span> hereditates; principes Græciæ ob leve calumniarum genus, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confiscātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: regis, Fl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fiss . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Findo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fistūca,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klubba, slägga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (golf- l. gatuläggares), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">jungfru:</text:span></text:span> pavire f-is, Pn.; adigere palos, tigna f-is, Cs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fistūco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Neddrifwa, -slå, jemna:</text:span></text:span> fundamenta, Cato; solum, Vitr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fistūcātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fistŭla,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rör:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i kroppar:</text:span> duæ f-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(luft- och matstrupe);</text:span> aurium; calami, Pn.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skrifpennans rör,</text:span> Ps.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om mechaniska ting:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wattenledningsrör:</text:span></text:span> in tectum aqua venit per f-am, Varr.; templo aquam suppeditare f-is, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blåsinstrument, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pipa, flöjt:</text:span></text:span> eburneola; pastoritia, C.; custodes ovium dicunt carmina f-ā, Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fistel:</text:span></text:span> per lumbos f-æ puris eruperunt, N. <text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Handqwarn:</text:span></text:span> ferraria, Cato. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fistŭlātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rörformigt:</text:span></text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fistŭlātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flöjtblåsare:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fistŭlātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: tabulæ, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">försedd med rör,</text:span> Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fistŭlōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pipig, porös:</text:span></text:span> caseus, terra, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fistelartad:</text:span></text:span> cancer, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fitilla (Sen.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fritilla.<text:line-break/>Fixus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Figo. <text:line-break/>Flab . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Flo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flaccus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slapp, slokig;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> serskildt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">med slokiga, nedhängande öron:</text:span></text:span> aures, Varr., C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>laccus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. cognomen, berömdt genom skalden</text:span> Q. Horatius Fl. † 746 a. U. C.: si quid in F-o viri est, Hor. Epod. XV. 12.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flacceo</text:span>, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara slak, swag; wara modlös:</text:span></text:span> lorum, Luc.; oratio, Lucil.; Messala, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flaccesco</text:span>, ccui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Inch.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wißna; slappas, mattas:</text:span></text:span> feniculum, Col.; oratio, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flaccĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slokig; wißnad; swag:</text:span></text:span> aures, Col.; folium, Pn.; turbo, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conflaccesco</text:span>, 3.: fluctus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sjunka tillsammans, lägga sig),</text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Flagell . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Flagrum.<text:line-break/>Flagitatio, -tator <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Flagito.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flāgĭtium,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: skamlig, neslig, skändlig gerning (mots.</text:span> facinus = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wåldsgerning) l. ord:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om osedlighet i enskilda lifwet, isynnerhet i fråga om otukt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Last, styggelse, orenlighet, skändlighet, slemhet:</text:span></text:span> f. facere; f-is infamem fieri, Ter.; f-is et stupris se contaminare; propter libidinem tanta f-a facit et dicit; f-is se inquinare; in f-is versari, volutari; f. suscipere; nihil f-i est, C.; f-i initium est inter cives nudari corpora, Enn. ap. C.; f-is et facinoribus coopertus, Sa.; minus esset, si f-is tantum effeminati essent, a facinoribus manus abstinuissent, L.; Germani - corpore infames cæno mergunt, tanquam scelera ostendi oporteat, dum puniuntur, f-a abscondi; numerum liberorum finire f. habetur, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i det offentliga lifwet, isynnerhet om feghet l. trolöshet i krig: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nesligt dåd, skambragd,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (skandal):</text:span> magnum dedecus et f., hostem non virtute, sed scelere superatum; f. Pompeji (Italiam relinquentis); non ego metum ex re militari, non poenam f-i dico tolli oportere; rei militaris f-um admittere, C.; Lentulus illa f-a militiæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppror och eftergifwenhet för de upproriskes fordringar)</text:span> aspernabatur, T. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om fel af dumhet l. tanklöshet (hyperboliskt): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skamlighet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (skandal):</text:span> ista f-a Leucippi (ex atomis omnia efficientis); f-a concipere animo; non sensit, quantum commisisset f-i (qui oblivisceretur, quid paulo ante posuisset), C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skam, nesa:</text:span></text:span> factum plenum f-i, C.; f. fatendi timoris, L.; pejus leto f-um timet, Hor.; cum f-o redire, N.; disseruit cum pudore et f-o, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flāgĭtiōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Full af styggelse; groft lastbar; liderlig; slem:</text:span></text:span> vita; homo f-simus et nequissimus; verba, libidines, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skandalös; neslig:</text:span></text:span> bonorum emptio f.; f. possessio, C.; socordia, Sa.; fama; periculosa severitas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mot de upproriske),</text:span> f-sa largitio, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flāgĭtiōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lastbart; på ohederligt, skandalöst sätt, skamligen; med skam</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">nesa:</text:span></text:span> vivere impure et f., C.; patres judicia male et f. tuentur; f. obire legationes; f. dicta; f-sime discedere a judicio, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perflāgĭtiōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Groft liderlig:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flāgĭto,</text:span> 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kräfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (skuldenär); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">uppfordra till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt; owilkorligt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fordra, begära, pocka på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T4">aliquem aliquid</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ngn på ngt);</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">aliquid ab aliquo</text:span>): clamore magno, Pt.; metuo, ne te f-ent, ego imperavi, ut rogarent; admonitum venio, non f-atum; Tulliola munusculum tuum f-at; hæc sunt, quæ me ludens Crassus f-bat; f-batur quotidie, ut causam susciperet; mercedem f. ab aliquo; postulo atque etiam f-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(att få höra)</text:span> crimen; a te tua promissa per literas f-t; quia tempus postulat, non f-at, præteribo; postulatur a te vel f-atur potius historia, C., miles stipendium; Cæsar Gallos frumentum, Cs.; foris telum, N.; largiora f-o amicum; f-at refici, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ifrigt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fråga:</text:span></text:span> quæ sint ea numina divom, Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stämma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> inför rätt:</text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flāgĭtātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kräfwande, kraf; bön:</text:span></text:span> æris alieni, C.; civitatum, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flāgĭtātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kräfware, -ande; som pockar på ngt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> f-em suum flagitare, Pt.; f. non molestus, sed assiduus, C.; pugnæ f. miles, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Efflāgĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utkräfwa; enständigt fordra, pocka på, begära:</text:span></text:span> epistolam convicio; potestatem tribuniciam populus; misericordiam; a Dolabella, ut mitteret, C.; ensem, Vg.; signum pugnæ, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Efflāgĭtātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/>(<text:span text:style-name="T2">Efflāgĭtātus</text:span>), <text:span text:style-name="T4">abl.</text:span> -tu: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pockande, uppfordran, fordran:</text:span></text:span> insulsa e.; e. ad aliquid faciendum; coactu et e-u meo, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕflāgĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kräfwa, fordra åter:</text:span></text:span> Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Flagrans, Flagrant . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Flagro. <text:line-break/>Flagritriba <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Flagrum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flăgro,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Låga, stå i låga; brinna:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> flamma, Lucr.; f-ntes onerarias, quas incenderant milites, videbatis, C.; fæx vini, Pn.; crinemque flăgrantem, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om lysande föremål:</text:span> flāgrantesque dei vultus, Vg.; lumina, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personers begär o. d.:</text:span> alicujus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till ngn)</text:span> amore, odio; f. studio dicendi; cupiditate; desiderio urbis, C.; cupidine currūs, Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Älska:</text:span></text:span> aliquam, Ppt.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">låga, brinna = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppröras, hwimla, storma:</text:span></text:span> non vidit f-ntem bello Italiam; f-bat domus cupiditate et studio hominum; multitudo f-ns in contionibus, C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>e. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara utsatt för:</text:span></text:span> infamiā, invidiā, C., T.<text:line-break/>f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sätta i brand</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (oeg.):</text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flăgrans</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. och oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Brinnande, het, glödande; ifrig, häftig:</text:span></text:span> æstus f-simus, C.; sol, Pn.; genæ, Vg.; aliquem f-simum (studio) accipere, C.; gratia, T.; tumultus, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flăgranter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ifrigt, häftigt:</text:span></text:span> specie recusantis f-sime concupierat, T.; f-ius exardescere, Amm. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flăgrantia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Brand; glöd:</text:span></text:span> Aetnæ, Gell.; oculorum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conflăgro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Brinna upp, uppgå i lågor:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> sidera si mota loco sint, c-re terras necesse sit; classis incendio, C.; castra flammis, L. - <text:span text:style-name="T4">part. pass. depon.</text:span>: urbs incendio c-ta, C. (Her.).<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: (förtäras):</text:span> incendio invidiæ, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conflăgrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Brand:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēflăgro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intrans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Brinna ned, af; förbrinna:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> ædes manu tua; templum Dianæ; Phaĕthon ictu fulminis, C.; igni d-at res, Lucr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swalna, lägga sig, lugna sig:</text:span></text:span> sic deflāgrare minaces, Luc.; iræ, L.; seditio, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">För-, uppbränna:</text:span></text:span> sol aliquid, Vitr.; fana d-ta, Enn. ap. C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> cinis imperii d-ti, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēflăgrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Brand, förbränning:</text:span></text:span> minari urbi d-em; mundi d., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flăgrum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Piska, gissel:</text:span></text:span> f-is pinsere, Pt.; cædere, L.; f-a pati, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flăgellum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Piska, gissel:</text:span></text:span> f-is ad mortem cædi, secari; dignum horribili f-o - scuticā sectari, Hor.; inusta f-a conscribillant nates, Catl.; insonuit f-o, Vg.; boum, Col.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> mens sibi conscia facti - torret f-is alqm, Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ungskott, toppskott:</text:span></text:span> pete summa f-a, Vg. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tjenande såsom </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kastrem:</text:span></text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flăgello</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gißla, piska;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">slå:</text:span></text:span> quæstorem, Su.; messem perticis, Pn.; comæ colla f-ant, Mt.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> annonam f-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppdrifwa, stegra),</text:span> Pn.; puteal multa vibice (= pejerantem tangere), Ps.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flăgrĭtrĭba</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: (τρίβω): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som sliter gissel, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gisselslitare:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. Flamen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Flo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Flāmen,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prest</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för enskild gudomlighet, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T4">flamen:</text:span></text:span> quod - caput cinctum habebant filo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> filum), flamines dicti <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enl. Mommsen beslägt. med</text:span> flag-ro, flam-ma = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(offer)tändare, offerprest; jfr Curtius, Griech. Etym.</text:span> 177): horum singuli cognomina habent ab eo deo, quoi sacra faciunt -, ut Martialis, Volcanalis, Dialis (Jovis fl.), Varr.; Numa f-em Jovi assiduum sacerdotem creavit, insignique eum veste et curuli regia sella adornavit. Huic duos f-es adjecit: Marti unum, alterum Quirino, L.; f-em prodere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utnämna),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flāmĭnĭca</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Flaminia, Prisc.), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flamens hustru:</text:span> T., Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flāmĭnius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till f. hörande:</text:span> ædes, Fs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flāmĭnia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: Flaminis Dialis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">boning:</text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flāmĭnium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flamens embete:</text:span> C., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>lāmĭnīnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. cognomen i</text:span> gens Quintia, C. de Sen. I. 1; N. Hann.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>lāmĭnius, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">Subst.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn;</text:span> circus Fl. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på</text:span> Campus Martius). <text:line-break/>Flāmĭniānus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. Flaminius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Flamen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flamma,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> flag-ro, φλέγω?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Låga, eld:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> f-am concipere, Catl.; excitare, Ct.; opprimere, C.; f-ā exanimari, Cs.<text:span text:style-name="T4">;</text:span> prius undis f. (coëat), ut ait poēta, quam -, C.; f-as <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eldsignaler)</text:span> regia puppis extulerat, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om glans såsom af eld:</text:span> stant lumina f-ā, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om lågande håg l. begär:</text:span> omnis illa vis et quasi oratoris f. exstinguitur, C.; memoriā rerum gestarum eam f-am (qua ad virtutem accenduntur) egregiis viris in pectore crescere, Sa.; f. amoris turpissimi, C.; digne puer meliore f-ā, Hor.; ultrix f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hämndens låga),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lågan af krig, fara, lidande:</text:span> belli; judicii; in invidiæ f-a esse, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flammesco</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Inch.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">börja låga l. glöda:</text:span> caelum, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flammeus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är af eld, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Eldig, lågande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> stellæ sunt naturā f-æ, C.; halitus, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">full af eld, lif:</text:span> versus, Varr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Eldfärgad, brandgul:</text:span></text:span> viola, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flammeum</text:span> <text:line-break/>(flameum), i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Eldfärgad slöja,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som bars af Flaminica och brudar:</text:span> Catl., Mt., Juv.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flammeārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förfärdigare af</text:span> flammea: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flammeŏlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som stöter i eldrödt:</text:span></text:span> Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flammeŏlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> flammeum: Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flammĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lågande, eldig:</text:span></text:span> Ap. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flammĭfer</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flammĭger</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Eldbringande, brännande:</text:span></text:span> currus Solis f-fer, Ov.; Titan f-ger, Luc.; vis (pestis) f-fera, poēt. ap. C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flammĭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Låga, uppkasta eld:</text:span></text:span> Aetna, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flammo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intrans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">part. præs. act.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Låga:</text:span></text:span> lumina, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tända; sätta i låga, brand:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> igni f-ta cremantur, Lucr.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Eldfärga:</text:span></text:span> toga f-ta, Mt. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Elda, sätta i brand:</text:span></text:span> milites literæ, T.; f-to corde, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flammŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liten låga:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēflammo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Släcka:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Inflammo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sätta i låga, sätta eld</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tända:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> tædas ignibus Aetnæ; classem, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om hetta, brand i kroppen,</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upptända, elda, upphetta;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">part. pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">brinnande, lågande:</text:span></text:span> (auditores) delectabat magis, quam i-bat; motus animi vel i. vel exstinguere; i-vit me studio (scribendi); i. invidiam; corporis facibus i-ri ad cupiditates; i-ri ad gloriam; i-ri spe, libidine, amore, furore; i. alqm in aliquem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mot);</text:span> morem omnem Lacedæmoniorum i-tum esse cupiditate vincendi; classis Sertorianis ducibus i-to studio ad Italiam rapiebatur, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Inflammanter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På ett upptändande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">upprörande sätt:</text:span></text:span> Gell. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Inflammātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inwärtes </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hetsighet, brand, inflammation:</text:span></text:span> ulcerum, Pn.; stomachi, Ce. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Antändning, låga:</text:span></text:span> poētam bonum - sine i-e animorum - neminem exsistere, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Flatura, Flatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Flo.<text:line-break/>Flaveo, -vesco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Flavus.<text:line-break/>Flavialis, -anus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Flavius. <text:line-break/>Flavicomus, -vidus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Flavus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>lāvius, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn, berömdt genom de tre kejsarne af detta namn,</text:span> T. Vespasianus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och hans söner.</text:span> Flāviālis, Flāviānus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flāvus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gul</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som guld), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">blond:</text:span></text:span> mel, Lucr.; aurum; crines; arva; Ceres, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flāveo</text:span>, ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wara, stå gul, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">blond:</text:span></text:span> maturis f-bit messis aristis, Col.; culta f-entia; f-tes arenæ, comæ, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flāvesco</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Inch.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gulna:</text:span></text:span> f-et campus aristis, Vg.; folium fagi celerrime f-it, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flāvĭcŏmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: (coma): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gullhårig:</text:span></text:span> Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flāvĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gulaktig:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sufflāvus</text:span> (sub-fl.), <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">någo</text:span>t <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blond:</text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Flebilis, -biliter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fleo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flecto,</text:span> flexi, flexum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böja; wända:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böja, kröka:</text:span></text:span> membra, C.; arcus; ulmum in burim; salignas crates <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fläta),</text:span> Vg.; ramum; æris cornua f-xi; partes corporis, quas sedendo f-imus; f-xus in anguem; f-xum mare, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wända, styra</text:span></text:span> [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">åt ett (annat) håll</text:span>]:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: currum de foro in Capitolium; viam, C.; iter, N., L.; huc f-e oculos; equos, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T4">reflexivt</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i pass. och i act.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">intrans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wända, wrida, wika af:</text:span></text:span> se sinistrorsus, Cs.; Euphrates ad meridiem f-itur, Pn.; miluus in gyrum f-itur, Ov.; ex Gabino in Tusculanos flexere colles, L.; ad <text:soft-page-break/>Sallustianos hortos f-unt, T.<text:line-break/>c. flectere locum = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kringsegla:</text:span></text:span> promontorium, T. <text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om tid:</text:span> f-xo in vesperam die, T. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med personliga och sakliga object:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böja, beweka, omstämma, förändra:</text:span></text:span> oratione alqm; animos teneros; natura subito fingi flective non potest; dii fata f-unt; judicium suum adversus alqm, C.; animum suum, Sa.; Jupiter omnipotens, precibus si f-eris ullis, Vg.; juvenis cereus in vitium f-ti, Hor. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wända, rigta, locka, tubba</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngt:</text:span> Gaditani ab omni studio Poenorum ad nostrum imperium mentes f-runt; animum alicujus ad voluntatem suam; animos inficiunt et f-unt, quo volunt, C.; animum scribentis a vero, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ord; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">härleda:</text:span></text:span> verba; e Græco f-xum, Qu.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwergå till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> in ambitionem; ad sapientiam, T. - <text:span text:style-name="T4">part. pf.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flexus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. motus f-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wridna, wrickande)</text:span> fractique, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om toner: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drillande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som slår öfwer till annan tonhöjd):</text:span> C. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om stafwelser: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Circumflecterad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som har en höjning och en sänkning):</text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flexănĭmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hjertebewekande:</text:span></text:span> oratio, Pac. ap. C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I hjertat bewekt:</text:span></text:span> id.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flexĭbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böjlig, lättböjd:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> materia, C.; arcus, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> oratio ita f., ut sequatur, quocunque torqueas; ad bonitatem; ætas f.; ingenium devium et f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ostadigt),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flexĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böjlig, böjd:</text:span></text:span> cornu; comæ, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flexĭlŏquus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: (loquor): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slingrande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i tal, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">twetydig:</text:span></text:span> oracula f. et obscura, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flexio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böjning, wridning:</text:span></text:span> virilis laterum, C.<text:line-break/>2. vocis f. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drillning:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Krokwäg, omswep:</text:span></text:span> diverticula et f-es quærere, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flexĭpes</text:span>, pĕdis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: (pes): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slingrande:</text:span></text:span> hedera, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flexo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böja:</text:span></text:span> Cato.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flexūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böjning, krökning:</text:span></text:span> laterum, Lucr.; vicorum, Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> virtus recta est: non recipit f-am, Sen.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ords </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böjning:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flexus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böjning, krökning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af kropp l. wäg), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wridning, swängning:</text:span></text:span> aurium; - ubi f. est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(der man wiker af)</text:span> ad iter Arpinas, C.; anguis, Ov.; metæ f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kring målet),</text:span> Ps.; suffraginum, Pn.; modicus f. (Rheni), T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böjning, wexling,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> variation af ton:</text:span> citharoedi; mille f. et artes desiderantur, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wändning, wändpunkt, öfwergångspunkt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">-tillstånd:</text:span></text:span> in f-u <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. blott</text:span> f-u ætatis (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid öfwergången från ungdomen till mannaåldren l. från mannaåldren till ålderdomen);</text:span> f. rerum publicarum, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gramm. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böjningsform:</text:span></text:span> Varr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flexuōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Full af böjningar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">krökningar; slingrande:</text:span></text:span> iter auditus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hörselns),</text:span> C.; vitis, Cato; mons; orbis intestinorum f-simus, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flexuōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slingrande:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Afflecto</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böja, åt, till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> Avien.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumflecto</text:span>, xi, xum, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böja, styra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> omkring:</text:span> longos cursus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kring Sicilien),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Circumflectera:</text:span></text:span> pænultimam, Gell. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumflexe</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med circumflecteradt uttal:</text:span></text:span> ponere syllabam, Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumflexus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Krökning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hwalf):</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conflexus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hopböjd:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēflecto</text:span>, xi, xum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böja, wända, leda ned, af, bort,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt annat håll:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: amnes in alium cursum d-xi, C.; tela, Vg.; ramum olivæ, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intrans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wika af:</text:span></text:span> de via, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bortleda, -locka, förwrida, -wandla:</text:span></text:span> sententiam alicujus a proposito; alqm de curriculo petitionis; ad verba rem, C.; virtutes in vitia; ab institutis studiis, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intrans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afwika, förirra sig:</text:span></text:span> de via consuetudo; oratio ab amicitiis perfectorum ad leves a.; a patris virtute; a veritate, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēflexio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēflexus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedböjning; afwikande; öfwergång:</text:span></text:span> palmes frangitur d-u, Col.; solis certa d-io, Mcb.; ab odio ad gratiam d-us, Val. Max.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Indēflexus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ej nedböjd; oförändrad:</text:span></text:span> maturitas senectutis, Pn.; cursus, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Inflecto</text:span>, xi, xum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (inåt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kröka, wända:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> ex alto ad urbem sinus i-itur; oculos ad se, C.; ferrum se, Cs.; capita, Catl.; cervix; aratrum i-xum, Vg.; radices in nodum, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> magnitudinem animi ne i-as cujusquam injuriā; jus civile neque i-i gratiā neque perfringi potentiā potest; rex se ad injustum dominatum i-xit; Demetrius primus i-xit orationem (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfwergaf den enkla, naturliga stilen,</text:span> naturale, rectum orationis genus), C.; primus hic i-xit sensus animumque labantem impulit, Vg. - <text:span text:style-name="T4">part. pf.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Inflexus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Krokig:</text:span></text:span> bacillum, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lockig:</text:span></text:span> capillus, Su.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om toner: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böjd, drillande, darrande:</text:span></text:span> sonus, vox; i-a voce miserabilem videri, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Inflexĭbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oböjlig:</text:span></text:span> dolor i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lamhet);</text:span> obstinatio; torvitas, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Inflexio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böjning, wridning:</text:span></text:span> laterum, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Inflexus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Krökning; böjning:</text:span></text:span> vicorum, Juv.; vocis, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Offlecto</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böja, wrida emot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> navem, Pt. (Rud. 1013).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕflecto</text:span>, xi, xum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böja, kröka bakåt, tillbaka:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> colla r., Vg.; caput, Catl.; caudam, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åter wända, leda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">beweka, lugna igen:</text:span></text:span> animum ad alqm, C., Vg.; mentes aut incitare aut r., C.; eum misericordia non r-xit, Ter.; in melius orsa, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intrans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wika, draga sig tillbaka:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕflexio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕflexus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillbakaböjning, krökning; omställning:</text:span></text:span> r-io cervicis, Mcb.; r-us Oceani; r-io sententiarum, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕtrōflecto</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böja, kasta tillbaka:</text:span></text:span> capillos, Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flēmĭna,</text:span> num, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bölder:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fleo,</text:span> flēvi, flētum, 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intrans.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gråta, begråta, gråta öfwer, för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> fletur, Ter.; ad tumulum alicujus f.; lapides f. et lamentari coēgisset, C.; flentes ad pedes projectæ sunt, Cs.; mortuos; vicem suam, Ct.; ultro flens compellare videbar; fleti Dardanidæ, Vg.; flebit et tota cantabitur urbe; quid fles, Asterie, quem tibi candidi primo restituent vere Favonii?; parentes Troilum; si vis me flere, dolendum primum ipsi tibi, Hor.; flenda fortuna, Ov.; fletus = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förgråten,</text:span> Ap. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> ploro).<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drypa:</text:span></text:span> omnia flent ubertim guttis, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flēbĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wärd att gråta öfwer, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Beklaganswärd, sorglig, ömklig, rörande:</text:span></text:span> gemitus; o f-es vigilias, o miseram et f-em speciem, C.; sponsa; Ino, Hor.; cantus, Pn. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wärd att begråtas:</text:span></text:span> multis ille bonis f. occidit, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flēbĭlĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ömkligt, sorgligt, rörande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sentimentalt):</text:span> canere, respondere, C.; gemere, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flētus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gråt, tårar:</text:span></text:span> nemo me lacrumis decoret nec funera f-u faxit, Enn. ap. C.; f-um movere; assiduus; cum f-u legere aliquid, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Affleo</text:span>, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gråta wid</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">mot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> Pt.; ut ridentibus arrident, ita flentibus afflent vultus humani, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēfleo</text:span>, ēvi, ētum, 2.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gråta ut; begråta:</text:span></text:span> in sinu amici, Pn.; casus reipublicæ; mors a multis d-ta, C. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om</text:span> Tusc. I. 87 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Seyffert).</text:span><text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förgråta:</text:span></text:span> oculos suos, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Indēflētus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Obegråten:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Difflētus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förgråten:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effleo</text:span>, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gråta ut; förgråta:</text:span></text:span> oculos, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Inflētus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Obegråten:</text:span></text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Fletus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fleo.<text:line-break/>Flex . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Flecto. <text:line-break/>Flictus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fligo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flīgo,</text:span> ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slå, stöta:</text:span></text:span> æquora ad saxa naves virosque, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flictus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanslagning,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">stötning:</text:span></text:span> galearum, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Afflīgo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(adfligo), ixi, ictum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slå, stöta, drifwa mot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt; absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kullslå, nedslå; drifwa på grund:</text:span></text:span> alqm ad terram, Pt.; statuam; ad scopulos navem; quum reflavit fortuna, a-imur, C.; arbores, naves, Cs.; equi et viri a-cti, Sa.; in undas naves Archimedes, L.; laceratum objicit et a-it in unda; terræ (<text:span text:style-name="T4">dat.</text:span>) alqm, Ov.; caput saxo, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(factiskt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedslå, kullslå; förlama; bringa på obestånd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fall; fälla, störta, krossa, förstöra, förderfwa:</text:span></text:span> non me plane enervavit aut a-xit senectus; virtus nostra nos a-xit; adolescentiam alicujus; calamitas alqm; equestrem ordinem; alqm in judicio, judicum sententiis a.; susceptam causam, C.; Asia mores nostros, Pn.; fames hostes, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till modet </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedslå, krossa, bedröfwa:</text:span></text:span> me discessus tuus; ægritudines animum, C.; desiderio alicujus a-gi, Ct. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedsätta:</text:span></text:span> vituperando, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Afflictus</text:span>, -tior, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slagen, krossad, förstörd, nödställd; modfälld, nedslagen, bedröfwad, förtwiflad:</text:span></text:span> salus; fortuna; condicio a-ior; virtus prostrata et a.; reipublicæ a-æ opem ferre; provincia a-a et perdita; animus a. et fractus; omnes mæstos et a-os vidi, C.; res Romana; urbs pestilentiā a-a, L.; res suas a-as videre, Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Afflictio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bedröfwelse:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Afflicto</text:span> <text:line-break/>(adflicto), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Frequ.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ideligen l. wåldsamt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wräka:</text:span></text:span> tempestas naves, Cs.<text:line-break/>2. se a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slå sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för bröstet såsom tecken till sorg; deraf i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jemra, klaga:</text:span></text:span> cur me non a-em?; de aliqua re acerbissime a., C.; mulieres a. sese, manus supplices tendere, Sa.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hårdt ansätta, plåga;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lida, wåndas, wara i betryck:</text:span></text:span> sævis fluctibus sum a-ta multum, Pt.; graviter æger, respublica a-atur, C.; hostem vulneribus, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Afflictātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Anfäktelse, wånda:</text:span></text:span> a. est ægritudo cum vexatione corporis, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Afflictor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som nedslår, förstör:</text:span></text:span> dignitatis (senatus), C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Afflictrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som stöter emot -:</text:span> nubes a. ignem dat, Ap. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Afflictus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stötande emot:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conflīgo</text:span>, ixi, ictum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intrans.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stöta ihop:</text:span></text:span> venti adversi, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i strid) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammandrabba; inlåta sig, deltaga i träffning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">drabbning;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwerhufwud: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">strida, kämpa:</text:span></text:span> temere in acie versari et manu cum hoste c.; armis; pro salute reipublicæ contra <text:soft-page-break/>conspirationem; copia c-it cum egestate, mens sana cum amentia; causæ inter se, C.; acie, L.; classe, navibus, N.; acriter; proelio; cum aliquo, Cs., Sa.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slå, stöta tillsammans, mot hwarandra:</text:span></text:span> semina obvia, Lucr.<text:line-break/>b. cum scripto factum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(motsätta, jemföra),</text:span> C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conflictio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanstöt, -stötning; strid:</text:span></text:span> corporum, Qu.; causarum, rerum contrariarum, dissimilium, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conflicto</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intrans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kämpa, dragas med:</text:span></text:span> cum malo, Ter.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slå, wara en plåga för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> per plura scelera rempublicam Macro c-averat, T. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: conflictari aliqua re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> cum aliqua re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> aliquo: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ansättas, plågas, lida af; kämpa, dragas med, hafwa att kämpa med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt l. ngn:</text:span> molestiis; judiciis turpibus; cum aliquo, C.; cum ejusmodi ingeniis, Ter.; magnā inopiā, Cs.; multis æmulis, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conflictātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanstötning, trängsel; drabbning:</text:span></text:span> Qu., Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conflictus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanstötning; tillstötande:</text:span></text:span> nubium; lapidum c-u et tritu elicere ignem, C.; incommodi c., Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Efflīgo</text:span>, ixi, ictum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slå ihjäl, döda:</text:span></text:span> Pompejum, C.; canes rabidos, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Efflicte</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Efflictim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dödligt:</text:span></text:span> amare, diligere alqm, Pt., Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Efflicto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Frequ.</text:span> = effligo, Pt</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Inflīgo</text:span>, ixi, ictum, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slå, drifwa in på, emot:</text:span></text:span> puppim vadis, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slunga emot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">slå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn ett slag (tillskynda):</text:span> crimen in adversarium; mortiferam plagam, vulnus reipublicæ; turpitudinem alicui, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōflictus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kullslagen, -stjelpt:</text:span></text:span> res p-æ et perditæ, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōflīgo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slå, nedgöra, slå på flykten</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en här:</text:span> copias, aciem hostium, Cs.; Mauros, Sa.; numerum decemplicem, N. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedslå, krossa, störta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i förderfwet:</text:span> rem publicam consiliis; mærore afflictus et p-tus, C.; opes Lacedæmoniorum ab tenui initio p-tæ, N.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nära fullända, bringa nära sitt afgörande:</text:span></text:span> bellum p-tum ac pæne sublatum; quæstio jam p-ta, C.; ætas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(långt framskriden),</text:span> Sen.; bellum Judaicum p-verat, reliquā oppugnatione Hierosolymorum, T.; templa, Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōflīgātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Olycklig, förstörd, förfallen:</text:span></text:span> homo p-simus; senatus judicia, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōflīgātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: bonorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förstörande),</text:span> Aus.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōflīgātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slösare:</text:span></text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flo,</text:span> flāvi, flātum, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåsa, fläkta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intrans.</text:span>: ventus lenissimus nobis, C.; ventus, Cs.; aura secunda velis; tibia flat, Ov. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåsa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> bort, ut, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utandas:</text:span></text:span> pulverem ventus, Cs. (Ht.); anima, quæ flatur, hieme apparet, Varr.; - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> magna f. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tala i hög stil,</text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om instrument:</text:span> tibia flatur, Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(metaller) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smälta, mynta:</text:span></text:span> pecuniam, C.; æs flatum, Varr.; lapidem Phrygium, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som blåses, andas = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Luftig, af luft:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flābra</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fläktar, ilar:</text:span></text:span> venti inhorrescunt lenibus f-is, Vg.; Boreæ, Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flābellum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hwift, pust</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (solfjäder):</text:span> Ter.; movere ventum f-o, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Retelsemedel:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flābellĭfĕra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(slafwinna) som bär solfjäder:</text:span> Pt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flābellŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liten solfjäder:</text:span></text:span> Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flāmen</text:span>, mĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fläkt, wind, pust:</text:span></text:span> Aquilonis f-a pulsant Persea (sidus), C. poēt.; ferunt sua f-a classem, Vg.; Boreas f-e tundit fores; classi contraria f-a, Ov.; cur cessant f-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(toner)</text:span> tibiæ?, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flātūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smältning, gjutning:</text:span></text:span> æris, Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåsande, fläktande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(windens) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåst, wind:</text:span></text:span> f. resedit; hiberni f-us, Vg.; prospero f-u fortunæ uti, C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(en lefwandes)</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> f-u figuratur vitium, Pn.; equorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(flåsande),</text:span> Vg.; tibia sedilia complet f-u <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(toner),</text:span> Hor.; ventris, Su. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hög ton, uppblåsthet:</text:span></text:span> f-us remittere, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Afflo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(adflo), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåsa, fläkta, andas mot, åt, på, till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol. l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">alicui</text:span>: ventus gelidus ex iis partibus, Varr.; odores tibi a-ant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dofta emot)</text:span> de gramine, Ppt.; Canidia cibo, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T4">alicui aliquid</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåsa ngt till, på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fläkta in i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">inandas ngt i ngt, (med winden) föra till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn, i eg. och oeg. bet.:</text:span> vaporem calidum alicui, Lucr.; mali aliquid faucibus alicujus; odores e floribus a-antur; aura (defensionis) in crimine alicui a-atur; rumor a-verat, frequentiam non fuisse, C.; mater oculis Aeneæ divinos affiarat honores, Vg. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="T4">aliquem, aliquid</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåsa, andas på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. och i allm.:</text:span> terga ventus, L.; Oriens alqm equis anhelis, Vg.; pulli a serpentibus a-antur, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om en gudomlig andes fläkt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inspirera:</text:span></text:span> divino spiritu a-ri, C.; numine dei, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om blixt, eld = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Träffa, tända, bränna:</text:span></text:span> fulminis a-vit me ventis, Vg.; ignibus a-ri proxima quæque solent, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Afflātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fläktande på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">mot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fläkt, wind; påandning, andedrägt:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> ex terra, C.; benignus ventorum, maritimus; montium, Pn.; polypi, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gudomlig fläkt, inspiration:</text:span></text:span> nemo vir magnus sine aliquo divino a-u unquam fuit, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eldens l. solens (heta andedrägt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glöd:</text:span></text:span> ambustus vaporis a-u, L.; truncus solis a-u peraruit, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumflo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåsa omkring; kringblåsa:</text:span></text:span> Austri, St.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> a ventis invidiæ c-ri, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conflo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hopblåsa) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppblåsa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om eld):</text:span> ignem, Pn.; incendium ventus, L. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammansmälta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">nedsmälta:</text:span></text:span> falces in enses, Vg.; c-atur argentum fulmine, Pn.; statuas sibi olim positas c-vit, Su.; Sp. Cassii statua a censoribus c-ta, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammansätta; samla, åsamka sig:</text:span></text:span> una ex duabus naturis c-ta videtur; ex his rebus c-atur id, quod dicimus honestum; manum improborum, C.; æs alienum grande, Sa. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hopsätta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (uppdikta); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillskynda, anstifta, uppwäcka:</text:span></text:span> crimen; mendacium, C.; invidiam alicui, C., Sa.; alicui periculum, negotium, malum, injuriam; bellum; seditionem; tumultum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conflātūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smältning:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕconflo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åter samman</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">- l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">upp-pusta:</text:span></text:span> nulla latens animai pars remanebat in membris, unde r-ri sensus per membra repente posset, Lucr. IV. 924.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēflo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåsa af, bort:</text:span></text:span> Varr., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Difflo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåsa åtskils, iser:</text:span></text:span> d-visti legiones spiritu, quasi ventus folia, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Efflo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intrans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåsa, pusta ut:</text:span></text:span> flamma fornacibus Aetnæ, Lucr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utblåsa, framblåsa, utandas:</text:span></text:span> animam, extremum halitum e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppgifwa),</text:span> C.; ignes naribus equi (solis), Ov.; balænæ nimbos in sublime; hæc e fornacibus e-antur, Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">uppgifwa anden, dö:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Inflo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåsa in, blåsa fram, åt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (angifwa tonen):</text:span> nolo verba i-ta et quasi anhelata gravius exire; servus cum fistula astabat, qui inflaret, C.; spiritum in alveos, Col.<text:line-break/>II.<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåsa på, upp; uppblåsa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (fylla med luft):</text:span> cibo i-atur venter, C.; carbasus vento, Vg.; Jupiter ambas buccas; se rana; venas tetra libido i-vit, Hor.; capilli i-antur, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåsa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ett instrument:</text:span> tibiæ i-tæ, C.; calamos leves, Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. Antipater paulo vehementius i-vit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(blåste starkare på = tog en högre ton l. flygt, i stilen),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inspirera:</text:span></text:span> divino spiritu i-atur poēta, C.; spem alicujus i-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(höja),</text:span> Ct.<text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra stolt:</text:span></text:span> animos, C.; poētam exanimat lentus spectator, sedulus i-at, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Inflātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppswälld:</text:span></text:span> collum serpentis, C., Ov.; fluvius aquis, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppblåst; bländad:</text:span></text:span> aliqua re; animus i. et tumens; homines i-i opinionibus turpiter irridentur, C.; juvenis i-ior, L.; errore, C. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swulstig:</text:span></text:span> Asiani (oratores), C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Inflāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppblåst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = med öfwerdrift:</text:span> Cs. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Inflātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppblåsning, wäderspänning:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1"> </text:span>ventris, Col.; faba habet <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(medför)</text:span> magnam i-em, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Inflātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppblåsande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= uppspelande af ett stycke); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">blåsande:</text:span></text:span> primo tibicinis; tibiæ i-um non recipiunt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ej ge ljud),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(påfläktning) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inspiration:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perflo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intrans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåsa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> allt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fram</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till -, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">stryka fram</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> ad moenia Aquilo -, Luc.; Favonius, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: venti terras turbine p-ant, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perflābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som kan genomblåsas:</text:span></text:span> dii, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perflātĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: id.: Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perflātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Luftdrag:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōflo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Framblåsa, -andas, -fnysa:</text:span></text:span> flammas, Ov.; toto pectore somnum, Vg.; iras, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smälta:</text:span></text:span> massa p-atur, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōflātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåst, andedrägt:</text:span></text:span> æstivus, Col.; (dormientis), St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕflo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåsa emot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wara widrig, om wind):</text:span> etesiæ valde r.; ventis r-bus rejici; quum fortuna r-vit, affligimur, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åter utblåsa; blåsa tillbaka:</text:span></text:span> āer ducitur et r-atur, Lucr.; sinu r-to, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕflātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Motwind:</text:span></text:span> navis delata Uticam r-u, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utblåsande, -sprutande:</text:span></text:span> balænæ, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sufflo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intrans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåsa inunder:</text:span></text:span> per fores (apium) rubetæ, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåsa upp:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> languidos ignes, Pn.; buccas, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sufflātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppblåst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (stolt); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wred; swulstig:</text:span></text:span> scientia, Varr.; Pt.; (orator), Gell. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sufflātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppblåsande:</text:span></text:span> bullarum, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Floccus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ullflocka, ullflockor, dun:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> ne qui ovium f-i intereant, Varr.; pinnis et f-is consternere nidum, Pn.; legere in veste, Ce.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. såsom beteckning för det minsta, obetydligaste (fnask, lappri):</text:span> f-i facere aliquid; f-um non interduim, Pt.; non f-i pendere aliquid, Ter.; rempublicam f-i non facere, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Floccōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēfloccātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afplockad, bar:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Flora, -ralis, -ralia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Florus, Flos. <text:line-break/>Florens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Floreo. Flos.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>lōrentia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">staden (Firenze) Florenz wid Arno, under forntiden obetydlig mot det ofwanför belägna</text:span> Fæsulæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Fiesole).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Flōrentīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Floreo, Floresco, Floreus, Flori . . ., Florulentus, Florus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Flos.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flōs,</text:span> flōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomma, blomster; blomning,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (blom), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">blomstring:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> f-es lætissimi Hennæ sunt omni tempore anni, C.; f-es decerpere, Lucr.; legere, Vg.; f-es amoenæ ferre jube rosæ; fons dulci digne mero non sine f-bus; caput impedire myrto aut f-e, terræ quem ferunt solutæ, Hor.; faba aquas in f-e concupiscit, Col.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">= </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ungdomsbehag, -fägring, -friskhet:</text:span></text:span> XVI anni: f. ipsus, Ter.; esse in f-e ætatis, C., L.; viridissimo f-e puella; amisit polluto corpore f-em, Catl.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomman</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = det förnämsta af ett folk, en klaß m. m.: abstract = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">blomstring, skönhet, lycka:</text:span></text:span> f. delibatus populi, Enn. ap. C.; omnis f. nobilitatis et juventutis; provincia Galliæ f. Italiæ; civium f. et robur; te quum vitæ f-e, tum mortis opportunitate divino consilio ortum et exstinctum arbitror; in ipso f-e Græciæ Pisistratus fuit, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">framställningens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blommor, prydnader:</text:span></text:span> oratio conspersa quasi verborum sententiarumque f-bus, C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af döda naturföremål = det öfwersta, högsta, finaste, bästa:</text:span> vini f., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fradgan l. doften,</text:span> Cato; Bacchi f. evanuit, Lucr.; f. salis = sal candidus, Cato; f. lactis = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gräddan,</text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flōreo</text:span>, ui, s. s., 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomma, stå i blomma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">blomning, blomstra:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men. (om wäxter och jord):</text:span> arbor; terra, C.; ager, Vg.; segetes, Ov.; cucumis, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wara ung och frisk, i ungdomens fulla kraft:</text:span> juvenum ritu, Hor.; genæ Apollinis, St.; tribus actis annis f-et equus, Lucr.; ætate et formā f., T.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara i wälstånd, wälmakt, flor; wara rik</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wara ansedd, mäktig, utmärkt, berömd, utmärka sig för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> Magna Græcia nunc deleta est, tunc f-bat; in senectute præter ceteros, Cato; in Græcia musici f-erunt; in curia f.; inter aliquos f.; Græcia quondam opibus, imperio, gloria f-uit; Pericles f-uit omni genere virtutis, Isocrates nobilitate discipulorum; honoribus et rerum gestarum gloriā f-re; Crassus magis privatis officiis et ingenii laude f-uit, quam fructu amplitudinis aut reipublicæ dignitate; in populari ratione <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(demagogien);</text:span> in omni actione, C.; urbes f-ent populis, mare puppibus, Lucr.; Miltiades et antiquitate generis et gloria majorum et sua modestia unus omnium maxime f-bat, N.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om win: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jäsa, fradgas:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flōrens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomstrande:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af ungdom):</text:span> f-es ætatibus, Vg.; ævum f., Lucr.; juventa, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lysande, prålande, strålande:</text:span></text:span> catervæ ære, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som är i blomstrande tillstånd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">mäktig, rik, ansedd, skön, utmärkt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt:</text:span> quam civitatem f-simam accepissent, dissipaverunt; <text:soft-page-break/>in f-sima civitate omnibus gloriā præstitit; te beatum, te f-em putas; homo f-ns ætate, opibus, honoribus, ingenio, liberis, propinquis, amicis; modus (transferendi) nullus f-ior est; castra Etruscorum f-sima, C.; f-es Etruscorum opes, L.; res f-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(blomstrande ställning),</text:span> Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flōresco</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Inch.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Börja blomstra:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> pulejum brumali die, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Börja komma till makt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">anseende, berömdhet:</text:span></text:span> hominem nunc primum f-tem evertere; tua justitia quotidie magis, C.; patria nostra, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flōreus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är af l. prydes af blommor, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomster-, blomsterrik:</text:span></text:span> corona, Pt.; rura, Vg.; serta, Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flōrĭcŏmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: (coma): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med hår af blommor, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">blomsterrik:</text:span></text:span> Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flōrĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomstrande, blommande, blomsterrik:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> f-a et varia, C.; prata, Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomstrande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till år och helsa:</text:span> puellula; ætas, Catl.; forma, Su. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om färger l. till färgen: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomstrande, färgrik, bjert:</text:span></text:span> colorum pulcritudine et varietate f-ora sunt in novis picturis pleraque, quam in veteribus, C.; colores, Pn.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om framställning: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomstrande, sirlig:</text:span></text:span> orator f-ior, C.; oratio, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flōrĭdŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomstrande:</text:span></text:span> os, Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flōrĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blommor frambringande:</text:span></text:span> saltus, Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flōrĭlĕgus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomstersamlande:</text:span></text:span> apes, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flōrĭpărus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: (pario): = florifer: ver, Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flōrŭlentus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomstrande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af ungdom):</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flōrus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomstrande:</text:span></text:span> Gell. - <text:span text:style-name="T4">Subst.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>lōra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blomstergudinnan, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flora:</text:span></text:span> Ov., Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>lōrālis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Flora tillhörig, Floras.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flōrālia</text:span>, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Floras fest:</text:span> Varr., Ov. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomstergård:</text:span></text:span> pomaria et f-a, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Floscŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomster, blomma,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med bibetydelse af swaghet och förgänglighet:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> ficta omnia velut f-i decidunt, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om det förnämsta, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomman</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af en sak:</text:span> f. Juventiorum, Catl.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">talets </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blommor, prydnader, grannlåt:</text:span></text:span> omnes undique f-os carpere, C.; f-os captare viro turpe est, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēflōreo</text:span>, 2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēflōresco</text:span>, rui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomma ut, blomstra ut; förwißna:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> vitis - pejus d-ret; omne frumentum octo diebus d-scit, Col.; flos quum carptus d-uit, Catl.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(wißna, falla af, sjunka):</text:span></text:span> formæ dignitas morbo; amores et deliciæ - celeriter; orator, C.; res; animi, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēflōro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">beröfwa ngt deß blomstring, glans:</text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Efflōreo</text:span>, 2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Efflōresco</text:span>, rui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fram-, uppblomstra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (bildl. = ”uppstiga till, lysa af”):</text:span> ex rerum cognitione oratio; utilitas ex amicitia; ei ad summam gloriam e-enti vita erepta est; ingenii laudibus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Præflōreo</text:span>, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomma i förtid:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Præflōro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">i förwäg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (taga blomman af ngt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">winna, njuta:</text:span></text:span> gloriam victoriæ jam ad Thermopylas p-tam esse; gaudium spes, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕflōresco</text:span>, rui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomma, börja blomma på nytt:</text:span></text:span> herba, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sŭperflōresco</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blomma ofwanför:</text:span></text:span> sibi cucumis, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Flu . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fluo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fluo,</text:span> fluxi, (fluxurus), 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyta, strömma, rinna:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. amnis per agros, C.; leni agmine Thybris; sudor undique rivis; æs f-it rivis, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. f. aliqua re = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drypa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt:</text:span> membra sudore, L.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. (om ledig, jemn rörelse, eg och oeg.):</text:span> f-unt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(glida)</text:span> arma de manibus; ex ejus lingua melle dulcius f-bat oratio; Herodotus sine ullis salebris quasi sedatus amnis f., C.; turba castris f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(strömmar),</text:span> Vg.; Lucilius f-it lutulentus, Hor.; carmen venā pauperiore f., Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bölja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fladdra, sitta lös; swäfwa ut, (sakna stadga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hållning):</text:span></text:span> nodo sinus collecta fluentes, Vg.; comæ per colla f-unt; tunica f-it, Ppt.; balteus, Qu.; efficiendum est, ne f-at oratio, ne vagetur, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utbreda sig; sprida sig:</text:span></text:span> doctrina Pythagoræ longe lateque f-bat, C.; ramos f-entes compescere, Vg.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upplösas; domna, slappas:</text:span></text:span> membra dissolvuntur f-untque, Lucr.: mollitiā, C.; vires lassitudine, L.; luxu aliquis, Ct.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyta undan, bort; förgå, -swinna:</text:span></text:span> omnia, quæ jam dilapsa f-runt; f-it voluptas corporis et prima quæque avolat, C.; ex illo tempore f-re spes Danaûm - fractæ vires, Vg.; tempora mihi tarda ingrata f-unt, Hor.<text:line-break/>f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Härflyta:</text:span></text:span> hæc omnia ex (ab) eodem fonte f-runt, C. <text:line-break/>g. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aflöpa; öfwergå till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> in rebus prosperis et ad nostram utilitatem f-tibus; res f-it ad interregnum, C. - <text:span text:style-name="T4">part. præs.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flytande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">= </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ledig, lätt:</text:span></text:span> tracta et f. oratio, C.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pussig;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om framställning) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">swamlig, lös; weklig, slapp:</text:span></text:span> buccæ; dissoluta et f. oratio, C.; discipuli, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluctio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flytande, flöde:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluctus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ström</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (strömning), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wåg, bölja:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> humoris f., Lucr.; ad f-um ajunt declamare solitum Demosthenem; f-u operiri; saxis frangitur f.; f-bus jactari, se committere, C.; vastos volvunt (venti) ad litora f-us; hi summo in f-u pendent; procella f-ūs ad sidera tollit; f-bus opprimi, Vg.; maris; tumidi; æquorei; f-u icta latus navis, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> f-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(anstormande)</text:span> totius barbariæ urbs ferre non poterit; f-<text:soft-page-break/>us contionum, C.; civiles f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(politikens),</text:span> N.; curarum; irarum, Lucr.; fortunæ, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluctĭcŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: Ap. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluctĭfrăgus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: (frango): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som bryter wågorna, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wågbrytande:</text:span></text:span> litus, Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluctĭgĕnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: (gigno): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I wågen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hafwet född:</text:span></text:span> Av.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluctĭger</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Af wågen buren:</text:span></text:span> paro, C. ap. Isid. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluctĭsŏnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: (sono): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Af wågornas brus genljudande:</text:span></text:span> litus, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluctĭvăgus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: (vagor): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwer hafwet ströfwande:</text:span></text:span> nauta, St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluctuo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dep.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluctuor</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om watten, hafwet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swalla, gå i wågor:</text:span></text:span> mare f-at, Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drifwas, wräkas af</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">på wågen:</text:span></text:span> quadriremem in salo f-ntem reliquerat; quid est tam commune quam mare f-tibus?, C.; lignum f-atur, Pn.; navis f-ns errat in undis, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om massor, skaror: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bölja:</text:span></text:span> turba f-ns, T.; acies f-ns et instabilis, L.; omnis tellus ære renidente (aciei), Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om föredrag: (orhythmisk), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lös, swamlig:</text:span></text:span> dissoluta et f-ns oratio, C. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till l. om sinnesstämning: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swalla, wara upprörd; wackla, tweka, wara obestämd:</text:span></text:span> in decretis suis f-re; sententiam f-tem confirmare, C.; magno irarum f-at æstu; nunc huc, nunc illuc f-at, Vg.; utrius populi victoriam mallet esse, f-tus animo fuerat, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluctuātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: stomachi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(häfning),</text:span> Pn.; totius corporis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(oro),</text:span> Sen.; animorum f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(willrådighet),</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confluctuo</text:span>, 1.: vestis, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfluctuo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomströmma:</text:span></text:span> artus, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluctuōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Böljande:</text:span></text:span> mare, Pt.; smaragdus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wågtecknad),</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I flytande rörelse:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flytande:</text:span></text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wåg, flöde:</text:span></text:span> Xanthi; Cocyti, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluentĭsŏnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af wågor dånande, brusande:</text:span> Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluĭdus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flūvĭdus</text:span> (Lucr.), <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flytande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till sin natur):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> liquor, Vg.; f-o contrarium terrenum, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lös, slapp, wek:</text:span></text:span> f-i pendent lacerti, Ov.; corpora Gallorum, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluĭto</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flūto</text:span> (Lucr., Varr.), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bölja, flyta omkring, simma:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> mare flutat, Lucr.; alveus, L.; navis in alto; belua, C.; sarcinæ, Ct.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i rummet) = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bölja, fladdra, wackla:</text:span></text:span> amictus, Catl.; vela, Ov.; vestis; miles, T.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i inre men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drifwas hit och dit, wackla:</text:span></text:span> fides, T.; dubiæ spe pendulus horæ, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flūmen</text:span>, mĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flod, ström:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: flöde, flod af ngt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> f-e vivo se abluere; lacrimarum, Vg.; picis; sanguinis, Lucr.; Tantalus fugientia captat f-a, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> ingenii; verborum; orationis, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">prægnant om ett föredrag: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lugn, jemn gång:</text:span></text:span> C. de Or. II. 10.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flod, ström</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> såsom ett serskitdt slag af wattendrag i naturen:</text:span> f. arcere, avertere; - non aqua inclusa tenetur, sed universum f. erumpit, C.; f. Rhenus, Rhodanus; f-e secundo, adverso <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med, mot strömmen);</text:span> Lutetiam ire contra vim et impetus f-is, Cs.; f. Nilus, N.; f. Asturæ, L.; f. labitur, Ct., Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flūmentāna</text:span> porta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i Rom:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flūmĭneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som tillhör flod, lefwer i, wäxer i l. wid flod, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flod-:</text:span></text:span> aqua; alnus, Sil.; volucris; ulva, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Strömmande, flöde:</text:span></text:span> amnis, Ap.; stomachi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utsot),</text:span> Ce.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flūta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hafsål:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fluto, Fluvidus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fluito, Fluidus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flŭvius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flod, ström:</text:span></text:span> Hypanis, Atratus f., C.; f-orum rex Eridanus, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flodwatten:</text:span></text:span> f-os ministrare (duci apium); dulcibus f-is perfundere pecus omne, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flŭviālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flod-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">som är af</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">från flod, som wäxer wid</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> aqua; arundo, Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flŭviātĭcus</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Flŭviātĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flod-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">som lefwer, finnes, går i flod:</text:span></text:span> testudo f-lis, C.; naves f-les, L.; animal f-um, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluxio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluxura</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluxus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flytning, flöde:</text:span></text:span> sanguinis, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluxus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flytande, rinnande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (drypande):</text:span> sucus, Pn.; vas, Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(böljande), lös, slak:</text:span></text:span> crinis, T.; cinctura, Su.; habena, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slapp, weklig; förfallen, swag, dålig:</text:span></text:span> nostræ res, C.; animus, Sa.; neglecta aut ævo f-a pars muri; Galbæ f-a auctoritas, T.; spado, Mt.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ostadig, opålitlig, förgänglig:</text:span></text:span> fides f., Pt., Sa.; formæ gloria incerta et f-a est, Sa.; res humanæ f-æ et mobiles, L.; instabilis et f., T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fluxe</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slappt:</text:span></text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Affluo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(adfluo), xi, 3.:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillströmma, -flyta; flyta inwid, utmed</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> æstus bis a-unt bisque remeant, Pn.; amnis castris, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med bibet. af riklighet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillströmma:</text:span></text:span> voluptates, C.; copiæ, L.; hostes, Ct.; ingens comitum numerus, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med bibetydelse af det lätta, omärkliga i närmandet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smyga sig, flyga till, på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> voluptas ad sensus; nihil rumoris a-xit, C.; amor incautis, Ov.<text:line-break/>II.<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerflöda, finnas i öfwerflöd:</text:span></text:span> divitiæ, Sa.; opes, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drypa af; hafwa öfwerflöd på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">af:</text:span></text:span> unguentis, C.; divitiis, Lucr.; voluptatibus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Affluens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Comp.</text:span> -tior, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerflödande, riklig:</text:span></text:span> copiæ omnium rerum a-es, C.; numerus senatorum, Su.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som har öfwerflöd på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rik, full</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af -:</text:span> homo a-ns copiis, bonitate, lepore; vera amicitia a-ior mihi videtur; domus omni scelere a., C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Affluenter</text:span>, -tius, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rikligt, öfwerflödigt, ymnigt:</text:span></text:span> vivere a-ius, N.; haurire voluptates, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Affluentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rikt förråd; öfwerflöd:</text:span></text:span> in omnium rerum a-a vivere, C.; annonæ, Pn.; munditiam, non a-am affectabat, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumfluo</text:span>, xi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kringflyta, flyta omkring:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> Carinam fluvius, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">swärma omkring, i mängd l. rikligt mått omgifwa ngn:</text:span> nos cervorum multitudo, Varr.; exercitus colonorum (Catilinam), C.; secundæ res vos, Ct.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol. = swäfwa ut, (utbreda sig, utan stadga och form):</text:span> oratio, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer:</text:span> c-re aliqua re = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Simma uti, frossa i öfwerflöd på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> c. omnibus copiis; gloriā, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumfluus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kringflytande:</text:span></text:span> amnis, Ov.; mare, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kringfluten:</text:span></text:span> Thybridis alveo insula, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confluo</text:span>, xi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanflyta, -strömma:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> duo portus in exitu c-unt; amnis dilapsus in unum c-it, C.; vasti amnes in Phasin, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Strömma tillsammans, tillströmma:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om menniskor:</text:span> multi in hanc urbem ex diversis locis; plures ad hæc studia, C.; vulgus ad ejus triremem, N. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker:</text:span> ad alqm laus honor, dignitas, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confluens</text:span>, tis; <text:span text:style-name="T4">plur.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confluentes</text:span>, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanflöde,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ställe der twå floder förena sig:</text:span> ad c-em Mosæ et Rheni pervenire, Cs.; in Euphratis c-e, Pn.; ad c-es (Tiberis et Anienis) castra ponere, L.; c-es Padi et Adduæ, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confluentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanflöde:</text:span></text:span> Mcb.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conflŭvium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: id.: Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēfluo</text:span>, xi, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyta, rinna ned, ut:</text:span></text:span> in plures partes Rhenus, Cs.; aries mersus secundo d-it amni, Vg.; mel ex arbore, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förrinna, rinna bort:</text:span></text:span> rusticus exspectat, dum d-at amnis, Hor.; hiberni torrentes, Sen. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bild:</text:span> non verendum est, ne quid in terram <text:soft-page-break/>d-at, aut ne plus æquo in amicitiam congeratur, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(strömma), falla, sjunka, swäfwa ned:</text:span></text:span> coronæ de capite, C.; eques ad, in terram, L.; vestis ad imos pedes, Vg.; multa tibi merces a Jove d-at, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med bibetydelsen: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sprida, utbreda sig:</text:span></text:span> hæc e fontibus Sophistarum in forum, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sjunka ned</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till ngt sämre):</text:span> ab amicitiis perfectorum hominum ad leves amicitias d-xit oratio; a necessariis artificiis ad elegantiora d-ximus, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rinna ned, falla af l. bort = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gå förlorad; förgå, -swinna:</text:span></text:span> comæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(falla af),</text:span> Ov.; tempus, vires, Sa.; unus me absente d-xit, C.; sic d-it horridus ille Saturnius, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēfluus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedströmmande, -rinnande, affallande:</text:span></text:span> vasculum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wattenur),</text:span> Ap.; capilli, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēflŭvium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: capilli <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hårfällning),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēfluxus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedflytande:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Diffluo</text:span>, xi, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyta åtskils, sprida sig, swäfwa ut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om wätskor):</text:span> humor, Lucr. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bild:</text:span> quasi extra ripas nos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i föredraget)</text:span> d-entes coërcuit, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upplösas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i naturlig och moralisk men.), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förslappas, -slöas, -derfwas:</text:span></text:span> privata cibo natura animantum, Lucr.; animus luxuriā et lasciviā, Ter.; deliciis d-entes; d-re luxuriā, C.; luxu, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Difflŭvio</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utgrena, dela:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effluo</text:span>, xi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyta, strömma ut:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> humor lactis, Pn.; vita cum sanguine, C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyta bort, upplösas i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">swäfwa, fladdra ut:</text:span></text:span> in lacrimas e., Luc.; toga laxa, Tib.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. (om sinliga och osinliga subject): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glida, falla ur, bort; förrinna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om tid):</text:span> manibus opus, Lucr.; urna manibus, Ov.; aliquid ex animo plane; mens solita alicui; ætas, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Komma ut, bli bekant:</text:span></text:span> multa ex vestra disciplina e-unt et ad aures nostras permanant, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Efflŭvium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utflöde:</text:span></text:span> humoris e corpore, Pn.; e-o lacus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stället der den utgräfda sjön flöt ut)</text:span> adpositæ mensæ, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Influo</text:span>, xi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inflyta, -strömma:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> Hypanis fluvius in Pontum; sanguis in ventriculum cordis, C.; Rhenus in Oceanum, Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om menniskomassor, språk: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inströmma, intränga:</text:span></text:span> copiæ Gallorum in Italiam, C.; Græcus sermo aliquo, Qu. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Intränga, insmyga sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (och dermed </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">intaga, utöfwa inflytande på):</text:span></text:span> est aditus ad multitudinem, ut in universorum animos tamquam i-re possimus; nihil tam facile in animos teneros ac molles i-it, quam canendi modi; quantis blanditiis in aures contionis i-bat Papirius, C.; dolor menti, Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingjutas, inläggas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillkomma; tillfalla:</text:span></text:span> ex illa lenitate ad hanc vim i-at oportet aliquid, C.; bonum alicui, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Influxio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inflöde:</text:span></text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sŭbinfluo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyta inunder:</text:span></text:span> aquæ terras, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Interfluo</text:span>, xi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyta emellan:</text:span></text:span> amnis moenia, Ct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Interfluus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som flyter emellan:</text:span> Euphrates, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfluo</text:span>, xi, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyta, rinna igenom, bort:</text:span></text:span> vinum per colum, Col.; amnis in mare, Pn.; commoda omnia quasi in vas pertusum congesta p-xere, Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drypa, droppa, wara otät:</text:span></text:span> lagena, Varr.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> hac atque illac perfluo (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kan ej tiga med ngt),</text:span> Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Præfluo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyta framför, förbi:</text:span></text:span> infima valle p-it Tiberis, L.; aquæ Tibur p-unt, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Præfluus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förbiflytande:</text:span></text:span> amnis, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Præterfluo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyta förbi, undan:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. amnis moenia, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: (förswinna):</text:span> sapiens non sinit præteritam voluptatem p-re, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōfluo</text:span>, xi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyta, rinna, strömma fram:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> humor, Vg.; lacus ad mare, C.; sanguis ex vulnere, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> ejus ore sermo melle dulcior, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fortgå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lätt, hejdlöst):</text:span> ad famam, C.; ad incognitas libidines facilitate adulteriorum, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōfluens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flytande, strömmande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> aqua, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> genus dicendi cum æquabili lenitate p.; loquacitas; celeritas, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōfluens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flytande, rinnande watten:</text:span></text:span> dejici in -, C., Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōfluenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flytande, lätt:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōfluentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flöde, (lätthet):</text:span></text:span> loquendi, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōfluus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flytande, strömmande:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōflŭvium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flöde, flytning:</text:span></text:span> sanguinis p. reprimere, Col.; mulierum; alvi; narium, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfluo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyta, rinna, strömma, swalla tillbaka,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i omwänd rigtning:</text:span> amnis; undæ, Vg.; Mæandros fluit r-itque, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfluus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillbakaströmmande:</text:span></text:span> mare, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Septemfluus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sjufaldt strömmande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med sju flöden (grenar):</text:span> Nilus, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Subterfluo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyta hän under:</text:span></text:span> torrens, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sŭperfluo</text:span>, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flyta ofwanpå:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> oeg.:</text:span> aures aliquid, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flöda öfwer, finnas i öfwerflöd; hafwa öfwerflöd; wara öfwerflödig:</text:span></text:span> Nilus, T.; pecunia, Sen.; superbus homo et s-ens, Catl.; nihil s-it, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sŭperfluus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerflödande; öfwerflödig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (onödig):</text:span> flumina campis, Pn.; quærere, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sŭperfluĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerflöd, -mått:</text:span></text:span> pampinorum, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Transfluo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rinna fram, utöfwer:</text:span></text:span> sanguis transfossis; vina, Pn.; dies <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förrinner),</text:span> Cd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Focale, Focaneus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fauces.<text:line-break/>Focillo, -lor, Foculus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Focus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fŏcus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Eldstad, härd, spis;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> äfwen flyttbar wärme- l. kokapparat, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fyrfat, kök:</text:span></text:span> ad f-um sedere; ejicere alqm domo f-isque patriis; pro aris et f-is pugnare, C.; ligna super f-o large repone, Hor.; unguere f-um, ubi coquantur placentæ, Cato; circa coenationem cum obsoniis f-os transferre, Sen.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Altarhärd, altare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (poet.):</text:span> f-os de cæspite ponere, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŏcillo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dep.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŏcillor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(wärma), Wårda, sköta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sjuka); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hålla wid makt, bota; befordra:</text:span></text:span> lenibus remediis f-re alqm, Sen.; societas reconciliationibus f-ta, Su.; sua commoda f-antur, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfŏcillo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wederqwicka:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŏcŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liten spis; litet fyrfat</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kök; altarhärd:</text:span></text:span> ferventes, Pt.; f-i, dolia, Cato; f-o ad sacrificium accenso manum imponere, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fŏdio,</text:span> fōdi, fossum, 3. (fodiri, Varr.): <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gräfwa, omgräfwa, utgräfwa, uppgräfwa:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> semper te video f-re aut arare -, Ter.; ipse sibi f-ret, C.; humum; cubilia talpæ, Vg.; puteos, Cs.; fossam; argentum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppgräfwa),</text:span> L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> oculos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utgräfwa, -rifwa),</text:span> Pt.; aquas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwerfara, plöja),</text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sticka, hugga, stöta, genomborra:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> stimulis aliquem, C.; equi armos calcaribus, Vg.; ora hostium hastis, L.; cornix pectora rostro, Ov.; gladio aliquem, T. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> pungit dolor: vel fodiat sane, C.; cor alicujus, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŏdĭco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stöta, hugga, sticka:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> latus alicujus servus, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> animum, Pt.; nos res malæ, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŏdīna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grufwa; gräfwande:</text:span></text:span> Varr., Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fossa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Graf</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (såsom befästning l. afloppskanal); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">dike, grop, kanal:</text:span></text:span> oppidum vallo et f-a circumdare; Rheni f-am (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Rh. såsom en fästningsgraf)</text:span> immanissimis gentibus opponere, C.; castra vallo et f-a munire; f-am ducere, præducere, obducere, Cs.; f-am navigabilem a lacu Averno ad Tiberim deprimere, Su.; f-am fodiens palæ innisus Cincinnatus, L.; f. agrestis; navigabilis; inter Mosam et Rhenum trium et viginti milium spatio f-am perduxit Corbulo, qua incerta Oceani vitarentur, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fossīcius</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fossĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppgräfd, gruf-:</text:span></text:span> creta f-cia; sal fossile, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fossio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gräfning, dikning:</text:span></text:span> agri, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fosso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomborra:</text:span></text:span> Enn. ap. Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fossor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gräfware, (bonde):</text:span></text:span> Vg., Hor., Col., Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fossŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Litet dike:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fossūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gräfnings-, dikningssätt:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Affŏdio</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gräfwa till, lägga till wid gräfwandet:</text:span></text:span> (inc. l.) nostro solo cæspitem, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumfŏdio</text:span>, (fōdi), fossum, 3. (4. Col.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gräfwa omkring, kringgräfwa:</text:span></text:span> platanos, Sen.; arbores, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumfossor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumfossūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: arborum, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confŏdio</text:span>, (fōdi), fossum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Omgräfwa, uppgräfwa:</text:span></text:span> terram minute, Cato; hortum, Pt.; venas, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomborra, -sticka:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> telis aliquem, N.; vulneribus alqm, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> tot judiciis c-sus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fälld),</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēfŏdio</text:span>, fōdi, fossum, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedgräfwa, -mylla:</text:span></text:span> thesaurum sub lecto, C.; cadaver, signum hominis in terram, L.; quidquid sub terra est, in apricum proferet ætas, d-iet condetque nitentia, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gräfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ut, upp:</text:span> scrobem, Col.; terram, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effŏdio</text:span>, fōdi, fossum, 3. (4. Pt.):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ut-, upp-, framgräfwa:</text:span></text:span> aurum, æs, argentum, C.; e-untur opes, irritamenta malorum, Ov.; scrobem, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utsticka:</text:span></text:span> oculos e-iri, Pt., Ter.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.</text:span> oculos oræ maritimæ, Carthaginem et Corinthum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infŏdio</text:span>, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">In-, nedgräfwa:</text:span></text:span> aliquid in terram, Cs.; aliquid humo, Hor.; corpora <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jorda),</text:span> N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utgräfwa:</text:span></text:span> lacum, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Interfŏdio</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sticka in emellan,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> uti -:</text:span> pupillas, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfŏdio</text:span>, fōdi (fodivi), fossum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomgräfwa, -spränga:</text:span></text:span> parietem, Pt., C.; montem, Varr.; fretum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gräfwa),</text:span> L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomborra, -sticka:</text:span></text:span> thoracem, Vg.; equum, Sil.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfossor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomgräfware:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Imperfossus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ogenomborrad:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Præfŏdio</text:span>, fōdi, fossum, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gräfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> framför = genom grafwar </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förskansa:</text:span></text:span> portas, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förut, på förhand gräfwa, nedgräfwa:</text:span></text:span> scrobem, Pn.; aurum, quod jam p-rat, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfŏdio</text:span>, fōdi, fossum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åter uppgräfwa:</text:span></text:span> sŏlum, Pn.; radices, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Suffŏdio</text:span>, fōdi, fossum, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undergräfwa, -minera; upprota:</text:span></text:span> sacella, C.; oppidum cuniculis, Pn.; sus rostro, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inunder</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">nedifrån</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">under</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sticka, genomborra:</text:span></text:span> equos, Cs., L.; ilia equis, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Suffossio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undergräfning, -minering:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Transfŏdio</text:span>, fōdi, fossum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomborra:</text:span></text:span> Gallos, Cs.; latus alicui, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Foecund . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fecundus.<text:line-break/>Foede <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Foedus.<text:line-break/>Foederatus, Foedifragus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Foedus.<text:line-break/>Foeditas, Foedo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Foedus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Foedus,</text:span> ĕris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enl.</text:span> Varr. olim fidus: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af roten i</text:span> fĭdes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med vocalstegring</text:span> fo-idus): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fördrag:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">politiskt:</text:span> ferire, icere, facere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sluta);</text:span> f. servare; cavere de f-e; frangere, violare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bryta);</text:span> renovare; f. sanctum et religiosum; in publicis f-um religionibus sanctus et diligens, C.; f. jungere, L.; f-e sibi adjungere alqm, Cs.; f. et amicitiam petere, accipere, Sa.; civitas æquissimo f-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på wilkor af största jemnlikhet)</text:span> cum Romanis, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerenskommelse, lag; förbindelse, förbund, förening:</text:span></text:span> scelerum, C.; naturæ, Lucr.; domesticum publico adjunxit f., filia in matrimonium data; Ap. Claudius expers et civilis et humani f-is; f. tollendæ appellationis (tribunorum), L.; Jupiter ventis dedit regem, qui f-e certo et premere et laxas sciret dare jussus habenas; non hæc in f-a veni <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ingått sådan (äkta) förening);</text:span> non æquo f-e amare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utan genkärlek),</text:span> Vg.; lecti, conjugale, amicitiæ, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Foedĕrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som står i fördrag, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förbunden</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngn:</text:span> populus; civitas, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Foedĭfrăgus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: (frango): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fördragsbrytande, (-are):</text:span></text:span> Poeni f-i, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Foedus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sinlig men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stygg, ful, wederstygglig, widrig, otäck, wanställd; hisklig, hemsk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> att se:</text:span> homo, Ter., Qu.; monstrum, C.; sapor, Lucr.; odor, Pn.; loca tetra, inculta, f-a, formidolosa; oculi, Sa.; tempestas; incendium, L.; cicatrix, Hor.; f-a fumo, Juv.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oanständig, moraliskt wederstygglig, neslig; skändlig:</text:span></text:span> f-a, flagitiosa; luxuria quum omni ætati f-a, tum senectuti f-sima est; f. exitus judicii; mortis genus; latrones f-simi, C.; facinus, Ter.; fuga, L., T., Sa.; f. consilium, exemplum; f-um inceptu, f-um exitu, L.; condiciones; Orpheus homines a f-o victu deterruit, Hor. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gräslig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förödande, förfärlig:</text:span></text:span> ego bellum f-simum fore arbitror, C.; pestilentia f-a hominibus, f-a pecori, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Foede</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wederstyggligt, gräsligt; skamligt, nesligt; skändligt; på förfärligt sätt:</text:span></text:span> f. distrahere alqm, Pt.; vita humana jacebat f. oppressa, Lucr.; causa optima agitur f.; f. divexari, C.; ad Alliam f. pugnatum est; f-ius pulsi sunt; Virginia f. ad libidinem petita, L.; f. perire, Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Foedĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wederstygglighet, widrighet:</text:span></text:span> odoris, C.; vulnerum, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">moralisk </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Styggelse, skamlighet, förnedring:</text:span></text:span> turpitudinis; animi turpificati depravatio et f.; vestitūs f. (quod senatus saga sumpsit contra consulem), C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gräslighet, förfärlighet:</text:span></text:span> Alpium; spectaculi, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Foedo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Besudla, wanställa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sarga, illa tilltyga):</text:span> Harpyiæ omnia f-ant immundo contactu; ora unguibus; ferro volucres; latebras Argolicas (equum), Vg.; verberibus aliquem, T.<text:line-break/>2.<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i religiös l. moralisk mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Orena, befläcka, utskämma, wanära:</text:span></text:span> ignes, quos ipse sacraverat, sanguine, Vg.; sanctissima sacella - summā turpitudine f-ta, C.; gloriam majorum, Pt.; victoria per avaritiam f-ta, T.; animi bona aliqua re, Ct. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förgripa sig på, wåldföra; föröda; göra sorglig, hemsk:</text:span></text:span> domestici belli exstinctorem scelere nefario, C.; agros; annus clade f-tus, L.; volucres, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Foemina, Foenum, Foenus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med härledningar se</text:span> Femina, Fenum, Fenus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Foeteo,</text:span> ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stinka:</text:span></text:span> anima alicui, Pt.; vino f-et, Mt. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> sermo mihi, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Foetĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stinkande:</text:span></text:span> os, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Foetor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stank:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Foetŭlentus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: = Foetidus: Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Foetūtīna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stinkande ort:</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Foetus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med härledningar se</text:span> Fetus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>ōlia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fŏlium,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blad, löf:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> laureæ; plumā aut f-o facilius moveri, C.; brevioribus f-is (laureæ) ornare alqm, Hor.; f-is mandat, in f-is describit carmina Sibylla, Vg., Juv.; myrti; cæpæ, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. chartarum f-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(pappersblad),</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŏliāceus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bladlik, -tunn:</text:span></text:span> semina, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŏliātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Löfwad:</text:span></text:span> Ap. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">deraf</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŏliātum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nardus-balsam:</text:span></text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŏliōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">löfrik:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Follis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blåsbälg:</text:span></text:span> sine f-e et incudibus, C.; fabrilis, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Penningepung, -påse:</text:span></text:span> tenso f-e reverti (mercatorem), Juv.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wäderboll:</text:span></text:span> ludere f-e, Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Follĭcans</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppspänd:</text:span></text:span> nares, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Follĭcŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Påse:</text:span></text:span> os obvolvere f-o, C.; frumenti, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Boll:</text:span></text:span> Su.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hylsa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (på säd, frukter):</text:span> spicæ, Sen.; acinorum, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Follītim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i fråga om pungen:</text:span> ductitare alqm <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bedraga),</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fomentum, Fomes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Foveo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fons,</text:span> tis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> fundo?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Källa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> f. aquæ dulcis; rivorum a f-e deductio, C.; f. prorumpit, Cs.; f. vivus, illimis, sacer, Ov.; exsilit, Pn.; f. splendidior vitro, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. (utm. det, hwarifrån ngt hemtas, härledes, -stammar, har sitt upphof):</text:span> f-es philosophiæ aperire; a f-bus Stoicorum haurire; tardi ingenii est rivos rerum consectari, f-es non videre; tui f-es etiam inimicis (de jure consulentibus) patent; f-es argumentorum, maledicti; philosophorum greges, jam ab illo f-e et capite Socrate, C.; curarum, Lucr.; Mæonides, a quo, ceu f-e perenni, vatum Pieriis ora rigantur aquis, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fontānus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är källas l. från källa, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Käll-:</text:span></text:span> aqua, Pn.; ora f-a recludere, Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fontĭcŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liten källa:</text:span></text:span> Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fontĭnālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">källas:</text:span> deus, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>ontejus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Fontejānus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fonticulus, -tinalis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fons.<text:line-break/>For <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fari.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">(<text:span text:style-name="T1">Fŏra,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">obr. nom. till)</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŏras</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T4">acc. pl.</text:span>): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wanl. = ur huset):</text:span> domus, in qua nihil geratur, quod f. proferendum sit, C.; exi f., Pt.; ire f., Ter.; se dare f., Enn.; spectare, Sen. - telum fertur f., Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŏris</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T4">abl. pl.</text:span>):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ute:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> et intra vallum et f. cædebantur, N.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utomhus; utomlands:</text:span></text:span> f. coenare, C.; f. sapit, animus est alicui, Ter.; parvi sunt f. arma, nisi sit consilium domi, C.; bellum f., seditio domi, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utifrån:</text:span></text:span> f. venire, Lucr.; petere, sumere, quærere, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŏrinsĕcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utifrån; ut:</text:span></text:span> Col., Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Forabilis, Foramen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Foro.<text:line-break/>Foras <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fora.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Forceps,</text:span> cĭpis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m., f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tång; kräftklo:</text:span></text:span> tenax, Vg., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fordus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äfwen</text:span> <text:line-break/>Hordus), <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: bos f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och absol.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Forda</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drägtig ko:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fordĭcīdia</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: (cædo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">offer af</text:span> forda: Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Fore, Forem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sum.<text:line-break/>Forensis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Forum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>ŏrentum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Apulien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Forfex,</text:span> ĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sax:</text:span></text:span> f-e amputare aliquid, Col. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kräftklo:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Forfĭcŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fori (<text:span text:style-name="T4">pl.</text:span>) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Forus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fŏria,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Träck:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŏrĭca</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afträde:</text:span></text:span> Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Foricula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Foris.<text:line-break/>Forinsecus, I. Foris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fora.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Fŏris,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: (foro): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dörr, dörrflygel:</text:span></text:span> tempestas f-em ex æde Lunæ raptam tulit ad -; f-em percutere, L.; exclusus f-e, Hor.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanligare i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">plur.</text:span>: f-es profanarum ædium januæ appellantur; in lateribus equi aēnei f-es erant, quibus apertis -; f-es cubiculi, carceris; f-es aperire, claudere, C.; objicere portarum f-es, L.; effringere, Ter. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> interest - qua commendatione quasi amicitiæ f-es aperiantur, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŏrĭcŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lucka:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Bĭfŏris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som har twenne dörrar l. flyglar:</text:span> argenti b-es radiabant Iumine valvæ, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Quădrĭfŏris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med 4 dörrar:</text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Forma,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Form; figur</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (såsom ett organiskt l. konstgjordt helt, under det</text:span> figura <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">är = bildning, formation i allm.):</text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Form för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, hwari det inneslutes l. hwarefter det formas:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i technisk men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Form, ram, mönster, modell</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngt:</text:span> caseorum, Col.; rivorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wattenledningsrör),</text:span> Front.; ligneæ, Vitr.; sutoris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(läst),</text:span> Hor.; f-æ, in quibus æra funduntur, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Plan, grundritning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för byggnad:</text:span> quum f-am vidi, quale ædificium futurum sit, scire possum, C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Form, plan, mönster, utkast, regel</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (teckning af ngt, affattning):</text:span> quoniam plura sunt orationum genera neque in unam f-am cadunt omnia, laudationum reliquarumque rerum f-am, quæ absunt a forensi contentione, non complectar; f-am totius negotii opinione majorem melioremque video; dare alicui recte loquendi f-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(regel),</text:span> C.; ea f. senatus consulti semper ultimæ necessitatis fuit, L.; naturā quadruplex est f., ad quam in declinando accommodari debeant verba, Varr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Form</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">art; artbegrepp</text:span></text:span> (species, C. Top. XII): innumerabiles sunt quasi f-æ figuræque dicendi; Curio suam quasi f-am dicendi expressit; aliæ causæ aliā f-ā dicendi sunt tractandæ, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wetenskapligt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">System:</text:span></text:span> f. similitudinum, analogiæ, Varr.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Styrelse-, statsform, -författning:</text:span></text:span> f. reipublicæ, civitatis, C.; in provinciæ f-am redigi, Su. <text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mönsterform, -bild, idée (ideal); begrepp:</text:span></text:span> quidquid est, id ad <text:soft-page-break/>ultimam sui generis f-am est redigendum; has rerum f-as ideas appellat Plato; quæ f. et quasi naturalis nota sit cujusque rei, describere; officii f.; f-am et quasi faciem honesti vides; f-am optimi, quæ Græce χαρακτήρ dicitur, exponere; ea oratio Demosthenis profecto in eam f-am, quæ est insita in animis nostris, sic includi potest, ut major eloquentia non requiratur, C.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Form,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som ngt factiskt eger, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">figur, skapnad;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mera oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utseende, företeelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwerhufwud</text:span> (species, figura):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sinlig men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> quinque illæ f-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(materiens grundformer, element),</text:span> e quibus omnia formantur; āer sine ulla f-ā deus esse non potest; situm, f-am, circumscriptionem totius terræ videre; animum per se viventem complecti non poterant, f-am aliquam et figuram requirebant; igneæ illæ f-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kroppar),</text:span> C.; f-a insolita pugna Romanos terruit, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Figur</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i mathematisk men.:</text:span> in geometria lineamenta, f-æ, intervalla, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lefwande warelsers </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gestalt, figur, skapnad;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utseende:</text:span></text:span> nullam partem corporis sine aliqua necessitate affictam totamque f-am quasi perfectam arte reperietis; omnium animantium f-am vincit hominis figura; f-æ figura <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gestaltens daning)</text:span> non venit ab hominibus ad deos; f. habitusque corporis; f. Jovis, Minervæ, leonis, C.; tædet harum quotidianarum f-arum; f. honesta et liberalis; bona; nondum recessit ei f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skönhet),</text:span> Ter.; divitiarum et f-æ gloria fluxa est, Sa.; neglecta f.; per insidias iter est f-asque ferarum, Ov.; f. imperatoria, N.; f-æ hominum et beluarum ambiguæ, T.; ignoti f. viri, Vg.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">specielt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ansigte:</text:span></text:span> f-æ dignitas coloris bonitate tuenda est; omnis ornatus viro non dignus a forma removeatur; natura f-am nostram reliquamque figuram, in qua esset species honesta, posuit in promptu: quæ partes autem - aspectum essent deformem habituræ, eas abdidit, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i osinlig men.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Form, utseende, art, beskaffenhet:</text:span></text:span> non eadem rei f. apud Romanos, L.; ne quære doceri, quæ f. viros fortunaque merserit, Vg.; scripti talis f. fuit; variā pereuntium f-ā et omni imagine mortium, T. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grammatisk </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bildning, form:</text:span></text:span> Varr., Gell. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i rhetorisk men.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>α. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">föredragets rhythmiska </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Form, byggnad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i det stora och hela:</text:span> modus et f. verborum; dixi de singulorum laude verborum, dixi de conjunctione eorum, dixi de numero et f-a (de Or. III. 52); f. ipsa et concinnitas verborum orbem suum conficiet, C.<text:line-break/>β. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Character, art</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med afseende icke blott på det rhythmiska, utan ock sjelfwa stilen och tonen:</text:span> C. Or. §. 134. <text:line-break/>γ. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Figur</text:span></text:span> (σχῆμα): C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formāceus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildad i form, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gjuten:</text:span></text:span> parietes f., qui in forma circumdatis tabulis inferciuntur, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som tjenar till modell, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mönster-:</text:span></text:span> epistola f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(concept),</text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Forma, gestalta, dana:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sinlig men.:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> materiam f-at effectio; ex V primis formis cetera omnia f-antur, C.; classem Aeneas, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om konstwerk: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bilda, skapa; afbilda:</text:span></text:span> Himera urbs in figuram mulieris f-ta; multa sunt verba, quæ nulla similitudine f-ri possint <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för hwilka ingen sinlig bild låter sig finna),</text:span> C.; f-tus cum cornibus Ammon, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bilda, skapa, ordna, inrätta:</text:span></text:span> notiones deorum, C.; omnia ad belli et pacis usus, L.; personam novam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skapa för scenen),</text:span> Hor.; verba, Qu.; epistolas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppsätta),</text:span> Su.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om föredraget: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gifwa form åt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -, rhythmiskt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">forma, bygga:</text:span></text:span> verba sicut ceram mollissimam; f. orationem eamque totam distinguere et variare, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i moralisk och intellectuel men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bilda, dana, leda;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om djur: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">dressera, inöfwa:</text:span></text:span> consuetudinem exercitationis assiduitate, C.; se in mores regis populus f-bat, L.; bovem ad usum agrestem, Vg.; pectus alicujus præceptis amicis, Hor.; dictis f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(instruera)</text:span> alqm, Ov.; studia alicujus, Qu.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stämma:</text:span></text:span> f-at enim natura prius nos intus ad omnem fortunarum habitum -, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Form, skapnad:</text:span></text:span> principiorum, Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Planritning; gestaltning, form:</text:span></text:span> oblonga fori, columnarum, Vitr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Daning, utbildning:</text:span></text:span> morum, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bildare, skapare:</text:span></text:span> universi, Sen.<text:line-break/>2. morum, ingeniorum, Pn., Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formātūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Form:</text:span></text:span> a labrorum f-a verba figurantur, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wälbildad,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till gestalt, wäxt, utseende </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skön:</text:span></text:span> cylindri forma mihi videtur f-ior; virgo, mulier, C.; nun<text:bookmark text:name="_GoBack"/>c f-simus annus; f-ose puer, nimium ne crede colori, Vg.; fis anus et tamen vis f-a videri, Hor.; coma; dies, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skönt:</text:span></text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formōsĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gestaltens skönhet, skön figur:</text:span></text:span> decorum positum est in tribus rebus, f-e, ordine et ornatu ad actionem apto, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formōsŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nätt:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Form, modell, infattning:</text:span></text:span> calcei, Amm.; rivorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wattenledningsrör),</text:span> Front.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mönsterform, fastställd form, regel, ordning, bestämning,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarunder ngt hör l. hwarefter det skall inrättas:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> quid est, quo præscriptum aliquod aut f-am exprimas, quum in suo quidque genere excellat et genera plura sint?; f. est constituenda, quam si sequemur in comparatione rerum, ab officio non recedamus; id abhorret a f-a consuetudinis nostræ, C.; ex f-a vivere, Sen.; hæc f. omnes, excepto sapiente, tenet, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lagbud,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> lagens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">stadgande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bestämning; lagparagraph; laga form, formulär:</text:span></text:span> legulejus, præco actionum, cantor f-arum; f-æ testamentorum, judiciorum, testimoniorum, pacti et conventi, C.; f-am juris exsequendi constituere, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i politisk men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fördrag;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> serskildt de stadgade </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wilkor</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. den </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ställning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett underlydande folk har till det herrskande:</text:span> f. deditionis; quæsierunt ex colonis, ecquid paratos ex f-a milites haberent; in sociorum f-am referri; Thessalorum f-æ facta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= införlifwad med,</text:span> contributa), L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wetenskapligt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">System:</text:span></text:span> certam disciplinæ f-am componere, C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gestalt, utseende:</text:span></text:span> Pt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formŭlārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Formulärkännare (paragraphhäst):</text:span></text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Bĭformātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dubbelgestaltad:</text:span></text:span> b-o impetu Centaurus ictus corpori infixit meo, C. poēt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Bĭformis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som har twå ansigten:</text:span></text:span> Varr.; Janus, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conformo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bilda, inrätta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i öfwerensstämmelse med ngt:</text:span> se ad alicujus voluntatem, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gifwa form, utbilda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt till harmonisk form, till deß rätta gestalt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bilda, dana:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> mundus a natura c-tus, C.; ursa fetum edit informem: lambendo postea c-at et fingit; ova in speciem volucris c-antur, Gell.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> præcepta, quibus usus vitæ in omnes partes c-ri potest; animum, mentem, mores c.; ad majora quædam nos natura genuit et c-vit; oratio c-anda est non solum electione, sed etiam constructione verborum, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conformātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanfogning, -paßning; daning, bildning:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> compositio membrorum, c. lineamentorum; quæ c. animi, quæ magnitudo, qui locus?, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> verborum; vocis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utbildning);</text:span> sententiarum ornamenta et c-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wändningar, figurer),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. animi c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">begrepp,</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēformis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Comp.</text:span> -ior:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wanskaplig, mißbildad, ful:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> motus statusve corporis; nasci d-em; aspectus; res turpiculæ et quasi d-es; adolescens; patria, C.; jumenta prava et d-ia, Cs.; corpus, Sen. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">moraliskt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ful, skamlig, neslig:</text:span></text:span> d-e est de se ipsum prædicare, falsa præsertim, C.; oratio sibi d.; agmen, L.; obsequium, T. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utan kropp:</text:span></text:span> anima, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēformĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mißbildning, wanskaplighet:</text:span></text:span> d. vitiumve corporis, C.; oris, Gell.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fulhet, wanställdhet, otymplighet, smaklöshet:</text:span></text:span> diserti sæpe d-e agendi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i utförandet)</text:span> infantes putati sunt; ad aliquam d-em pravitatemve venire, C.; claudus erat altero pede. Quæ res etiam nonnullam afferebat d-em, N.; noscitabatur tamen in tanta d-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wanställdhet),</text:span> L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förnedring, skam:</text:span></text:span> animæ; fugæ, C.; judicibus d-i fuit rei damnatio, Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēformĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fult, skamligt:</text:span></text:span> Qu., Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēformo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utstaka, forma, afteckna, uppgöra teckning, ritning till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt; äfwen med ord </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">teckna, beskrifwa:</text:span></text:span> areas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rabatter),</text:span> Cato; locum ad <text:soft-page-break/>speciem tabulæ cum capitulo, Varr.; operis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(byggnadens)</text:span> speciem d.; scenas signis, columnis, fastigiis d., Vitr.; ille (orator), quem supra d-vi, C.<text:line-break/>2.<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra wanskaplig, ful; wanställa, -pryda:</text:span></text:span> d-tus corpore, fractus animo; paries nudus et d-tus, C.; macies vultum, Vg.; tonsura capillos, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bringa i oordning, föröda; wanrykta; swärta:</text:span></text:span> Italiam; civitas in omni genere d-ta; ea accusatores hujus (rei) d-andi causa dixerunt, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēformātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Planritning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt:</text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wanärande, förnedring:</text:span></text:span> a d-e tantæ majestatis oculos avertebant, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Informis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Formlös, oformlig:</text:span></text:span> alvei, L.; limus; cadaver, Vg.; apud Germanos neque tegularum nec cæmenti usus: i-i materiā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wirke)</text:span> ad omnia utuntur, T.; caro, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ful, wanställd, oskaplig; wanställande; neslig:</text:span></text:span> monstrum horrendum, i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(oskaplig);</text:span> letum, Vg.; color, Tib.; ager ossibus; situs <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mögel),</text:span> Hor.; facies cruore i., Luc.; Germania i. terris, aspera caelo, tristis cultu aspectuque, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Informo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Forma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i utkast l. till grunddragen), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillskapa; utstaka:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> erat i-tum fulmen, jam parte polita; clypeum, Vg.; quarta hebdomade i-atur caput (fetus), Varr.; areas, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tanken l. phantasien: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bilda, göra sig ett begrepp, en föreställning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om ngt:</text:span> in animis hominum i-tæ sunt notiones deorum; deos ne conjecturā quidem i-re possumus; virtutem i., C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i ord: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra ett utkast af, plan till, teckna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en bild af ngt:</text:span> causa jam ab illo, qui ante dixit, i-ta est; proscriptio generatim i-ta; oratorem talem i-bo, qualis nemo unquam fuit, C.; oratorem, Qu.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">andligen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dana, bilda:</text:span></text:span> animus a natura bene i-tus; artes, quibus pueri ad humanitatem i-antur, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Informātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utkast, planritning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngt:</text:span> ædium, Vitr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">omedelbart </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Begrepp, föreställning:</text:span></text:span> antecepta animo rei i., C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Teckning, antydning,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> allmän </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">beskrifning:</text:span></text:span> unius verbi imagine totius sententiæ i.; verbi descriptio aut i., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Præformo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Forma, teckna för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">på förhand gifwa ett utkast till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> infantibus literas; incipientibus materiam p-tam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(redan disponeradt thema)</text:span> dare, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕformo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Återställa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt till deß </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förra form</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skick:</text:span></text:span> quod ante fuit, r-re, Ov.; aliquid ad aliquid, Sen.; mores, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕformātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Återställande, återupprättande:</text:span></text:span> Ap., Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕformātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Återställare:</text:span></text:span> literarum senescentium, Pn. ep.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Transformis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gestalter skiftande:</text:span></text:span> membra t. adulterat arte Proteus, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Transformo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Omskapa, förskapa, förwandla, -ändra:</text:span></text:span> sese in vultus aniles; naves in stellas, Ov.; animum ad naturam alicujus, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Trĭformis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tregestaltad:</text:span></text:span> diva t. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> Hecate), Hor.; mundus, Ov. Met. XV. 859.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ūnĭformis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> varius): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Enahanda, enskild, likformig:</text:span></text:span> non sufficit, ut ad tempus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för tillfället)</text:span> simplex quiddam et u-e doceamur, T. (Dial. 32); humanum genus, Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ūnĭformĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Enformighet:</text:span></text:span> Mcb. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ūnĭformĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Enformigt:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Formaceus, -malis, -mamentum, Format . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Forma.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>ormiæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Latium.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Formiānus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Formiānum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Ciceros landtställe wid Formiæ.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Formīca,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Myra:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formīcīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: gradus, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formīco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Krypa, kräla; klia:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formīcātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klåda:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formīcōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rik på myror:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formīcŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liten myra:</text:span></text:span> Front.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Formīdo,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fasa, förskräckelse, fruktan, rädsla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för ngt hemskt, dunkelt; ofta om widskeplig, religiös fruktan):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> metus permanens est f.; subita f.; f-em injicere alicui; ignoratione rerum horribiles exsistunt f-es, C.; f-i esse alicui, Sa.; f-em incutere alicui, Ct.; vertêre modum f-e fustis, Hor.; gelida coit f-e sanguis, Vg.; o genus attonitum gelida f-e mortis, Ov.; f. cælestis iræ; silva auguriis patrum et prisca f-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(widskepelse)</text:span> sacra, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">meton.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hemskhet:</text:span></text:span> lucus plenus f-e, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skräckmedel</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (skrämskott); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fasor; spöke</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (skrämma):</text:span> f-es opponere alicui, C.; f. avium furumque Priapus, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt:</text:span> linea <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tråd, garn)</text:span> pennis distincta, quæ feras contineat et in insidias agat, f. dicta est, Sen.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> Vg. Aen. XII. 750. G. III. 372.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formīdo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara rädd, fasa för; rädas, frukta:</text:span></text:span> omnia f.; iracundiam alicujus f.; satietas f-ta est, C.; f-ta Parthis Roma, Hor.; f-do credere: f., ne - arbitretur; f. auro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wara rädd om),</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formīdābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Faslig, förfärlig, fruktanswärd:</text:span></text:span> Orcus; serpens; non f-lis ulli, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formīdāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skrämma, spöke:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Afformīdo</text:span>, 1. = formīdo: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Præformīdo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På förhand frukta:</text:span></text:span> Qu. (inc.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕformīdo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skygga tillbaka, wara ömtålig, rädd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för -, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">frukta, hafwa försyn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för -:</text:span> insuetum solem lumina <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ögon),</text:span> Ov.; reprehensionem vulgi; crimen amicitiæ; bellum; vide, quam non r-em; refugit animus et ea dicere r-at, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕformīdātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tillbakaskyggande), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Försagdhet, betänklighet:</text:span></text:span> deliberantis, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formīdŏlōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rädd, försagd, förskrämd:</text:span></text:span> homo, Ter.; mancipium, Varr.; boves ad ingrediendum flumen, Col. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hemsk, förfärlig, fruktanswärd:</text:span></text:span> tempora dubia et f-a; bellum f-simum; locus, C.; loca foeda, tetra, f-a, Sa.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Formīdŏlōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hemskt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ett sätt, som är egnadt att skrämma:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Försagdt:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Performīdŏlōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mycket rädd:</text:span></text:span> Aur. Vict.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Formo, Formos . . ., Formul . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Forma.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Formus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: vox obsoleta: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Het</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af</text:span> ferveo): Paul. Diac.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fornax,</text:span> ācis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ugn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (masugn, bakugn o. s. w.):</text:span> calcaria, Cato; ardentes, C.; (ferraria), Lucr.; æraria, Pn.; f-e temperantur fruges; Aetnæ f-es, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fornācālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ugnens, till ugn hörande:</text:span> deæ f-i sunt sua sacra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ugnens gudomlighet, äfwen kallad</text:span> Fornax), Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fornācālia</text:span>, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ugnsfesten</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i Februari månad:</text:span> Ov. Fast. II. 527. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fornācŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fornix,</text:span> ĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hwalf, hwalfbåge,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> så wäl en fristående (triumphbåge), som = hwälfdt tak l. hwälfdt rum; spec. = byggnad med hwälfdt tak, källare, jordwåning:</text:span> ædes, intercolumnium, f.; f. Fabii <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(triumphbåge på forum),</text:span> C.; scortum in f-e stans, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fornĭcātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hwälfd, med hwalf:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fornĭcātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hwalfbyggnad:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confornĭco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hwälfwa, slå hwalf:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fŏro,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> foris): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra hål i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">genomborra:</text:span></text:span> aurem; arborem, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŏrābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som kan genomborras, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomtränglig:</text:span></text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŏrāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hål, öppning:</text:span></text:span> f-a, quæ patent ad animum a corpore, i. e. aures, oculi et cet., C.; f. tibiæ, Hor.; fistulæ, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumfŏrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rundtomkring borrad:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effŏrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utborrad:</text:span></text:span> truncus, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infŏro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Borra:</text:span></text:span> truncum, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfŏro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomborra, borra; genombryta, genomtränga:</text:span></text:span> navem; viæ sunt p-tæ ab animæ sede ad oculos; ex cubiculo Stabianum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(göra en uthuggning mot St.),</text:span> C.; latus ense, Ov.; sol omnia p., St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Transfŏro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomborra:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>ŏrojūliensis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är från</text:span> Forum Julii <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(se</text:span> I. Forum).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Forpex,</text:span> ĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tång:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fors,</text:span> fortis, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl. blott i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">nom.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">abl.</text:span> forte, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> fero, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liksom</text:span> sors <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> sero, mons <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> mineo, pons <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> pendo?):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blind</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> rörelse l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fart:</text:span></text:span> nos f-e suā tempestas his appulit oris, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl. = händelsernas gång, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slump, öde, händelse, tillfällighet;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> äfwen personificerad såsom gudomlighet:</text:span> quod f. ferat, feramus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bära);</text:span> f. id mihi attulit; f-e fortuna unā affuit amicus, Ter.; vosne velit an me regnare hera quidve ferat F., virtute experiamur, Enn. ap. C.; F. domina campi (ɔ: comitiorum); ut f. tulit; f. in talibus rebus plus, quam ratio, potest, C.; falso queritur de natura sua genus humanum, quod imbecilla et brevis ævi f-e potius quam virtute regatur, Sa.; eum primum locum f. obtulit, N.; f-e quadam divinitus Tiberis super ripas effusus erat; f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tillfälle)</text:span> se dare visa est imperii recuperandi; ædem Fortis Fortunæ ex manubiis faciendam locare, L.; fatone res mortales et immutabili necessitate an f-e reguntur?, T.; nulla tibi me f. obtulit, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af detta ord brukas såsom adverbia:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T4">nom.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fors</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kanhända:</text:span></text:span> f. et debita jura vicesque superbæ te maneant ipsum, Hor.; f. et poenas reposcent, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Af en händelse:</text:span></text:span> f. cessit victoria Turno, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T4">abl.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Forte</text:span>: <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ensamt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Af en händelse, tillfälligtwis, just</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (då för tillfället):</text:span> f. evenit, ut in Privernati essemus; f. adsedimus in Tiburti ego et Marcus filius, C.; f. incidit de uxoribus mentio; f. in duobus exercitibus erant trigemini fratres; ibi f. stipendium militibus dabatur, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med uttryck för förmodan l. medgifwande, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Möjligtwis),</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> efter</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">si, nisi, ne</text:span>: aa. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> si f., ut fit plerumque, ceciderint, tum intelligitur, amicos iis nullos fuisse; propensior benignitas esse debebit in calamitosos, ni si f. erunt digni calamitate; videndum est in vita, ne f. quid discrepet, C.; ne f. credas interitura, quæ loquor-; ne f. viriles partes mandentur puero, - in adjunctis aevoque morabimur aptis, Hor.<text:line-break/>bb. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">elliptiskt:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">si f.</text:span>: (alicujus) supplosionem pedis imitari et pauca verba et alqm, si f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i bästa fall),</text:span> motum; si opulentum defenderis, in uno illo aut, si forte, in liberis manet gratia, C. - cc. <text:span text:style-name="T4">nisi f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utom för det fallet, att</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Om ej kanhända; men kanhända,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ironiskt i wederläggning:</text:span> nisi f. ego vobis nunc cessare videor, cum bella non gero, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Forsan</text:span> (fors, an), <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det är en möjlighet (om), att</text:span> -]: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Möjligtwis, kanske:</text:span></text:span> f. verum sermonem antiqui auctores tradiderint (<text:span text:style-name="T4">conj.</text:span>), L. (IlI. 47. 5); f. et hæc olim meminisse juvabit, Vg.; et mihi f., tibi quod negarit, porriget hora, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Forsit</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Forsĭtan</text:span> (fors sit, an), <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Möjligtwis, törhända, kanhända, kanske, tilläfwentyrs</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hos de bättre författarne alltid med verbet i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">conj.</text:span>): forsit mihi honorem invideat, Hor. (semel) -; f. ea mendacia sunt, Pt.; iis f. concedendum sit rempublicam non capessentibus, qui excellenti ingenio doctrinæ se tradiderunt; f. quæratis; f. dixerit quispiam; videor mihi liberius pro Siculis dicere, quam f. ipsi velint, C.; dictis dabit ipsa fidem res f., Lucr.; f. et, Priami fuerint quæ fata, requiras, Vg.; f. tacerem, si -; f. et publica, sua certe liberata fide, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fortan</text:span> = Forsitan, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fortasse</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fortassis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.</text:span> = forsitan, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">men med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">indic.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">conj.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tilläfwentyrs, törhända:</text:span></text:span> f. metuis, Pt.; longiorem orationem f. causa postulabat; dicam, quod f. nemo vestrum audierit; riserit aliquis f. hoc præceptum; dicam incondite f., sed ut res possit intelligi; ego f. vaticinor et hæc meliores habebunt exitus, C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">acc. c. inf.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Det kanhända</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> att:</text:span> f. te æs dicere, Pt. Truc. III. 2. 12.<text:line-break/>3. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På sin höjd, ungefär:</text:span></text:span> versus f. triginta; biennio f. major, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fortassean</text:span> = fortasse: Varr., Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fortuītus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillfällig, af ödet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">händelsen tillskickad:</text:span></text:span> effectum esse caelum ac terram nulla cogente natura, sed concursu (atomorum) f-o, C.; casus et eventus rerum plerumque f-i sunt; mors f., T.; cæspitem f-um spernere leges non sinebant, Hor.; f-orum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(oförmodade händelser)</text:span> capax mare, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oförberedd:</text:span></text:span> oratio, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fortuīto</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fortuītu</text:span>, Pt.), <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Af en händelse; tillfälligtwis, utan afsigt:</text:span></text:span> f. in vestrum sermonem incidi; verbum excidit f., C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blindwis, utan att tänka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">se sig före:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span> ne quid temere ac f., inconsiderate et negligenter agamus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fortūna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wäl egentl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adj.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lycklig, lyckosam,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i förbindelsen:</text:span> Fors Fortuna <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fors.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="T4">Subst.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lyckan,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm. såsom makt, l.</text:span> in abstr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ödet, slumpen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ödets nyck), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">omständigheterna:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. magna vis est in f-ā vel ad secundas res vel ad adversas; quid aliud est f., nisi quum quid ita evenit, ut vel aliter evenire potuerit?; ea sunt in casu et f-a sita; f-æ varietas, temeritas; natura multo et firmior et constantior est, quam f.; f. mortalis cum immortali natura pugnare videtur; cum f-a bellum restabat; a f-a vulnus accipere; multa patent in eorum vita, quæ f. feriat; sunt illa omnia dona f-æ; eandem in utroque potestatem habuit f., usa est in altero; nulli f-æ succumbere, C.; profecto f. in omni re dominatur; sævit, Sa.; a f-a deseri; f-æ gratiam habere, Cs.; non poterat majora consequi, quam vel f. vel natura tribuerat; f. suā mobilitate, quem extulerat, demergere est conata, N.; aspirat primo f. labori, Vg.; f-æ filius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lyckans son);</text:span> f-æ rivus inaurat alqm, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med utförd personification, gudinnan </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fortuna:</text:span></text:span> L. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt dyrkad i Antium,</text:span> Hor. Od. I. 37; nullum numen habes, si sit prudentia, nos te, nos facimus, Fortuna, deam cæloque locamus, Juv.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">någons </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lycka,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> god l. dålig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lycka, öde, lott, ställning:</text:span></text:span> f. florens, prospera, secunda; adversa, dura; ejusmodi multa et varia in hominum vita f-aque versantur; ejus laudatur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(prisas)</text:span> f.; Metelli sibi sperat quisque f-am, C.; pari usus f-ā; non simplex (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wexlande);</text:span> nullam sejunctam ab amico voluit f-am, N.; f. misera, gravis, repentina; f-am periclitari, tentare, experiri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(pröfwa, fresta),</text:span> Cs.; <text:soft-page-break/>bona; miseranda; simul cum moribus f. mutatur; vicit f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(goda lycka)</text:span> reipublicæ, Sa.; imperium in paucorum hominum virtute ac f-ā positum; patriæ, L.; f. dulcis; æqua; manca; magna, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="T4">plur.</text:span>: in amplissimis f-is mori, C.; omnes f-as meas laudabant, Ter.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">någons sociala l. borgerliga </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ställning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i afseende på stånd och förmögenhet, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">samhällsställning, stånd, wilkor:</text:span></text:span> in maximā f-ā minima licentia; supra f-am animum gerere; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">plur.</text:span>: utinam emori meis f-is (regis) honestus exitus esset, Sa.; præstantiam aliquam virtutis, ingenii, f-æ consequi; spes amplificandæ f-æ; infima est condicio et f. servorum; in hominibus juvandis aut mores aut f. spectari solet, C.; pro f-a quisque hospites accipit, T.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">plur.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">så wäl serskildt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förmögenhet, egendom,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som = ngns hela </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wälfärd,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> exsistens:</text:span> salutem, liberos, f-as suas committere alicui; hunc animum malim, quam omnes istorum f-as; pecuniā nostra f-is contentus sit, vitam ne petat; in me præsidium f-is suis positum esse arbitrantur; causam sociorum f-asque provinciæ defendere; me socii f-arum suarum defensorem esse voluerunt, C.; ex alienis f-is liberalem esse; regno me f-isque omnibus Jugurtha expulit; f-as suas in extremo sitas vidit, Sa.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lycka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">god lycka:</text:span></text:span> quo mihi f-am, si non conceditur uti?, Hor.; socii penates, dum f. fuit -, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fortūno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wälsigna:</text:span></text:span> tibi rem dii f-ent, C.; tu, quamcunque deus tibi f-verit horam, gratā sume manu, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fortūnātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lycklig; säll, lycksalig:</text:span></text:span> haberi f-simum; exitus; nihil insipiente f-o intolerabilius, C.; f-um species et gratia præstat, Hor.; f-us et ille, deos qui novit agrestes; f. laborum; f-orum insulæ, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rik, mäktig:</text:span></text:span> homo f. et nobilis; inopis et optimi viri causæ anteponere gratiam f-i et po - tentis, C.; ingenium arte f-ius putat Democritus, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fortūnāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lyckligt:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infortūnātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Olycklig:</text:span></text:span> senex, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infortūnĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Olycka:</text:span></text:span> Gell. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infortūnium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mißöde, olycka:</text:span></text:span> i-o mactare alqm; invenire, Pt.; ferre <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(röna),</text:span> Ter.; filium, ni pareat patri, i. habiturum, L.; tunc tua me i-a lædent, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Forsan, Forsit, Forsitan, Fortan, -tasse, -tassis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fors.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fortax,</text:span> ācis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spisgrund, arne:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Forte <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fors.<text:line-break/>Forticulus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fortis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fortis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kraftig, uthållig, rask:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kroppsligen (stark, dugtig, frisk):</text:span> familia, Pt.; ad opera f., Col.; coloni; tauri; equi, Vg.; filium filiamque f-es invenire, Pn.; vires f-es, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till sinnelag och character: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kraftig, rask, fast, manlig, karlawulen, modig, oförskräckt:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. om personer:</text:span> arator f. et experiens; animus f. et magnus duabus rebus cernitur; f-is et constantis est non perturbari in rebus <text:soft-page-break/>asperis; vir contra audaciam ad pericula; sententiæ; impetus animi; genus orationis; oratio diserta et oratoria, non f. et virilis; f-es fortuna (juvat), C.; ut virum f-em <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(en karl)</text:span> decet, Ter.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt i fråga om krig: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tapper, hjeltemodig:</text:span></text:span> f-es et magnanimi habendi sunt, non qui inferunt, sed qui propulsant injuriam; f. in proelio; adolescens f-simus; vir f-simus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hjelte);</text:span> rebus imbellibus dolent f-es, C.; manu f., consilii plenus, N.; f-ia facta, L.; f. arma, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fortĭcŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ironiskt: liten hjelte :</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fortĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med kraft, med fart; raskt; manligt, modigt, fast; tappert:</text:span></text:span> astringere aliquid, Pt.; facere;. ferre <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fördraga)</text:span> aliquid; f-sime perseverare, C.; sustinere impetum hostium, Cs.; f. occupa portum, Hor.; f. ausa, Vg.; mittit in Euboicas tormento f. undas, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfortĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mycket raskt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">manligt:</text:span></text:span> Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fortĭtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kroppslig styrka, friskhet:</text:span></text:span> hircorum, Phdr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mod att lida</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">handla, sinnesstyrka; mannamod, manhaftighet, tapperhet:</text:span></text:span> f. est affectio animi in patiendo ac perferendo summæ legi pārens; f-is est - nihil, quod homini accidere possit, intolerandum putare; f. in periculis, labor in negotiis; f-em virtutem esse dicunt propugnantem pro æquitate, C.; Helvetii pro gloria f-is angustos fines se habere arbitrabantur, Cs. - <text:span text:style-name="T4">plur.</text:span>: sunt domesticæ f-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(behjertade handlingar i fred)</text:span> non inferiores bellicis, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fortuit . . ., Fortun . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fors.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>ŏrŭli, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sabinsk stad.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. Foruli <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Forus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Fŏrum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> foras <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> foris; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> forensis): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öppen, fri plats:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i städer, tjenande</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Torg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. försäljningsplats, t. ex. i Rom</text:span> f. boarium, f. olitorium, f. piscarium,<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom medelpunkt för affärslifwet och det offentliga lifwet</text:span> (in foro et publicarum et privatarum rerum rationes per magistratus gubernantur, Vitr.); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">så i Rom det nedanför Capitolium belägna s. k. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Forum Romanum</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. blott </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Forum,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwilket war omgifwet af wexlarebodar, localer för auctioner</text:span> (atria auctionaria), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för lagskipning</text:span> (basilicæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i grekisk stil sedan Catos tid), för förwaltning</text:span> (ærarium, tabularium) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">samt senatssammanträden</text:span> (curiæ), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och der folkmöten och tal till folket (från</text:span> rostra) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">höllos. Enahanda bestämmelse hade det af portiker, basilicor, curiæ m. fl. offentliga byggnader omgifna stora forum i Pompeji och i Rom de s. k. kejsarefora. I äldre tider höllos också</text:span> ludi gladiatorii <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på forum (jfr</text:span> Vitr. V. 1). <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Från denna fori centrala betydelse i romerskt stadslif härleda sig följande talsätt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. scisti uti f-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sköta dina affärer),</text:span> Ter.; ratio pecuniarum, quæ in f-o versatur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(cursen);</text:span> versari in f-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(drifwa affärer),</text:span> C.; cedere f-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(göra </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bankrutt),</text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med afseende på rättegångswäsende och politiska förhandlingar):</text:span> ne semper f., subsellia, rostra curiamque meditere; f. et jurisdictionem cum ferro et armis conferatis; extra suum f. vadimonium promittere, C.; f. litigiosum, Ov.; f. litibus orbum, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">göromål på forum; lagskipning, ting:</text:span></text:span> obrui ambitione et f-o; f. agere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hålla),</text:span> C.; indicere, Vg.; - in f-um venire, f-um attingere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(börja att uppträda såsom talare l. i allm. i det offentliga),</text:span> C.; in f-o esse coepit; de f-o decessit, N. <text:line-break/>c. f. ornatum ludorum causa, C., L. <text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Torg-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> och </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tingsplats</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på landet; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">köping:</text:span></text:span> per omnia f-a et conciliabula supplicationes indicere, L. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">häraf namn på flere orter, som sedermera uppwuxit till städer:</text:span> F. Flaminium, Aurelium, Livii <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Forli),</text:span> Julii <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Frejus; jfr</text:span> Forojuliensis) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">m. fl.</text:span><text:line-break/>III. forum (sepulcri) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl.</text:span> C. = vestibulum sepulcri, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den frie platsen framför ett grafställe.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŏrensis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i mots. till</text:span> domesticus: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som är, sker, brukas utomhus; yttre:</text:span></text:span> vestitus f., L.; res publicæ, privatæ, domesticæ, f-es, C.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utländsk:</text:span></text:span> sermo exoticus et f., Ap.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som wistas på torget l. i allm. i staden:</text:span> factio, L.; Fauni caveant, ne velut innati triviis et pæne f-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stadsboar) -,</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T4">forum</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hörande, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T4">forum</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> förekommande; som hör till forum; hörande till l. förekommande i det borgerliga, offentliga, embets- l. statsmannalifwet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">borgerlig, offentlig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> så wäl:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> turba et barbaria f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på forum);</text:span> f-es disceptationes judiciorum aut deliberationum; infinitus rerum f-ium labor; consuetudo dicendi popularis et f., C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt: som hör till </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rättegångs-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">domstolswäsende:</text:span></text:span> cancelli f-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(omkring tribunalet);</text:span> oratio judicialis et f.; instrumentum hoc f-e, litigiosum, acre - exiguum saneque mendicum est; loci graves ex philosophia, abhorrentes ab hoc usu f-i et publico; sine judiciali asperitate et sine sententiarum f-bus aculeis, C.; opera f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(såsom patronus),</text:span> N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumfŏrāneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: æs c-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som är i rörelsen på forum, lånadt af wexlarne wid forum);</text:span> pharmacopola c., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kringstrykande qwacksalfware, som besöker</text:span> fora = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">marknader,</text:span> C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> domus, hostia, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som flyttas, bäres omkring,</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Fŏrum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ho, kärl,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som anwändes wid winpreßning:</text:span> lectius vinum defertur in f. vinarium, unde in dolium inane veniat, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Fŏrus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">plur.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gång</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på däcket af ett skepp emellan roddarnes bänkar, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">däck:</text:span></text:span> per f-os cursare, C.; laxat f-os, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rader</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af sittplatser på circus, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(loger):</text:span></text:span> L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sängar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i en trädgård:</text:span> Col. <text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Celler, afdelningar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i en bikupa:</text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Fŏrus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(l.</text:span> Forum?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spelbräde:</text:span></text:span> tesserā et f-o funeris mala levare, Sen.; f-um aleatorium calfecimus, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŏrŭli</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bokhyllor</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skåp:</text:span></text:span> libros dabit et f-os mediamque Minervam, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>ōsi, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">germaniskt folkslag.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Foss . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fodio.<text:line-break/>Fotus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Foveo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fŏvea,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Graf; grop</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till att fånga wilddjur):</text:span> f-is abscondere (cadavera bestiarum), Vg.; fera incidit in f-am, C.; cautus lupus metuit f-am, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fŏveo,</text:span> fōvi, fōtum, 2.:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rufwa;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: genom meddelande af kroppslig wärme </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hålla warm, uppfriska, lifwa:</text:span></text:span> aves pullos exclusos - pennis f-ent, ne frigore lædantur; matres, a quibus pulli exclusi fotique sunt, C.; ova plumis matrum f-da dabat, Ov.; ursi fetus apprimendo pectori f-ent, Pn. <text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rufwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">beständigt ligga på, i:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> progeniem nidumque apes; larem; humum serpens; castra, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> hiemem luxu f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sofwa bort),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Taga i skötet, omfamna:</text:span></text:span> inimicum meum osculabantur et f-bant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bildl.),</text:span> C.; gremio, sinu alqm, Vg.; aperto pectore nomen, Ov. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wärma, uppwärma:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> focus dicitur, quia f-et omnia, Ov.; epulas foculo, Pt. <text:line-break/>b. medullas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hjerta)</text:span> igne, Ov.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bada, skölja, belägga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bestryka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt wärmande l. wederqwickande:</text:span> dolores <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(liksom lägga kylande omslag på),</text:span> C.; vulnus lymphā; ora haustu aquarum; rimosa cubilia apium limo, Vg.; alveus accipit artus f-dos; aura hortum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(smeker),</text:span> Ov.; cutem lacte asinino, Pn. <text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Omhulda, hylla, gynna, uppmuntra, befordra, underhålla; hysa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om meningar o. d.):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med personl. object:</text:span> Hortensium, C.; pugnantes certa spe, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med sakliga object:</text:span> sensus hominum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(smickra);</text:span> amorem alicujus f. et augere, C.; patrum voluntatem; rem Romanam, L.; hoc regnum dea gentibus esse - tenditque f-etque <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(önskar);</text:span> spem inanem f., Vg.; vota, Ov.; alias partes, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fōmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Omslag, förband, plåster:</text:span></text:span> adhibere, Col.; f-a vulnus non levantia, Hor.; vulneribus nulla f-a, T. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lindrande medel; lugnande, kylande medel:</text:span></text:span> doloris, Pn.; frigida curarum f-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som afkyla hans ifwer för högre sträfwanden),</text:span> Hor.; militaribus animis adhibenda f-a, ut ferre pacem velint, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fōmes</text:span>, ĭtis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det, hwarmed ngt antändes:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Torrt träd, fnöske, tunder:</text:span></text:span> arida nutrimenta igni circumdedit rapuitque in f-e flammam, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upphof, anledning:</text:span></text:span> Gell., Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fōtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Påbadning:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confŏveo</text:span>, fōvi, fōtum, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wärma; wederqwicka:</text:span></text:span> Col., Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfŏveo</text:span>, fōvi, fōtum, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åter uppwärma, upplifwa, stärka, wederqwicka:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> artus igne, Ct.; vires, Vell.; agrum stercoratione, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> studia prope exstincta r., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frăces,</text:span> um, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grums i olja; drägg:</text:span></text:span> Cato, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frăcesco</text:span>, frăcui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Murkna, bli mör:</text:span></text:span> olea, Varr.; terra, Cato.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frăcĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mör, halfrutten:</text:span></text:span> olea, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confrăcesco</text:span>, frăcui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ruttna upp:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fract . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Frango.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frāga,</text:span> ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smultron:</text:span></text:span> humi nascentia, Vg.; montana f. legere, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fragil . . ., Fragm . . ., Fragor, Fragos . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Frango.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frāgro,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dofta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lukta wäl):</text:span> casiā cinnamoque, Mt.; redolent thymo f-tia mella, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frāgranter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frāgrantia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Doft:</text:span></text:span> unguentorum, Val. M.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frămea,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(germaniskt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spjut, lans:</text:span></text:span> hastas vel ipsorum vocabulo f-as gerunt, angusto et brevi ferro, sed ita acri et ad usum habili, ut eodem telo - vel cominus vel eminus pugnent, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frango,</text:span> frēgi, fractum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bryta, bräcka, knäcka, sönderslå; krossa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> navem f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lida skeppsbrott),</text:span> Ter.; brachium; anulum aureum; cervices alicujus; ova; nuces, C.; fasces f-untur a multitudine, L.; caules alieni horti, Hor.; fluctus a saxo f-untur, C.; fruges f. saxo, Vg.; aliquid in micas, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">factiskt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förswaga, kufwa, krossa, nedslå:</text:span></text:span> calor se f-it; nationem f. et domare; Viriathum Lælius fregit et comminuit; sententiam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wederlägga);</text:span> consilium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(omintetgöra),</text:span> C.; vires, opes alicujus; hostem, N.; diem mero; f-tus membra labore, Hor.; morbum, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bryta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sitt ord o. d.:</text:span> fidem; foedus, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till modet) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedslå, besegra, beweka, röra:</text:span></text:span> contumelia non fregit eum, sed erexit, N.; animus f-itur; f-i dolore, metu; Plato, ut rationem nullam afferret, auctoritate sua me f-ret <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skulle öfwertyga),</text:span> C.; fletus virum f-bat, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fractus</text:span>, -ior, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bruten, ledbruten, slapp; nedslagen, modfälld:</text:span></text:span> ætas, Lucr.: quid est tam f-um, tam minutum, tam in ipsa concinnitate puerile?, C.; in compositione verborum f-um, Qu.; animus; spes amplificandæ fortunæ f-ior, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fractūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Brott</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (brytning):</text:span> cruris, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frăgĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som lätt brytes, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bräcklig, skör:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> saccharon dentibus, Pn.; rami, Vg.; rates, Hor.; glacies, Ov.; penna f-ior, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = swag, förgänglig:</text:span> f-e corpus animus sempiternus movet; res humanæ f-es et caducæ sunt; o fallacem hominum spem f-emque fortunam!, C.; formæ gloria fluxa et f. est, Sa.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frăgĭlĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skörhet, bräcklighet, förgänglighet, swaghet:</text:span></text:span> ferri; turis, Pn.; humani generis, C.; humana, Ct., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fragmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fragmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">afbrutet l. lösryckt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stycke, bit, spillra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt (wanl. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pl.</text:span>): ingens montis f-en; f-ina remorum, Vg.; rami, silvarum f-ina, Lucr.; lapidis f-tum aut gleba, nulla cohærendi natura <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> arbor, in qua est artis similitudo); sæptorum f-ta, C.; ramorum f-ta, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frăgor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sönderbrytande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (delning); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sprängning, remnande:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Brak, dån, sorl:</text:span></text:span> terra quasi f-e et sonitu hostium adventus significat, C.; tectorum, quæ diruebantur, L.; nubes dat fissa f-em, Lucr.; totus cecidit pelagi f., Vg.; sternitur et propulsa dat f-em silva, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frăgōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Full af springor, klyftor; oländig, stenbunden; ojemn:</text:span></text:span> f-a sunt corpore raro, Lucr.; silva, Ov.; vada, Vfl.; aures f-is offenduntur, lævibus mulcentur, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sorlande, dånande:</text:span></text:span> torrens, Vg.; venti, Vfl.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frăgōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med dån:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Affrango</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Affringo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bryta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">emot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> ungues postibus, St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Anfractum</text:span> <text:line-break/>(amfractum), i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: (amb-fractum): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Krökning:</text:span></text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Anfractus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Krökning, bugt, swängning, slingring; krokwäg, omwäg:</text:span></text:span> (circuli) figura nihil habet - a-bus incisum, C.; anguis, St.; litoris, montis, L., Pn.; a-ūs viarum, L.; via habet a-um; (is) capit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tager)</text:span> a-um, N.<text:line-break/>b. solis a-us reditusque, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wändning på sin bana, omlopp,</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kringswängning; omswep, omwäg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i tal l. handlingssätt:</text:span> oratio sit circumscripta non longo a-u <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(period),</text:span> sed ad spiritum vocis apto; quid opus est circuitione et a-u, ut sit utendum somniorum interpretibus?, C.; juris a., Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confringo</text:span>, frēgi, fractum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bryta; slå sönder och samman; spränga, krossa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> navis in alto acta c-itur, Pt.; hirneam, Cato; digitos, C.; claustra portarum; turres, Luc.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> consilia senatoria vi sua, C.; hostium vires, Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confrăgus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppbruten, -sprängd), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spärrad, snåruppfylld:</text:span></text:span> dumetum, Luc.; c-a silvæ, St.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confrăgōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Söndersprängd;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om mark) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">oländig, ojemn, stenbunden:</text:span></text:span> ager, Varr.; locus lapidibus, Col.; loca, via, L. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ojemn, skroflig, beswärlig:</text:span></text:span> versus velut c., Qu.; condiciones, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēfringo</text:span>, frēgi, fractum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bryta af, itu:</text:span></text:span> crura, Pt.; pedem; ramum arboris, surculum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Diffringo</text:span>, frēgi, fractum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bryta i sönder; slå i stycken:</text:span></text:span> crura, Pt.; basin Apollinis, Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effringo</text:span>, frēgi, fractum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bryta upp, spränga:</text:span></text:span> fores, C., N.; thesaurum, Pn.; cistam e-tam queri, Hor.; cerebrum alicujus, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effractārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som bryter upp dörrar, gör inbrottsstöld:</text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infringo</text:span>, frēgi, fractum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bräcka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (genom inböjning), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">knäcka, bryta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> remus i-tus, C.; arundinem; telum, Vg.; liminibus lumbos et crura i., Hor., unda i-itur, St. - colaphum alicui i-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(”smälla” ngn en örfil),</text:span> Ter.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> lingua alicujus i-itur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förlamas),</text:span> Lucr.; spem, gloriam alicujus; est hujus sæculi labes virtuti invidere, florem ipsum dignitatis i.; cedere cogere et propemodum i.; Drusi tribunatus i-i et debilitari videbatur, C.; vim militum; conatus alicujus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(omintetgöra),</text:span> Cs.; animos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(nedslå),</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infractus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bruten, wanmäktig, nedslagen, modfälld:</text:span></text:span> furor tuus i. inanes faciebat impetus; non modo non i-o animo, sed etiam confirmato, C.; i-i adverso Marte Latini defecerunt, Vg.; i-a partium fama, T.; oratio summissa et i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ynkligt),</text:span> L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om tal och röst: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Styckad, bruten, swäfwande:</text:span></text:span> (numerum orationis fugientes) i-a et amputata loquuntur, C.; nutricis blanda et i-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stammande)</text:span> loquela, Lucr.; oratione nulla ex parte i-ore concionatus est, Val.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infractio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: animi i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. brytning, brutenhet), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klenmodighet:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infrăgĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Obrytlig:</text:span></text:span> adamas, Pn.; animus, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Interfringo</text:span>, frēgi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bryta af</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för ngn, ngn till förfång):</text:span> si quid ventus i-erit, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Offringo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bryta på twären), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På twären genomplöja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> de uppkastade jordklimparne, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">twära:</text:span></text:span> o-itur terra, glebæ o-untur, quum iterum transverso sulco aratur, Fs., Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfringo</text:span>, frēgi, fractum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genombryta, spränga, bryta (sig) igenom:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> saxum, C.; phalangem hostium; munitiones; angustias et tela vi et virtute, Cs.; glaciem dolabris, Ct.; boves et aratra campos, Pn.; jumenta p-bant (nives), L.; pectora, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spränga; wåldföra; beweka:</text:span></text:span> repagula juris, pudoris, officii; jus civile nec inflecti gratiā nec p-i potentiā potest; judicum religionem et veritatem p.; leges, judicia, decreta; animos, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Præfringo</text:span>, frēgi, fractum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På spetsen afbryta, toppbryta, twärbryta:</text:span></text:span> caulem, Cato; rostrum, Cs.; hastam, L.; pinum, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Præfractus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i tänke- eller handlingssätt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twär, hänsigtslös, pedantisk:</text:span></text:span> Aristo ferreus et p., C.; Charondæ justitia p-ior, Val.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i framställningens form: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twärbruten, ej rundad:</text:span></text:span> orator, C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Præfracte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twärt, hänsigtslöst:</text:span></text:span> Cato nimis p. ærarium defendit, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōfringo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bräcka framåt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppbryta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med plogen; jfr</text:span> proscindo): St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfringo</text:span>, frēgi, fractum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppbryta, -bräcka; spränga:</text:span></text:span> cellam, Pt.; portas, Enn., Cs.; claustra, C.; carcerem, L.; ramum Aeneas, Vg.; glebam, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bryta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i farten), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hämma:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> vim fluminis, Cs.; radii solis r-untur, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> Atheniensium dominationem, N.; Priami domus Hectoreis opibus Achivos r-egit, Hor.; occæcat animos fortuna, ubi vim suam ingruentem i-gi non vult, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfractārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gensträfwig, styf:</text:span></text:span> contumax et r., Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfractāriŏlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Något styf:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Suffringo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Krossa, sönderslå under</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> talos, crura alicui, Pt., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frāter,</text:span> tris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Broder:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> germanus f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(köttslig),</text:span> Pt., C.; f-es gemini, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T4">pl.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Syskon:</text:span></text:span> T.<text:line-break/>b. = f. patruelis, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">syskonbarn på fädernet,</text:span> C.; f. erat (Achilles mihi, sc. Ajaci), Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom wänligt tilltalsord l. såsom officiel hederstitel för bundsförwandter:</text:span> f., pater adde: ut cuique est ætas, ita quemque facetus adopta, Hor. - Aedui, f-es populi Romani, C., Cs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frātercŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kär broder:</text:span></text:span> C., Juv.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frātercŭlo</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">1.:</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wäxa upp som twillingbröder, oeg.:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frāternus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Broder tillhörig, broders-, brödra-:</text:span></text:span> hereditas, parricidium, C.; cædes f.; Erycis fines f-i, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Broderlig:</text:span></text:span> amor, C.; animi, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frāterne</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Broderligt, som det anstår en broder:</text:span></text:span> epistolæ non f. scriptæ f. debes ignoscere, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frāternĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Broderskap, brödraskap:</text:span></text:span> usurpare nomen f-is, T.; f-is affectus, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frātria</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Brors hustru; swägerska:</text:span></text:span> Non.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frātrĭcīda</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: (cædo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Brodermördare:</text:span></text:span> C., N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fraud . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fraus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fraus,</text:span> fraudis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: [<text:line-break/>(frus) frudi, Lucr <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> Frustra)]:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bedrägeri, swek</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hwarigenom ngn förfördelas, ej får sin rätt); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">försåt, snara, fälla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i oeg. men.):</text:span> in f-em illicere, Ter.; - duobus modis, aut vi aut f-e, fit in juria; facere alicui f-em; is fons est f-ium, maleficiorum, scelerum omnium; delabi, incidere in f-em; impellere alqm in f-em, C.; f-e ac dolo aggredi alqm, L.; sine f-e se dedere, Cs.; ne sit tibi frudi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(må det bedraga dig),</text:span> Lucr.; f-em alicui incogitare, Hor.; f-e petere aliquem; f. innexa clienti, Vg.; pia f., Ov.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förfång, men:</text:span></text:span> f-em facere alicui; id mihi f-em tulit, f-i fuit, C.; quod sine f-e mea populique Romani fiat, L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Brott, ondska; skuld:</text:span></text:span> f-em capitalem admisit, qui contra - arma tulit; f-em hominum ad perniciem vocare; f-is poenas dii in diem reservant; republica violanda inexpiabiles f-es concipere, C.; f-em capitalem audere; ne cui f-i esset <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(räknas till last)</text:span> concivisse plebem ad repetendam libertatem, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fraudo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hos</text:span> Pt. 3. frausus sit):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swika</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wanl. i handel och wandel) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(preja), bedraga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">genom swek beröfwa:</text:span></text:span> spe f-andi sublata solvendi necessitas consequebatur; socium, pupillum; alqm per societatem aut per rem mandatam; debito f-ri; non potest arator uno grano f-re decumanum, C.; milites prædā, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Beröfwa; undandraga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">undanhålla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> rem vetere nomine, C.; se ipse victu suo, L.; alqm laude, Ct.; stipendium militum, Cs. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fraudātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bedragande, bedrägeri:</text:span></text:span> heri, Pt.; hinc fides, illinc f., C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fraudātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bedragare, -swikare:</text:span></text:span> creditorum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēfraudo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(och</text:span> <text:line-break/>Dēfrūdo), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bedraga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (preja) på ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">beröfwa:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> absol.,</text:span> Ter.; alqm drachmā, Pt.; eum aliqua re, C.; se fructu victoriæ, L. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: -</text:span> ne brevitas (ambitus verborum) aures d-asse videatur, C.; d. genium suum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lefwa knappt, tarfligt, mots.</text:span> indulgere genio), Pt., Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fraudŭlentus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bedräglig, swekfull:</text:span></text:span> homo; venditio, C.; f-simus, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fraudŭlenter</text:span>, -tius, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: Col., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fraudŭlentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bedräglighet:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frustrā</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> Fraus, Frus (Lucr.); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> defrudo; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">abl. sing. fem.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af ett adj.</text:span> fruster, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liksom</text:span> extra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> exter): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I willfarelse; på skam; förgäfwes:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom prædicatsord:</text:span> f. est, fuit, f. habetur:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mißtaga sig, komma på skam, gäckas:</text:span></text:span> ne f. sis!, Pt.; adnitendum - ut illi f. sint, Sa.; legati ut f. habiti discesserunt, Amm.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blifwa till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">om intet; mißlyckas, slå fel; åsidosättas:</text:span></text:span> nullum ejus aut consilium aut inceptum f. fuit; ea res f. fuit, Sa.; spes f. fuit, Js.; brevi servata, deinde f. habita sunt, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fåfängt, fruktlöst, förgäfwes, utan nytta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">påföljd:</text:span></text:span> operam sumere, Ter.; f. auxilium implorare, laborem suscipere, tempus conterere; ita vixi, ut non f. me natum existimem, C.; non ultra f. dictator ero, L. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för intet:</text:span> nisi feres argentum, f. me ductare non potes, Pt.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utan skäl, utan grund; utan mening</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ändamål:</text:span></text:span> non f. quid facere deo dignum est; f. appellantur animantes et animalia, et totum nomen inane est, C.; non f. adversus impios hebescunt sidera; haud f. dicta, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frustro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Narra, bedraga, gäcka:</text:span></text:span> ego me, Pt.; Hannibal f-tus a Fabio, Aur. Vict.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frustror</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intrans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slå fel, träffa miste; swika:</text:span></text:span> tela missa remiserunt, pauci in pluribus minus f-ti, Sa.; Coccejus vide ne f-etur, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gäcka, göra fruktlös</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">onyttig; swika</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = smyga sig undan ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bedraga, föra bakom ljuset, uppehålla med falska löften:</text:span></text:span> imprudenter facta opera impensas f-antur, Col.; per avia sequentes f-tus est, T.; Cloelia f-ta custodes Tiberim tranavit, L.; fides tua nos; spes me, Ter.; non ultra f-bor cives meos; Tarquinios spe auxilii non f-bor; differendo spem consilii exsequendi militarem impetu f-ri, L.; me ipsum et alios, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frustrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förfelande, swiken wäntan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (att blifwa beswiken):</text:span> quo magis me petiverunt, tanto majorem his f. dolorem attulit, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Beswikande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> bemödande att swika, isynnerhet att uppehålla med falska förespeglingar: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">swek, swepskäl, narrspel:</text:span></text:span> cupiditatis, Col.; Gallorum f-es spectabant, ut tempus tererent; clament, eam f-em esse legis tollendæ, L. (<text:span text:style-name="T2">Frustrātus</text:span>), ui, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: f-ui habere aliquem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till narr),</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Frausus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">part.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> Fraudo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hos</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fraxĭnus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ask</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(-träd):</text:span> procēra, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fraxĭnus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fraxĭneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är af </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ask:</text:span></text:span> virga f-na, Ov.; f-ea sudes, Vg.; hasta f-ea, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>rĕgellæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Latium.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Frĕgellānus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Frĕgellāni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inwånare i F.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>regēnæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Etrurien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frĕmo,</text:span> ui, ĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. om dofwa, orediga ljud:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af döda ting: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sorla, susa, gny, hwina:</text:span></text:span> venti indignantes circum claustra f-unt; flamina f-unt et cæca volutant murmura; saxa tormento concita, Vg.; ventus, Lucr., Ov.; unda, St.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af djur:</text:span> canis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(murrar),</text:span> Lucr.; leo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ryter);</text:span> equus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gnäggar),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af menniskor:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sorla:</text:span></text:span> f-bant caelicolæ vario assensu; circum altaria mixti populi f-unt; - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med accusativ-object:</text:span> omnes eadem ore f-bant, Vg.; omnia clamoribus f-bant, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Knorra, knota, fnysa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> förtrytsamt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">mumla, ropa, yttra sin förtrytelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer -:</text:span> f-ant omnes licet: dicam id, quod sentio; Arrius consulatum sibi ereptum esse f-it, C.; stabat acerba f-ens, Vg.; miles se proditione victum f-bat, T. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med acc.-obj.:</text:span> arma amens f-it <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(liksom ryter efter),</text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frĕmĕbundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Brusande; fnysande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af harm:</text:span> C. poēt., Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frĕmĭtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sorl, sus, gny:</text:span></text:span> murmurantis maris; terræ; armorum, C.; marinus, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. equorum, Lucr., Cs.; canum, Col.; apium, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">menniskors </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sorl; knorrande, knot:</text:span></text:span> egentium, C.; plausu f-uque consonat nemus; f. secundus, Vg.; contionum f-ūs non expavescere, Qu.; si displicuit sententia, f-u aspernantur, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frĕmor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gny, sorl:</text:span></text:span> Varr., Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Affrĕmo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gny wid, inwid:</text:span></text:span> Boreas, Sil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumfrĕmo</text:span>, 3.: aves nidos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(flaxar omkring),</text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confrĕmo</text:span>, ui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med en mun, på en gång </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sorla, gny:</text:span></text:span> c-uere omnes, Ov.; caelum et circus, Sil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infrĕmo</text:span>, ui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fnysa, ryta, brusa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot ngn:</text:span> aper, Vg.; bellum, Sil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfrĕmo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fnysa:</text:span></text:span> delphini, poēt. ap. C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Frenator <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Freno, Frenum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frendo,</text:span> frēsum, fressum, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gnißla med tänderna, skära tänder</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af ilska l. smärta):</text:span> dentibus f-it, Pt.; leo f-ens, poēt. ap. C.; f-ens Proteus, Vg.; Hannibal f-ens gemensque, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sönderkrossa, mala:</text:span></text:span> fabam, Col.; cicera fresa, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infrendens</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">part.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gnißlande:</text:span></text:span> dentibus gemitu, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Nefrens</text:span>, dis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som ej än kan bita, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tandlös:</text:span></text:span> ovis, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Freni, Freniger, Freno <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Frenum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>rentāni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">samnitiskt folk.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Frentānus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frēnum</text:span> <text:line-break/>(frænum), i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">pl.</text:span> -i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> -a, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Betsel,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> äfwen poet. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tygel:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i egentliga uttryck:</text:span> equus f-a accipit, C.; equus f-um recepit, f. depulit ore, Hor.; f-os equis detrahere, L.; f-a concordia jugo ferunt quadrupedes; equus f-os audit sonantes, Vg.; f-a sonantia addunt equis; f-a remittere, retinere; f-a jacent laxa in tergo, Ov. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttryck för: hålla tillbaka, hämma, kufwa, beherrska o. s. w.:</text:span> f-os adhibere alicui; alter f-is eget, alter calcaribus; exsultanti f-os furoris injicere; f. mordere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tredskas),</text:span> C.; f-a furenti concutere, Vg.; f-a injicere licentiæ, Hor.; f. accipere et parēre, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frēnĭger</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">betslad:</text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frēno</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Betsla, lägga betsel på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> equos, Cs.; f-tus equus, Vg., Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tygla, styra, kufwa:</text:span></text:span> furores alicujus legibus, C.; Aeolus ventos vinclis et carcere; gentes superbas justitiā, Vg.; voluptates temperantiā, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frēnātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som betslar, kör, styr:</text:span> equorum, St.; animus infinitæ potestatis f., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēfrēnātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(befriad från betslet), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ohejdad:</text:span></text:span> amnes d-o cursu in æquora volvuntur, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effrēnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(Effrēfrenis, Pn.):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fri från betsel, med aftaget betsel:</text:span></text:span> e-o equo in medios ignes inferri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äfwen</text:span> equi liberi frenis), L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Otyglad, utan band:</text:span></text:span> gens virûm, Vg.; amor, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effrēno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">befria från betslet, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lössläppa:</text:span></text:span> Vulturnum ventum e-at Juno, Sil.; equi velut e-ti passim ferebantur, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effrēnātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ohejdad, tygellös, öfwerdådig, oförsynt:</text:span></text:span> libido, cupiditas, violentia, audacia, mens; homines secundis rebus e-i; vox libera atque etiam e-ior (alii: effrenatio), C.; libido Appii, quo impunitior, eo e-ior, L.; affectibus e-simis abstrahi, Sen. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effrēnāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tygellöst, öfwerdådigt:</text:span></text:span> e-ius in hostem irrumpere; libidines temere et e. ad potiendum incitantur, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effrēnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tygellöshet, öfwerdåd:</text:span></text:span> impotentis animi e., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infrēnis</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infrēnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Otyglad; wild:</text:span></text:span> i-is equi lapsus, Vg.; cursus i-us, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infrēno</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Påbetsla, betsla:</text:span></text:span> equos, L.; - currus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hästarne till wagnen),</text:span> Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fastgöra; styra:</text:span></text:span> naves ancoris, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Offrēnātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tyglad, betslad:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfrēno</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med betsel</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tygel hålla, draga tillbaka:</text:span></text:span> equos, Ct.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillbakahålla, afhålla, hämma, kufwa:</text:span></text:span> fluvios, Lucr.; a gloria, a reditu r. alqm; juventutem r. et coërcere; libidines, C.; licentiam, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfrēnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillbakahållande, beherrskande:</text:span></text:span> doloris, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Suffrēnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppfästande, fastgörande:</text:span></text:span> lapidis, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frĕquens,</text:span> tis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i allm.: som ofta gör ngt l. är någorstädes; som ofta sker, som förefinnes i mängd, som mycket l. i mängd besökes l. befolkas o. s. w., således): </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i afseende på tiden: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ständig, idelig, flitig, wanlig;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ofta att öfwersätta med adv.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ständigt, ofta, flitigt:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer:</text:span> Demosthenes f. fuit Platonis auditor; venio in senatum f-ns; Roscius erat Romæ f., C.; esse f-em cum aliquo, Ter., C.; f-em exercere tellurem, Vg.; f-ns secretis (= qui s-tis interesse solet), T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker (som ofta l. allmänt sker, brukas, öfwas): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ständig:</text:span></text:span> latrocinia f.; iambum et trochæum f-em segregat ab oratione Aristoteles; pocula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ideliga),</text:span> C.; familiaritas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(liflig),</text:span> N.; f-ior <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wanlig)</text:span> usus anulorum; res usu f-ior, Pn.; erat f-ns <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfligt)</text:span> senatoribus, si quid e re publica crederent, loco sententiæ promere, T.; f. imitatio, Qu.; f-ior sententia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mera gängse),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Talrik, i mängd församlad:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> refert, qui audiant, f-es an pauci; equites Romani in gradibus Concordiæ f-simi steterunt; f. senatus; f-es fuimus in senatu, C.; f-es convenerunt ad eum, Cs.; equitatus f., Ct.; conventus, N.; Tyrii per limina laeta f-es convenere, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om collegier: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Domför:</text:span></text:span> f-i senatu, C., L., Pt.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om orter l. ställen: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Folkrik, mycket besökt, liflig; uppfylld</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af menniskor); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tätt bebygd, bewuxen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med; i allm. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rik</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngt:</text:span> præfectura, municipium; theatrum, C.; terra colubris, Ov.; compita, Hor.; via, L., Ov.; urbs populis f., Luc.; urbs tectis f-ns; loca ædificiis f-ia, L.; regio vicis, urbibus, Ct.; campus herbis, Vg.; mons silvæ f-ns, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frĕquenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ofta; tätt och ofta; ständigt:</text:span></text:span> translationibus omnis sermo f-sime utitur; f. ventitare ad alqm, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Talrikt:</text:span></text:span> interceditur, C.; ecce coturnices inter sua proelia vivunt: forsitan et fiant inde f. anus, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frĕquentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stort antal, talrikhet, mängd:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af menniskor på ett ställe l. wid ett tillfälle: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Folksamling, publik, folkmassa; stort tillopp; följe:</text:span></text:span> hujus janua maximā quotidie f-ā civium celebratur; domum reducebatur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> efferebatur summa cum f-a; magna f.; non usitatā f-ā stipati sumus; a coetu hominum f-aque - in solitudinem se recipere; equites ei assiduam f-am præstabant, C.; vulgi, N.; negotiatorum f., Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af ting:</text:span> epistolarum; sepulcrorum; rerum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ämnen, tankar),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frĕquento</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ofta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">allmänt göra, anwända, öfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> hæc (genera transferendi) f-at Demetrius maxime, C.; neque ideo f-bantur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(blefwo wanliga)</text:span> cognatorum conjugia, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Talrikt församla, hopa:</text:span></text:span> scribas dies ad ærarium f-verat; (in oratione) multa acervatim f., C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ofta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">i mängd besöka, bewista, bebo; befolka;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">uppfylla, rikligen förse, utstyra med ngt:</text:span></text:span> ludos, festum, domum alicujus, C., T.; arva, Vg.; Agrippinam, T.; triumphum, L.; Italiæ solitudinem, urbes, C.; loca cultoribus, Sa.; oratio f-da est est luminibus sententiarum et verborum, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frĕquentāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upprepande:</text:span></text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frĕquentātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ständigt l. allmänt öfwande af ngt:</text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hopande, samlande:</text:span></text:span> argumentorum; f. est, quum res in causa dispersæ coguntur in unum, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frĕquentātīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som utmärker upprepande, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Frequentativ:</text:span></text:span> verba, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infrĕquens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som sällan är l. gör ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sällspord, försumlig, owan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wid, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">okunnig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om:</text:span> is est i. Romæ, C.; deorum cultor i., Hor.; rei militaris i. (”qui abest a signis”, Fs.), C.; miles, Pt.; vocum Latinarum, Gell.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Owanlig, sällsynt:</text:span></text:span> vocabulum, Gell.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fåtalig, gles:</text:span></text:span> senatus, copiæ, C.; i-a armatis signa egressa (erant) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(glest åtföljda, omgifna af),</text:span> L.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swagt befolkad, bebodd:</text:span></text:span> (loca) urbis i-sima, L.; alvei, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infrĕquentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fåtalighet, liten samling:</text:span></text:span> senatus, C., L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Folkbrist, brist på rörelse:</text:span></text:span> i-æ locorum - subvenire, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfrĕquens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mycket besökt, liflig:</text:span></text:span> emporium, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fresus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> Frendo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frĕtum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: rarius<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frĕtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> ferveo?):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ström, jäsning af wätskor</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">watten:</text:span></text:span> f-us ipse anni permiscet frigus et æstum; hæc f-a anni <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wår och höst, jäsningsperioden)</text:span> sunt, Lucr.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> talis domi ac foris populi Romani f. illud adolescentiæ, id est secundæ ætatis, qua flore virtutis exarsit et <text:span text:style-name="T4">ferbuit,</text:span> Fl.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sund;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spec. Messinska sundet; poet.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">haf:</text:span></text:span> quid de f-is aut de æstibus marinis plura dicam?; perangusto fretu dividi; ab Italia F-o disjungi; a F-o se septimo die venisse dicebat, C.; in f-a dum fluvii current -; Sigea f-a, Vg.; æstuosa, Hor.; tumida, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frĕtensis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: mare f. = mare Siculum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Messinska sundet),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfrĕto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerfara:</text:span></text:span> Sol.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Transfrĕto</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fara, segla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hafwet:</text:span></text:span> Su., Gell.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerskeppa, -föra:</text:span></text:span> Amm. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Transfrĕtātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerfart:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frētus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Litande, tröstande, byggande på: stödjande sig på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i kraft af, medelst) ngt</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T4">aliqua re;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sällan</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">alicui rei</text:span>): malitiā f., Ter.; diis, Pt.; hæc duo plerique ingenio f-i simul faciunt; qui voce f-i sunt, Epigonos (fabulam) eligunt, qui gestu Melanippam; vobis f-us hoc promisi, C.; nulli rei præterquam numero f-us proelium iniit, L.; potuit manes arcessere conjugis Orpheus f-us citharā fidibusque canoris, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Friabilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Frio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frĭco,</text:span> cui, cātum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> ctum, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klå, rifwa, stryka, gnida (frottera):</text:span></text:span> sus arbore costas, Vg.; dentes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skura),</text:span> Pn.; corpus oleo, Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frĭcātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frĭcātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rifning, frottering, gnidning:</text:span></text:span> f-us dentium, Pn.; vehemens f-io corporis, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Affrĭco</text:span>, cui, ctum, cātum, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gnida, stryka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot l. på -:</text:span> vitiosum locum corporis pecudes - arbori a-ant, Col. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> malignus comes candido rubiginem a-at, Sen. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Affrictio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Affrictus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Strykning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot -, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T4">friction:</text:span></text:span> flamma se accendit a-u, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumfrĭco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rundtomkring gnida, (skura):</text:span></text:span> labra dolii, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confrĭco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gnida mot hwartannat; gnugga, rifwa, frottera:</text:span></text:span> genua, Pt.; faciem sibi, Su.; dentes, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēfrĭco</text:span>, cui, cātum, ctum, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">genom gnidning l. rifning rena från ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rifwa ren, skura, rykta, frottera:</text:span></text:span> dentes, Catl., Ov.; equum, Sen.; in balneo d-ri, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> multo sale (Lucilius) urbem d-uit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(frotterade, ingned</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">twålade),</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effrĭco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gnida</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af, ut:</text:span> sudorem fronte, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infrĭco</text:span>, cui, ctum, cātum, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gnida in</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ingnida,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> frottera med ngt:</text:span> fuliginem ulceri, Col.; dentes, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfrĭco</text:span>, cui, cātum, ctum, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomfrottera, -rifwa, öfwerstryka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (stryka sig öfwer -):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> caput et os unguento; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.:</text:span> p-ri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i badet),</text:span> C.; faciem pisce, Su. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> caput manu p. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rifwer sig i hufwudet, såsom tecken till betänklighet);</text:span> os p-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för att drifwa bort rodnaden = lägga bort all blygsel l. blygsamhet),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfrĭco</text:span>, cui, ctum, cātum, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upprifwa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> in linteum indito aut in mortarium, r-ato denuo, Cato.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upprifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sår, och bildl.: ngns </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">smärta, minnet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt o. s. w.:</text:span> cicatricem, vulnus; dolorem, desiderium, memoriam, animum, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intrans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bryta upp, ut igen:</text:span></text:span> lippitudo, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Suffrĭco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rifwa undan; undertill skura:</text:span></text:span> fæcem; vasa, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frīgeo,</text:span> 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara kall, stelfrusen, kallnad:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> totus f-et, Ter.; membra f-ntis (mortui) lavant, Vg.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i kroppslig men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara matt, slapp:</text:span></text:span> effetæ f-ent in corpore vires, Vg.<text:line-break/>2.<text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara kall, stel, utan känsla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lif:</text:span></text:span> in re ferventissima f-es, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om personer) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara dåsig, sysslolös; intet förmå, icke komma någon wäg, mißlyckas:</text:span></text:span> nihil fit, plane f-eo, C.; hi homines f-ent <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äro slagne ur brädet),</text:span> Ter.; hic f-et (in petitione consulatus); cantor f-ens ad populum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som ej gör ngn effect),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om saker) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stå stilla, ej gå, ej lyckas; drifwas slappt; ligga nere:</text:span></text:span> f-bant omnia consilia; si ista f-bunt, recipias te ad nos, C.; studia; opus, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frīgĕfacto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afkyla:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frīgesco</text:span>, frixi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Inch.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kallna, stelna:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> oleum, Cato; pedes manusque, T.; cor Ulixi, Liv. Andr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kallna, slappna; bli kall</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot ngn:</text:span> opus; affectus, Qu.; majorum limina tibi, Ps.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frīgĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kall:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såwäl kylig, iskall, som swal:</text:span> aër; flumen f-ius, C.; loca f-sima, Cs.; fons; vespera, Vg.; aura, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dödskall, froßkall, rysande:</text:span></text:span> membra nati; f-a mors (animo divellit artus); mihi f. horror membra quatit, Vg.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kroppsligen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Matt, slapp:</text:span></text:span> f-a bello dextera, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">andligen</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slapp, kall, likgiltig, död:</text:span></text:span> accusator, C.; legere aliquid f-um, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tråkig, fadd, platt, dum:</text:span></text:span> orationis genus; dicta; calumnia; literæ, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rädd, förfärad:</text:span></text:span> mens criminibus, Juv.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ryslig, förfärande:</text:span></text:span> f. penetrat per compita rumor, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frīgĭda</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kallt watten:</text:span></text:span> Pn., Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frīgĭdārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är för kallt watten l. bad:</text:span> cella, Pn.; aheneum, Vitr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frīgĭdārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rum för kallt bad:</text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frīgĭde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slappt, platt:</text:span></text:span> agere, C.; dicere multa, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frīgĭdĕfacto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afkyla:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frīgĭdiusculus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Något platt:</text:span></text:span> Gell. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frīgĭdŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Matt:</text:span></text:span> ocelli, Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frīgus</text:span>, ŏris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Köld:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">luftens kyla, frost:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. (i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">sing.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">plur.</text:span>): intolerabile, maximum impendet f.; nullo f-e adducitur, ut operto capite sit; f-um vim pellere et calorum molestias tolerare; terra obriget f-e, C.; f-ora mitescunt Zephyris; dissolve f. ligna super foco reponens, Hor.; prima auctumni f-a, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swalka:</text:span></text:span> f. captabis opacum Vg.; amabile, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i mots. till</text:span> æstas = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Winter:</text:span></text:span> lac mihi non æstate novum, non f-e defit; f-bus mediis Hebrum bibere, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inre </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kyla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hos en död l. sjuk kropp; l. ss. en werkan af förskräckelse, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kall rysning:</text:span></text:span> corpus perfusum f-e leti, Lucr.; corpus tentatur f-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(froßrysning).</text:span> Hor.; illi solvuntur f-e membra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om en döende),</text:span> Vg. - extemplo Aeneæ solvuntur f-e (= frigido horrore, gelidā formidine) membra; sanguis concrevit f -e, Vg.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dåsighet; köld</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">likgiltighet; bristande sympathi</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">intreße; kallsinnighet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (onåd):</text:span> nos f-e frigescimus, C.; aliena deliratio (recitanti apud auditores) f-us attulit, Pn.; majoris amici f., Hor.; notus amicitiā Tiberii et f-e, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frigĕro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kyla, swalka,</text:span></text:span> Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frīgŏrĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kylande:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfrīgesco</text:span>, frixi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Inch.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förkyla sig:</text:span></text:span> Varr., Mt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bli matt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">platt:</text:span></text:span> (in dicendo), Front.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfrictio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förkylning, -frysning:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfrīgĕfăcio</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Komma att rysa:</text:span></text:span> cor mihi, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfrīgĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mycket kall:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Præfrīgĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hårdt kall:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfrīgesco</text:span>, frixi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(åter) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afkylas, kallna:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> vinum, Cato; cor vulnere læsum, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swalna, kallna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = komma i glömska, i förakt, komma ur rörelsen, till korta:</text:span> res, Ter.; crimen in re recenti caluit, nunc r-xit; sortes jam r-xerunt; Memmius (candidatus) r-xit (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förlorat alla utsigter),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfrīgĕro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afkyla, komma att frysa; swalka:</text:span></text:span> ignis in aquam conjectus ratur; calore r-to; Saturnus summa (caeli) r-at; me frigus r-vit; umbris aquisque r-ri salubriter, C.; æstum, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">komma att </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">swalna, mattas:</text:span></text:span> accusatio, sermo hominum r-tur, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bringa ngn ur fattning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (concepterna), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">göra flat, afsnäsa:</text:span></text:span> a se ipso r-tus, Su.; testem interrogatione refutare aut urbane dicto r., Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfrīgĕrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swalkande; swalka:</text:span></text:span> r. æstate, C.; auræ, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfrīgĕrātōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kylande, swalkande;</text:span></text:span> vis, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfrīgĕrātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kylande:</text:span></text:span> natura, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Subfrīgĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Subfrīgĭde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Något matt, platt:</text:span></text:span> argumentum, Amm.; dictum, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Frigero <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Frigus, Frigeo.<text:line-break/>Frigesco, Frigid. . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Frigeo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frigilla</text:span> l.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fringilla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bofink:</text:span></text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frīgo,</text:span> xi, ctum, (xum), 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rosta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (på eld), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bryna:</text:span></text:span> sal, Cato; triticum, Varr.; ciceris f-cti emptor, Hor.; hordeum f-unt, deinde molunt; ova, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frĭgo,</text:span> 3.:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frĭgŭlo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frĭgūtio</text:span> <text:line-break/>(fringutio, <text:line-break/>fringultio), 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Qwittra;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om menniskor = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">qwida, mumla, stamma:</text:span></text:span> merulæ f-tiunt, Ap. -; neptis de lecto frigit, Afr.; vix singulas syllabas f-utiens, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Frigorificus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Frigus, Frigeo.<text:line-break/>Frigulo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Frĭgo.<text:line-break/>Frigus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Frigeo.<text:line-break/>Frigutio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Frĭgo.<text:line-break/>Fringilla <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Frigilla. <text:line-break/>Fringultio, -gutio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Frĭgo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>riniātes, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liguriskt folk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frio,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Söndersmula:</text:span></text:span> terra f-tur, Varr.; crusta, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Friābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lös,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lätt smulas:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Affrio</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smula till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">i ngt:</text:span></text:span> a. et aspergere, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infrio</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Insmula</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> uti, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">strö på:</text:span></text:span> salem vulneribus, Col.; farinam in aquam, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>rīsii, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Friserne, germaniskt folk:</text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frit,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">Ind.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">yttersta spetsen af ett ax:</text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fritilla</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Fitilla), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Offerrätt (-mos):</text:span></text:span> boni etiam farre et f-ā religiosi sunt, Sen. (de Benef. I. 6); Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frĭtillus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bägare,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwari tärningar omskakas:</text:span> Sen., Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frĭtinnio,</text:span> 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Qwittra:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frīvŏlus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> frio?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lumpen, simpel, ringa:</text:span></text:span> sermo f. et illiberalis, C.; labor, Sen.; jocus, Qu.; f-a origo superbissimi animalium (hominis), Pn.; auspicio f-o mente recreata, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">neutr. pl. subst.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Småsaker, tarfligt bohag:</text:span></text:span> jam f-a transfert Ucalegon, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Frond. . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Frons.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Frons</text:span> <text:line-break/>(fruns), dis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trädens grönska; löf;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">sing. collectivt</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">plur.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">löfwerk, grönt; kransar:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span> virgulta et f. multa, C.; teneras turbavit janua f-es; manibus carpere f-es, Vg.; campi nudi sine f-e; in f-em crines, in ramos brachia crescunt, Ov.; populeā velatur f-e juventus, Vg.; f-e comas vincti coenant et carmina dictant, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frondārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: fiscina <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwari löf uppsamlas och bäres),</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frondātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">trädens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Qwistande, aflöfwande:</text:span></text:span> Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frondātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som afqwistar:</text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frondeo</text:span>, ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">stå löfwad, löfbeklädd; grönska:</text:span></text:span> nunc f-ent silvæ, nunc formosissimus annus; ramus f-ens, Vg., vitis, Col.; nigrā nemus ilice f-ens, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frondesco</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Inch.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Löfwas:</text:span></text:span> simili f-it virga metallo, Vg.; alia plantarum genera hieme nudata vere f-unt, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frondeus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som bildas l. består af </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">löf: löfwad, löfrik:</text:span></text:span> corona, Pn.; tecta f-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skogens löf-hwalf);</text:span> nemora, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frondĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. bär löf; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Löfwad:</text:span></text:span> domus avium, Lucr.; Naev.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frondōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rik på grönska, löfrik:</text:span></text:span> silva, Enn.; montes, Varr.; ramus, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infrons</text:span>, dis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Löflös; aflöfwad;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">saknar grönska:</text:span></text:span> ager, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Frons,</text:span> tis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span> Pt.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Panna:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(såsom kroppsdel hos menniskor och djur): </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> f-em percutere, ferire, C.; ingens lumen sub f-e Cyclopis; f. equi nascentis, Vg.; tenui f-e insignis Lycoris, Hor.; hirta, Sen.; rugosa, Mt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i uttryck för sinnesstämning l. rörelser:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tillsammans med verber:</text:span> contrahere, C.; obducere, Qu.; exporrigere, Ter.; remittere, Pn.; sollicitam explicare f-em, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ensamt</text:span> (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">min, uppsyn, ansigte):</text:span> astitit severo f-e curans, cogitans, Pt. (Mil. 201); f. est janua animi; f., oculi, vultus sæpe mentitur; præclara est in omni vita æquabilitas et idem semper vultus eademque f.; f-e occultare sententiam; fremit, sed utrum f-e an mente, dubitatur; tabella (suffragiorum) f-es hominum aperit, mentes tegit; ne in foro quidem pristinæ f-is reliquiæ apparent, C.; f. læta, Vg.; proterva, Hor.; minax; perfricare f-em <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(drifwa bort rodnaden, ej blygas),</text:span> C., Sen.; f. (= pudor) periit, Ps.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Framsidan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utsidan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> a tergo, a f-e, a lateribus, C.; f-e sub adversa (litoris) scopulis pendentibus antrum, Vg.; mille pedes in f-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på bredden, långs med wägen),</text:span> trecentos cippus in agrum dabat, Hor.; castrorum; collis, Cs.; Caucasi, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en härs </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Front:</text:span></text:span> octo cohortes in f-e constituit, Sa.; æqua f-e ad pugnam procedere, L.; recta f-e concurrere hosti, Ct. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Framstam</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ett skepp:</text:span> una ambæ feruntur junctis f-bus, Vg.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildliga uttryck = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Det yttre, ytan, utseendet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (den första anblicken) af en sak:</text:span> causæ f. parum honesta; grammatica plus habet in recessu, quam in f-e promittit; dura primā f-e quæstio, Qu.; superasse tantum itineris, transisse æstuaria pulcrum ac decorum in f-em, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frontālia</text:span>, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pannprydnad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för hästar;</text:span> L., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frontātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: lapis, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hörnsten, som står ut åt båda sidor,</text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fronto</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Storpannad,</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Bĭfrons</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med twenne ansigten:</text:span></text:span> Janus, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Frontalia, -tatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Frons.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>rontīnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>ronto, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. cognomen i</text:span> gens Cornelia. <text:line-break/>Frontōniānus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. Fronto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Frons.<text:line-break/>Fruct. . ., Frug. . ., Frument. . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fruor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frūniscor,</text:span> 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Njuta, winna:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infrūnītus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Onjutbar; smaklös:</text:span></text:span> Sen.; copia orationis, Mcb.<text:line-break/>Fruns <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Frons.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fruor,</text:span> fructus (C. ap. Prisc., Lucr.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> fruitus (Jct.), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sällsynta;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">part. fut.</text:span> fruiturus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Njuta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">= </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skörda frukten; draga nytta, inkomst af</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">göra sig till godo, nyttja, komma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wara i åtnjutande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt (med förswagad betydelse = wara begåfwad med ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ega;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">re,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sällan</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">rem</text:span>): agro, Ter.; te tuaque virtute f-i cupide; gratiā et opibus alicujus; eum f. vitā nolebant, C.; frigoribus agricolae parto f-untur; sociā urbe f., Vg.; pabulum f. ex Kal. Sept. occipito, Cato; is demum mihi vivere et f. animā videtur; vita, qua fruimur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som beskäres oß),</text:span> brevis est, Sa.; nemo impediebatur, quominus rebus Cimonis, quibus quisque vellet, f-retur, N.; agrum f-dum locare, L.; fructibus Siculis; f. paratis integra mente; dii tibi divitias dederunt artemque f-di, Hor.; corpora uti sunt levissima, ita mobilitate f-untur, Lucr.; bello, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Njuta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = hafwa njutning l. nöje af ngt (i mots. till arbete l. till nytta):</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker:</text:span> satiatis jucundius est carere, quam f-i; beatum esse, qui voluptatibus f-retur confideretque se fruiturum esse -; recordatione amicitiæ sic f-or, ut beatum me esse putem, quod cum Scipione vixerim; si pace f. volumus, bellum gerendum est; securitate f-i optimum est; usu et moribus alicujus, C.; hoc ingenium meo modo, Ter.; Hannibal quum victoria uti posset, f-i maluit, Fl.; ea, quae fructus es, periere, Lucr. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med personl. object: = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Njuta af någons umgänge:</text:span></text:span> neque nos te f-mur et tu nobis cares, C.; minus sæpe, quam vellet, Attico f-batur, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fructus</text:span>, us (-i, Cato, Ter.), <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">abstr.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nyttjande, åtnjutande, njutande; njutning:</text:span></text:span> meus f. prior est, Pt.; nec mihi f. otii datus est -; omnem f-um voluptatum auferret solitudo; quis esset tantus f. in secundis rebus, nisi haberes (amicum)?, C.; f-um capere oculis ex casu alicujus, N.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">concret: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afkastning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm. och såsom </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inkomst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för en egare):</text:span> fundi, Cato, Varr.; me non f. modo, sed etiam ipsius terræ vis ac natura delectat, C.; vaccæ, Col.; aviariorum, Varr.; f-us ex bestiis, ex rebus inanimis percipere; ex pecudibus f-um capere; ovium, pecudum, prædiorum; pecuniæ f-bus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rentor)</text:span> exercitum alere; an partus ancillæ sit in f-u habendus?, C.; f-us maritimi et terrestres (regis); f. metallorum, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frukt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af wäxter i allm. l. med uteslutande af säd (utan afseende på en, för hwilken det är inkomst; jfr.</text:span> fruges): arborum bacæ terr æque f-us; f. apparet in herbis; frugum f-uumque reliquorum perceptio et conservatio; f-us serere, demetere, percipere, condere; ver tanquam adolescentiam significat ostenditque f-us futuros; f-um ferre, efferre, C.; reddere, Varr.; f-us feros mollire colendo, Vg.; f-us sunt et eæ res, quas fundus et quas, quæ in fundo, ferunt, ut fruamur: hinc declinatæ fruges et frumenta, sed eæ e terra, Varr.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttryck: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frukt; fördel, winst, lön:</text:span></text:span> is philosophiæ f. est uberrimus; f. senectutis est ante partorum bonorum memoria; artes - in omni vita cultæ, quum diu multumque vixeris, mirificos efferunt f-us; f-um diligentiæ capere, pietatis ferre; posse libertate uti, non spoliantem se patrimonio, pecuniæ est f. maximus; omnis amicitiæ f. in ipso amore inest; f. ingenii et virtutis - tum maximus capitur, quum in proximum quemque confertur, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fructĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fruktbärande:</text:span></text:span> arbor, Col., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fructuārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som bär frukt, som föder; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afwels-:</text:span></text:span> rami oleæ; palmes, ager, Col.; scrofa, Varr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är bestämd för frukter l. grödan:</text:span> pars villæ; cella, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fructuōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som gifwer rik afkastning l. inkomst; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gifwande, lönande, indrägtig, fruktbärande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i yttre men.:</text:span> nihil bonum norunt, nisi quod f-sum sit; ager quamvis fertilis sine cultura f. esse non potest; ager f-simus; aratio, res pecuaria, prædia, ars; est non modo liberale paulum de jure nonnunquam decedere, sed etiam f-um, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i andra hänseenden:</text:span> tota philosophia frugifera et f-a est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ett lönande, tacksamt fält);</text:span> f-ior <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mera fruktbringande)</text:span> hominum generi - (est) eorum (vita), qui se ad rempublicam accommodaverunt, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infructuōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ofruktbar, lönlös, fruktlös:</text:span></text:span> vitis; cultura, Col.; militia gravis et i., T.; preces, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">(<text:span text:style-name="T2">Frūgis</text:span>, Varro;<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frux</text:span>, Enn. Ann. 412), Frūgis, -em, -e, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanligare i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pl.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">fruges</text:span>, gum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jordens frukt, gröda, säd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (skidfrukter inberäknade:</text:span> f-um duo genera frumenta et legumina, Pn.): quod segetes ferunt, (dicuntur) f-es, Varr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr.</text:span> Fructus II, 2); (viriditas herbescens) fundit <text:soft-page-break/>f-em spici ordine structam; non omnem f-em in omni agro reperire possis; f-es terræ bacæque arborum; ubertas f-um et fructuum; inventis f-bus glande vesci; terra feta f-bus; f-es serere, percipere, C.; terra parens f-um, Vg.; provisæ f-is copia, Hor.; tellus fert f-es, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mera sällan: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frukt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm., äfwen af träd:</text:span> quercus et ilex multa f-e pecus, multā dominum juvat umbrā; pomifer autumnus f-es effudit, Hor.; f-bus idonea pars vitis; f-es caducæ, Col.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frukt, nytta, ordentligt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">nyttigt lefnadssätt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lefnadssätt, art:</text:span></text:span> rem ad f-em perducere, Qu.; centuriæ seniorum agitant expertia f-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(moral),</text:span> Hor.; ad f-em animum applicare, Pt.; ad bonam f-em se recipere, C.; homo non bonæ f-is, Gell. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt märkes</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">dat.</text:span>:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frūgi</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">till frukt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. gagn, i bruket närmande sig till ett (indeclinabelt)</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer (mots.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">nequam</text:span>): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gagnelig; som sköter sig och sitt wäl), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Redbar, stadig;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i lefwernet) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ordentlig, återhållsam, anständig, dygdig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr.</text:span> frugalitas): f. homo; de symbolis quid actum est? paratum est. - F. es!, Ter.; f. hominem dici non multum laudis habet in rege; homines f. et sobrii; servus f. et integer, C.; Piso tanta virtute et integritate fuit, ut solus f. nominaretur, C.; mancipium, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ordentlig, sparsam, enkel:</text:span></text:span> victus, Qu.; atrium, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frūgālior</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frūgālissimus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Redbarare, ordentligare, sparsammare; enklare, -st:</text:span></text:span> optimus colonus, parcissimus, f-simus, C.; in re perdita, quam in salva factus est f-ior, Pt.; f-ior villa, Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frūgālĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ordentlighet, stadga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i lefwernet), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">anständighet, återhållsamhet,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (dygd):</text:span> ego f-em, id est modestiam et temperantiam, virtutem maximam esse judico; omnem abstinentiam, reliquas etiam virtutes f. continet; f-is proprium est motus animi appetentis regere et sedare, C.<text:line-break/>b. = fruges, Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frūgālĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ordentligt, dygdigt, anständigt:</text:span></text:span> f. et honeste fit; loqui f., C. - vivere parce et f., Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frūgĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fruktbärande:</text:span></text:span> agri non omnes f-i, qui coluntur; campi f-i, C.; arbores, T. - tota philosophia f-a et fructuosa est, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frūgĭfĕrens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frukt-, sädesbärande:</text:span></text:span> mare velivolum, terræ f-es, Lucr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frūgĭlĕgus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sädplockande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">-samlande:</text:span></text:span> formicæ, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frūgĭpărus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som frambringar l. alstrar säd:</text:span> primæ f-os fetus - mortalibus dididerunt Athenæ, Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frūgĭperdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: salix f. (”quæ ante maturitatem amittit semen”), Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frūmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n. collect.</text:span>: (olim dicebant frugmentum, nunc frumentum profertur, Val. Max. de nominum ratione): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(axfrukt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Säd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sädesslag), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">spannmål:</text:span></text:span> in segetibus f. est, in quo culmus extulit spicam, Varr.; frugum duo genera, f-a, ut triticum, hordeum, legumina, ut faba -; f-a hiberna, æstiva, Pn.; f. ex agris comportare; æstimare; metiri, C.; admetiri, Su.; f-a luxuriosa, C.; f-i copia; f-a in <text:soft-page-break/>agris matura non erant; f-a maturescunt, Cs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frūmentārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är för l. består af säd, spannmål; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sädes-, spannmåls-:</text:span></text:span> ager Varr.; loca, Cs.; prædo, lex, largitio, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frūmentārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spannmålshandlare:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frūmentor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i fält) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indrifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">taga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hemta spannmål:</text:span></text:span> f-andi aut pabuland i causa progredi; f-tum ire, mittere, Cs., L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frūmentātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sädeshemtning, fouragering:</text:span></text:span> Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sädesutdelning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (åt hufwudstadsbefolkningen):</text:span> publicas f-es in perpetuum abolere, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frūmentātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spannmåls-samlare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för armée), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(fourageur):</text:span></text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfruor</text:span>, (fructus), 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fullt njuta; i fullt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rikt mått njuta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">draga inkomst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt:</text:span> gaudiis; rerum gestarum gloriā et sapientiae laude; expetuntur divitiae ad p-das voluptates, C.; summa amoenitate perfructus, C. ap. Prisc.; fertilitate et amoenitate agri, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>rŭsĭno, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Latium.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Frŭsĭnas, ātis, A. <text:line-break/>Frŭsĭnātes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inw. i F.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Frustatim, -stillatim, -sto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Frustum. <text:line-break/>Frustr. . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fraus.<text:line-break/>Frustul. . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Frustum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frustum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stycke, bit:</text:span></text:span> casei, Col.; lardi, Hor.; pars in f-a secant (carnem), Vg.; vomit f-a esculenta, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frustātim</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frustillātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Styckewis:</text:span></text:span> Ap., Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frusto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stycka:</text:span></text:span> Fl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frustŭlentus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">full af bitar:</text:span> Pt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frustŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">litet stycke:</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frŭtex,</text:span> tĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Buske, buskwäxt, -stam:</text:span></text:span> f-es, ut rosæ, arundo, Col.; domus antra fuere et densi f-es, Ov.; juniperi, Pn. cedri, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Telning, utskott</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på träd:</text:span><text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stjelk, stam:</text:span></text:span> lupini, Col.; olerum, Pn.; quercus antiqua - ramos f-e dedit, Su.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. skällsord = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stock:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frŭtectum</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frŭtĭcētum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Småskog, busk-snår:</text:span></text:span> ager f-is obsessus, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frŭtectōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">full af buskar l. småskog:</text:span> tractus, Col.; loca, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frŭtĭcesco</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Inch.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slå ut i telningar,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> grena sig, bli buskig:</text:span> vitis cito, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frŭtĭco</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frŭtĭcor</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dep.</text:span>: 1.: I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om träd) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skjuta skott,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> framdrifwa qwistar, telningar; utgrena sig:</text:span> inula spatiose f-at, Pn.; excisa arbor est, non evulsa: itaque, quam f-etur, vides, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> pili, Juv. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frŭtĭcātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">collect.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">telningar, rotskott:</text:span> (stolones) appellantur in arboribus f. inutiles, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Frŭtĭcōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om träd) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rik på telningar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">qwistar;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om orter) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">med busksnår bewuxen, öfwerwuxen:</text:span></text:span> aizoum aradice f.; rami; calamus f-simus, Pn.; litus, Ov.; mare arboribus f-um, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>rūtis, is, f. = Aphrodite, Venus: Iscr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Frux <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fruor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fu</text:span> <text:line-break/>(fue), <text:span text:style-name="T4">Interj.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fy:</text:span></text:span> fu oboluisti allium, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fucatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fuco, I. Fucus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>ūcĭnus lacus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sjö i mellersta Italien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fuco, Fucosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Fucus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Fūcus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: v. gr. 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Färglaf:</text:span></text:span> phycos thalassion, id est f. marinus, Pn.; Aquinas, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Färgämne,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som bien hemta från blommor:</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Röd färg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (purpur); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">smink:</text:span></text:span> Tyrio f-o rubens, Ov.; color venustatis non f-o illitus, sed sanguine diffusus; sine pigmentis f-oque puerile, C.; mentiri colorem f-o, Qu.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smink</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= oäkta prydnader, grannlåt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">flärd, falskhet:</text:span></text:span> in oratoris cincinnis et f-o offenditur; sine fuco et fallaciis, more majorum negatur, C.; f-um facere alicui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(slå dunst i ögonen på någon),</text:span> Ter., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Färga bestryka, sminka:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> lanam Assyrio veneno, Vg.; tabula colore f-ta, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> unumquodque genus dicendi, quum f-atur, fit præstigiosum, Gell.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">isynn.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">part.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūcātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sminkad, oäkta, falsk:</text:span></text:span> f-a et simulata a sinceris et veris secernere; candor et rubor; nitor f., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūcōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">full af (smink) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">flärd; sminkad:</text:span></text:span> amicitia, merces, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infūcātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sminkad:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Offūcia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smink:</text:span></text:span> neque purpurissum neque cerussam neque aliam ullam o-am, Pt. Most. 254.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bländwerk, bedrägeri:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Fūcus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Drönare, wattubi:</text:span></text:span> f., ignavum pecus, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>ūfius, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">Subst.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fŭgio,</text:span> fūgi, fŭgĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fly:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">intrans.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">taga till flykten, flykta:</text:span> ex proelio, C.; testabatur (Cocles), nequidquam deserto præsidio eos f-re; non tentato certamine intacti f-runt; Romulus turbā f-tium actus, L.; oppido, Cs.; in montes Ct.; aper de cavea, Mt.; ex patria <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gå i landsflykt),</text:span> N.; fuge et - te eripe, Vg. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T4">transit.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fly för, undan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">från,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (öfwergifwa):</text:span> me inermem lupus f-it; quis exsul se quoque f-it?, Hor.; nos patriam f-imus et dulcia <text:soft-page-break/>linquimus arva; taurus aram saucius; auras aegra f-it; Dido germanum f-ens, Vg.; conspectum sceleratorum f-entes abdimus nos, C.; te, dea, te f-unt venti - adventumque tuum, Lucr.<text:line-break/>II.<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i local mening, om döda ting: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ila, ila bort; förswinna:</text:span></text:span> dextrā impulit puppim, f-it illa per undas ocior jaculo; f-ens per gramina rivus, Vg.; calor de corpore, Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om tid, tillstånd, egenskaper): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fly, förgå, förswinna;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om saker: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förlora sig, (skämmas):</text:span></text:span> tempus; optima quæque dies - prima f-it, Vg.; memoria, L.; ætas, Catl.; vita, Lucr.; f-it juventus et verecundus color reliquit ossa, Hor.; fugēre pudor verumque fidesque, Ov.; poma, Sen.; vinum f-ens, C. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fly, undfly, sky</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt ss. ondt, obehagligt l. orätt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undwika (wara rädd för), söka undgå, undandraga sig, taga sig till wara för, underlåta, låta bli (låta):</text:span></text:span> nuptias, Ter.; si curam f-imus, virtus f-enda est; congressus hominum f. et odisse; f. solitudinem, vituperationem tarditatis; nimias amicitias; ea f-it et reformidat oratio; laborem; f-da est injuria, talis sollertia, pecuniæ cupiditas; (perspicitur) quid sit propter turpitudinem f-dum; appetitus exsultantes sive cupiendo sive f-endo, C.; f-e magna: licet sub paupere tecto reges vitā præcurrere, Hor.; procurationem reipublicæ, N.; f. dicere; f., ne offeramus nos periculis sine causa; f-amus ab omni, quod abhorreat ab approbatione oculorum, C.; quid sit futurum cras, fuge quærere, Hor.<text:line-break/>4.<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undgå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> någons syn, uppmärksamhet, minne, kunskap; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">undfalla, wara obekant</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(glömmas):</text:span></text:span> tanta tenuitas, ut f-at aciem (oculorum); nisi quæ me forte f-unt, hæ sunt fere de animo sententiæ; nulla res hujus viri scientiam f. potest; numerus (orationis) f-it et prætervolat (auditores); non te f-it, omnium laudatarum artium procreatricem quandam esse philosophiam; huic rei me f-erat rescribere, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">poet., om orter, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dölja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förswinna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngns syn:</text:span> jam tandem f-entem prendimus Italiam, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭgiens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rädd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skyende:</text:span></text:span> laboris, Cs.; culpæ, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭga</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flykt:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> præceps, turpissima, C.; foeda, L.; in f-am se dare, convertere, conjicere, conferre; f-æ se dare, C., se mandare, Cs.; f-am capere, Cs.; capessere, L.; in f-am impellere aliquem, Cs.; in f-am vertere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(drifwa),</text:span> dare aliquem, C.; f-am parare, reprimere, C.; sistere f-am alicujus, L.; inhibere, Ov.; ex f-a retrahere aliquem, Sa.; f-æ servorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rymningar),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Landsflykt, -förwisning:</text:span></text:span> nobilitas multos ferro aut f-ā exstinxit, Sa.; Metelli, C.; f-ā puniri, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om lefwande och döda l. abstracta ting) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ilande, lopp, fart,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (snabbhet, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">flygt):</text:span></text:span> Harpalyce volucrem f-ā prævertitur Hebrum, Vg.; cervis f. data est, Lucr.; annorum series et f. temporum, Hor. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bemödande att undwika:</text:span></text:span> axilla factum est ala f-ā literæ vastioris; cavendum est, ne id bellandi magis f-ā quam utilitatis ratione faciamus; periculi f-ā committere, ut imbellis videaris, C.; in <text:soft-page-break/>vitium ducit culpæ f., si caret arte, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undflykt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (medel, utwäg till att undgå):</text:span> hanc ego ignominiam morte vitassem, si alia f. non esset, L.; non jam f. super ulla pericli, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förjaga, drifwa på flykten; drifwa i landsflykt:</text:span></text:span> hujus tertio consulatu Latini ad Veserim fusi et f-ti; homines lapidibus et ferro f-re, C.; classem, N.; equitatum, Cs.; hostes, Sa.; astra Phoebus, Hor.; patriā alqm, Lucr.; me Musa, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭgax</text:span>, ācis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Benägen att fly</text:span></text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">feg, skygg:</text:span></text:span> hostis f-simus; dux f., L.; mors et f-em persequitur virum, Hor.; cervus f.; caprea, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ilande, snabb; flygtig, förgänglig:</text:span></text:span> lympha f. trepidat rivo; eheu f-es labuntur anni, Hor; hæc brevia, f-ia et caduca existima, C.; poma Pn.; bona, Sen.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som skyr; skyende, rädd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för:</text:span> ambitionis, Ov., gloriæ, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭgācĭter</text:span>, -cius, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fegt:</text:span></text:span> vix rationem iniri posse, utrum a se audacius an f-ius ab hoste geratur bellum, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭgĭtīvus</text:span>,<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förrymd, förlupen,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som smyger sig från ngt.</text:span> servus, Sa.; f. a domino, a legibus, a jure, C.; f. rei familiaris, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. om saker (som undgå ngn):</text:span> retraham ad me illud f-um argentum, Ter.; amor, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T4">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rymmare, förrymd slaf</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> eller </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">soldat</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (desertör):</text:span> quae crux potest huic f-o satis supplicii afferre?, C.; ut sacerdotis f. liba recuso, Hor.; ea res per f -os Aemilii hostibus enuntiatur, Cs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭgĭtīvārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rymmares återhemtare,</text:span> Varr., Fl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭgĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fly undan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (undwika, undandraga sig), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sky:</text:span></text:span> miserrimus fui f-do, ne quis me cognosceret; patrem; conspectum alicujus, Ter.; hanc provinciam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(denna befattning),</text:span> Pt.; quæstionem, C. - <text:span text:style-name="T4">part.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adj.</text:span>: herus liberalis et f-ans <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(obenägen)</text:span> litium, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭgĭtor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som tager till flykten (i krig), springare:</text:span> credo, me - acrem f-em fore, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Aufŭgio</text:span> (ab <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> fugio), fūgi, (fŭgĭtum), 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fly bort, undan; rymma:</text:span></text:span> jam aliquantum ex eo loco - a-erat, L.; domo, Pt.; servus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confŭgio</text:span>, fūgi, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Taga sin tillflykt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till -:</text:span> in aram, in arcem; ad te, ad misericordiam, opem, fidem alicujus, C.; ad florentes opes Etruscorum, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Söka undanflykt i något:</text:span></text:span> scilicet eo c-ies, Ter.; illuc confūgit, ut diceret, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confŭgium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillflykt, tillflyktsort:</text:span></text:span> is est mihi, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēfŭgio</text:span>, fūgi, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fly ned, hän:</text:span></text:span> eo, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sky, undwika:</text:span></text:span> aditum ac sermonem alicujus, Cs.; injurias fortunæ; inimicitias, C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undandraga sig:</text:span></text:span> disputationem, ad quam juvenes te volunt accedere; munus a deo assignatum; auctoritatem rei <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(answaret för),</text:span> C.; non d-o, quin dicam, Varr.; periculum mortis, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Diffŭgio</text:span>, fūgi, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fly åt skilda håll, hit och dit:</text:span></text:span> metu perterriti d-imus C.; d-imus visu exsangues; d-unt comites, Vg.; ad præsidia, Cs.; domum; in vicos suos, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upplösa sig, förswinna:</text:span></text:span> vox in multas voces, Lucr.; d-ēre nives: redeunt jam gramina campis, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Diffŭgium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flykt åt skilda håll:</text:span></text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effŭgio</text:span>, fūgi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">intr.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fly undan, undkomma; undfly, undgå:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> de proelio; e manibus, C.; ex agris, Cs.; ex vinculis, N.; equitatum Cæsaris, Cs.; plagam; manus, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. men.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med personliga subj.:</text:span> vituperationem; hospitis speciem; crimen rei<text:span text:style-name="T4">;</text:span> poenas; hæc morte e-untur, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med sakl. subj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undgå, undfalla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> nihil te e-iet, atque omne, quod erit in re, occurret atque incidet, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effŭgium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undflykt; medel till undflykt:</text:span></text:span> e. mortis - apud aliquem assequi, C.; mali, mortis, Sen.; habere e-a pennarum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Interfŭgio</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fly emellan:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i tmesis),</text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfŭgio</text:span>, fūgi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fly öfwer:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på främmande område: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rymma öfwer:</text:span></text:span> ad asylum Romuli ex finitimis civitatibus turba omnis avida rerum novarum, L.; hostes ad nostros imperatores p-runt -; a Pompejo ad Cæsarem, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för säkerhets l. bistånds skull):</text:span> jam Tarquinii ad Porsennam p-rant; in fidem alicujus, L.; in Capitolium - ut eo subsidio utatur, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfŭga</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerlöpare,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från ngn:</text:span> a Pyrrho p. senatui est pollicitus, se regi venenum daturum; initio proditor, deinde p., C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfŭgium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillflykt, tillflyktsort:</text:span></text:span> domus tota spectat in nos solos nec potest aliud habere p.; salutis p. et præsidium; fortunæ miseræ hic locus p.; portum paratum nobis et p. putemus; domus, commune p., C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undflykt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= ursäkt):</text:span> illo desperatissimo p-o (utebatur), se imprudentem fecisse, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prŏfŭgio</text:span>, fūgi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fly bort</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i hast, hals öfwer hufwud), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skynda sig undan:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intr.</text:span>: a domino agresti et furioso; domo; in exsilium; in oppidum devium, C.; turbato ludicro mæsti parentes virginum p-un<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">t,</text:span> L.; formidine pars ad Romanos, p. ad Bocchum p-rant, Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fly ifrån,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i flykt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">öfwergifwa:</text:span></text:span> conspectum alicujus; irritamenta, Sen.; agros civitas, Hor.; sedes suas, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prŏfŭgus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På flykt stadd, flyende, flyktig:</text:span></text:span> milites Jugurthini p-i discedunt, Sa.; ex proelio, T.; vinculorum, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flyktig = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Biltog, kringirrande; hemlös:</text:span></text:span> urbe, domo p-i, Vg.; <text:soft-page-break/>Trojani Aenea duce p-i, Sa.; Evander p. ex Peloponneso, L.; Scythæ, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfŭgio</text:span>, fūgi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fly tillbaka, undan; draga sig tillbaka:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intr.</text:span>: Syracusas classe amissa; ad legatos; vitis a brassicis tanquam nocentibus r., C.; ad urbem, L.; hostes velocissime r-bant; ex cæde, Cs.; sanguis timido, C.; r-it a litore templum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(synes för dem, som närma sig, draga sig inåt landet),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T4">transit.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Draga sig tillbaka för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> impetum armati, C.; draconem attollentem iras, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rysa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skygga, draga sig tillbaka; sky, hafwa owilja för</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> r-it animus et reformidat dicere, C.; multa tibi possum præcepta referre, ni r-is -; meminisse horret animus luctuque r-it, Vg.; ab hoc genere sermonis semper r-ūgi; a dicendo ingenuo quodam pudore r-isti; a te admonendo; periculum, C.; jurgia, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">inf.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(Tweka,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wägra):</text:span> Polyhymnia tendere barbiton, Hor. <text:line-break/>c. ea memoriam r-unt meam, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfŭgium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillflykt, -s-ort:</text:span></text:span> silvæ dedere r., L.; senatus fuit regum, populorum, nationum portus et r., C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfŭgus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillbakaflyende, som drager sig, sjunker tillbaka:</text:span></text:span> r-os sequi, T.; captavit undam r-am (Tantalus); flumen r., Ov.; amnis, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Subterfŭgio</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Undfly, undandraga sig; undgå:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intr.</text:span>: mihi is, Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: periculum, crimen, poenam, militiam simulatione insaniæ; id imprudentiam ejus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Suffŭgio</text:span>, fūgi, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fly, söka skydd inunder:</text:span></text:span> imber - in tecta s. coēgit, L. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fly</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = ej wara åtkomlig för, ej fattas af:</text:span> natura deorum manuum tactum, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Suffŭgium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillflykt, skjul, skydd:</text:span></text:span> subterranei specus, s. hiemi et receptaculum frugibus, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Transfŭgio</text:span>, fūgi, fŭgitum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rymma öfwer, gå öfwer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till fiende:</text:span> ad hostes, L., N. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> ab afflicta amicitia, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Transfŭga</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerlöpare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från ngn:</text:span> t. senatui dixit -, C.; nec orator Hannibalis nec t. ad vos Saguntinos veni, L.; t. divitum partes linquere gestio, Hor.; proditores et t-as arboribus suspendunt Germani, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Transfŭgium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rymning, öfwergång</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till fienden:</text:span> L., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fulcio,</text:span> si, tum, 4.:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stödja, uppbära, hålla uppe:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> vitis, - nisi f-ta est, ad terram fertur, C.; domus f-ta columnis, Ppt.<text:line-break/>2.<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttryck:</text:span> labentem rempublicam; porticum Stoicorum f. Chrysippus; qui ruunt, f-endi sunt; imperium gloriā f-tum esse debet et benevolentia sociorum, C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(Hålla wid makt, stärka):</text:span></text:span> cibis corpus, Lucr.; vino venas, Sen.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tränga, beklämma:</text:span></text:span> ærumnis f-ta, Ps. I. 78.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulcīmen</text:span>, mĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulcīmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stöd:</text:span></text:span> terra nullo f-ine nixa pendet aëre subjecto, Ov.; desertum f-tis suis, Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulcrum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(Stöd), säng-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">soffstolpe</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">-fot;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> meton.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">säng:</text:span></text:span> lucent genialibus toris aurea f-a, Vg.; liberi Claudii ad f-a lectorum sedentes vescebantar, Su.; sacrum; nobile, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulmenta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stöd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till en byggnad:</text:span> Cato.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skoklack:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stöd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (stolpe, colonn):</text:span> Vitr., Sid.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fultūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stödjande, stöd:</text:span></text:span> f. et substructio, Col. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> stomacho ruenti f., Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effultus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">part.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stödd, hwilande på:</text:span></text:span> tergo bidentium, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infulcio</text:span>, si, tum, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Instoppa, tillfoga:</text:span></text:span> cibum alicui, Su.; verbum epistolae, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Praefulcio</text:span>, si, tum, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(framtill stödja, tränga); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På förhand bereda stöd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hjelp:</text:span></text:span> magnis miseriis p-or, Pt.; illud p-ci et præmuni, ut annui simus (in provincia), C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Suffulcio</text:span>, si, tum, 4.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(under-) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stödja, uppbära, uppehålla, hålla wid makt:</text:span></text:span> porticum columnis; cibo artus, Lucr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sätta under ss. stöd:</text:span></text:span> mento columnam, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>ulfŭlæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">samnitisk stad.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fulgeo,</text:span> si, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulgo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixtra:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: personl. och opersonl.:</text:span> Jove f-ente; si f-serit, C.; f-it, Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om andra lysande föremål: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixtra, glimma, glänsa, blänka:</text:span></text:span> tecta auro et ebore; is purpurā, C.; caelo f-bat luna sereno; sidera nautis, Hor.; gladii, L.; stella, sidus, Vg.; dies, Ov.; gemma, Lucr.; illæ, quas f-ĕre cernis in armis, Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Framblixtra, -stråla:</text:span></text:span> indoles virtutis in eo, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulgens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixtrande, strålande; utmärkt:</text:span></text:span> arma, Vg.; f-ior astris, Cd.; juvenis f-simus, Vell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulgenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På ett blixtrande sätt; med glans:</text:span></text:span> color radiat, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulgĕtrum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixt, Luftsken:</text:span></text:span> Sen., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulgĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixtrande, glimmande:</text:span></text:span> sidus; fax, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulgor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixtrande, blixt, sken, glans, ljus:</text:span></text:span> ea, quae faciunt f-em; f-em cernimus ante, quam tonitrum accipimus, Lucr.; f. Jovis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(planeten Juppiters);</text:span> auri, C.; purpurae, Pn.; solis, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> nominis, Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulgur</text:span>, ŭris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixt, ljungeld:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanligen ss. blott </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sken:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> fulmen): f-a fiunt, Lucr.; emicant, Ct.; f-a et tonitrua, C. Div. II. 44.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixtstråle, blixt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som slår ned, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">åskwigg:</text:span></text:span> cadunt caelo sereno, f-a, Vg.; f-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(deras betydelse)</text:span> interpretari; caeli f-a (de Legg. II. §. 21), C.; feriunt summos f-a montes, Hor.; condere, procurare f., Juv., Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulgŭrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixt-,</text:span></text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som handlar om</text:span> fulgurum procuratio: liber, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulgŭrio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixtra:</text:span></text:span> Næv. - <text:span text:style-name="T4">part.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulgŭrītus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">träffad af blixt:</text:span></text:span> arbor, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulgŭro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixtra, glänsa:</text:span></text:span> Jove f-ante, C.; f-at <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det blixtrar),</text:span> Pn.; domus auro, St.; ignis oculis, Sil.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulgŭrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixtrande:</text:span></text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulgŭrātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som försonar l. tyder blixtslag:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēfulgŭro</text:span>, 1.: (<text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixtra ned:</text:span></text:span> Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Praefulgŭro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixtra fram:</text:span></text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixt, ljungeld,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> enl.</text:span> Cic. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. nedslående </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">blixtstråle, åskwigg:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> si nubium conflictu ardor se expressus emiserit, id esse f., (de Div. II. §. 44); Jupiter f. emittit, jacit in medium mare; f-e percuti, percelli; f-is ictu deflagrare; Cyclopes fabricantur f-a C.: f-e ici, L.; f-a torquet Jupiter; f-is alis afflavit Anchisen deorum pater, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: (betecknande ngt ss. på en gång glänsande och förfärande, förkrossande):</text:span> fortunæ f-a contemnere; duo f-a nostri imperii, Cn. et P. Scipiones, C.; duo f-a domum meam perculerunt, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt: om blixtrande, ljungande föredrag:</text:span> (orator) nec acumine posteriorum nec f-e utens superiorum, C.; Ciceronis f-a, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulmĭneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>;<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixt-, blixtens</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. af blixten:</text:span> ignis, Ov.; ictus, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ljungande, krossande:</text:span></text:span> ensis; Mnestheus, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulmĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixtra (slå ned), ljunga,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (eg. o. oeg.):</text:span> manus Jovis f-antis, Hor.; fortuna f-at, Ov.; oculis f-re, Ppt.; Cæsar ad Euphraten bello, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulmĭnātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">part.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Träffad af blixten:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fulmĭnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixtrande:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">(<text:span text:style-name="T2">Affulgeo</text:span>), fulsi, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stråla emot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> någon</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T4">alicui</text:span>), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. och oeg. uttryck:</text:span> lux quaedam civitati a-sisse visa est; spes, fortuna a-sit alicui, L.; instar veris vultus tuus a-sit populo, Hor.; Venus (stella), Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumfulgeo</text:span>, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rundt omkring stråla:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effulgeo</text:span>, si, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stråla, blixtra fram, fram ur ngt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ur en massa = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">öfwerstråla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr.</text:span> excello):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg..</text:span> sol inter graves nubes, L.; Pallas nimbo e-ens et Gorgone saevā; nova lux oculis e-sit, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> fama majorum conspectum Persea efficiebat, sed e-bant Philippus ac Magnus Alexander, L.; sensus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(reflexion)</text:span> arguta et brevi sententia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tanke, innehåll),</text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Interfulgens</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">part. praes.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixtrande, strålande emellan:</text:span></text:span> aurum argentumque cumulo rerum aliarum i-ens, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Offulgeo</text:span>, si, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blixtra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">stråla till mötes, emot</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T4">alicui</text:span>): hic primum nova lux oculis o-sit et ingens visus ab Aurora caelum transcurrere nimbus, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Praefulgeo</text:span>, si, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stråla framför, öfwerstråla allt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr.</text:span> praepotens, praevalens), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. och oeg.: -</text:span> ne aut occaecentur tenebris imagines <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i mnemoniken)</text:span> aut splendore peant, C.; equus p-ens dentibus aureis Vg.; nitor smaragdi collo p-et tuo (corvi), Phdr.; viginti clarissimarum imagines familiarum ducebantur (in funere), sed p-bant Brutus et Cassius, eo quod non visebantur, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfulgeo</text:span>, si, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Återstråla, kasta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett strålande </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">återsken; stråla, glänsa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> Canis (stella), C.; Castoris et Pollucis simul alba nautis stella r-sit, decidunt venti fugiuntque nimbi; Jovis tutela r-ens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om planeten Juppiter),</text:span> Hor.; dixit et avertens roseā cervice r-sit Venus, Vg.; arma L.; humus luce, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> fama, Pp<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">t.;</text:span> certa spes, Vell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fŭlĭca,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭlix</text:span>, ĭcis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sothöna:</text:span></text:span> Pn., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fūlīgo,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sot:</text:span></text:span> abstergere, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">smink:</text:span></text:span> Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fulix <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fulica.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fullo,</text:span> ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klädesstampare,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> - l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">walkare; filtförfärdigare:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr. Rich):</text:span> Pt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fullōnĭcus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fullōnius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stampares:</text:span></text:span> pila f-ca, Cato; saltus, Sen.; creta, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fullōnĭca</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stampares yrke; stamp:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Cato.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fullōnium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stamp, stampqwarn:</text:span></text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fulmen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fulgeo.<text:line-break/>Fulmenta, -mentum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fulcio.<text:line-break/>Fulmin. . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fulmen, Fulgeo.<text:line-break/>Fultura <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fulcio.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>ulvius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>ulvia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Clodii, sedan triumviren Antonii hustru.<text:line-break/></text:span>Fulviānus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>ulviaster, stri, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Fulvii eftersägare:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fulvus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mörkgul, gulröd; mörk:</text:span></text:span> nuntia f -a Jovis mirandā visa figurā, C. poēt.; leo; lupa; aurum; iaspis; oliva, Vg.; divitias alius f-o sibi congerat auro, Tib.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fūmus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rök:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> pernas in f-o suspendere, Cato; f-o excruciare alqm, C.; f. evolvitur; f-i incendiorum, Cs.; f. erigitur; undat mixto pulvere; it ad auras; terra exhalat nebulam f-mque, Vg.; lacrimosus, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttr.:</text:span> f-os vendere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(narra),</text:span> Mt.; vertere bona in f-um et cinerem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(låta uppgå i rök, förtära),</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūmārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rökhus</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för win:</text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūmeus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rökig:</text:span></text:span> lumina tædis, Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūmĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rökande, rökig; rökfärgad, luktande ss. af rök:</text:span></text:span> tæda, Vg.; tecta Ov.; cautes; virus, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūmĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som bringar, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utkastar, framhwirflar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> rök:</text:span> Cacus glomerat sub antro f-am noctem, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūmĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: id.: Pt., Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūmĭfĭco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Röka, antända rökelse:</text:span></text:span> Dianæ Arabio odore amoene, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūmĭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sprida rök, röka; genomröka:</text:span></text:span> globi f-antes, Gell.; mellarius alvos apium, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Suffūmĭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inunder röka, genomröka:</text:span></text:span> alveum apium, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūmo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Röka, ånga, dunsta:</text:span></text:span> terra calens, C.; villarum culmina; ex humo f-at Neptunia Troja; pulvere campi; equi sudore, Vg.; ara, Hor., Catl.; atria ignibus, Ov.; nasus ursi, Mt.; obsonia, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infūmātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inrökad:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Transfūmo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ånga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> fram, ut:</text:span> anhelitus (equorum), St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūmōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Full af rök, inrökad, nedrökad:</text:span></text:span> imagines <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(anbilder af wax, hwilka stodo i</text:span> atrium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid härden);</text:span> flamma, C.; perna, Hor.; focus; cadus, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Funalis, -nale, Funambulus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Funis. <text:line-break/>Functio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fungor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Funda,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slunga:</text:span></text:span> f-ā vulnerari; f-is glandes jacere, Cs.; stridentem f-am adductā habenā circum caput egit - et liquefacto plumbo hostis tempora diffidit, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kastnät:</text:span></text:span> amnem verberare f-ā, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Penningepung:</text:span></text:span> Mcb.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fördjupning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för stenen i en ring:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fundĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slunga:</text:span></text:span> aliquem; verba, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fundĭtor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slungare:</text:span></text:span> (Baleares), L.; Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fundam. . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fundo, Fundus. <text:line-break/>Fundanus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fundi.<text:line-break/>Fundat. . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fundo, Fundus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>undi, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sjöstad i Latium.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Fundānus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Fundāni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inw. i F.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fundito, -ditor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Funda.<text:line-break/>Funditus, Fundo (1.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fundus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fundo,</text:span> fūdi, fūsum, 3.: <text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gjuta:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ut-, framgjuta;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">strömma, flyta:</text:span></text:span> sanguinem e patera; sanguis in corpore fusus, vina pateris; vina fusa vertunt se in cruorem, Vg.; maculas fudit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(plumpat)</text:span> incuria, Hor.; imber repente fusus, L.; urinam f.; fluvius in Rhenum f-itur, Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gjuta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= bilda af flytande massa):</text:span> fusum durius, Hor.; imaginem <text:soft-page-break/>ex ære f., Pn. <text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gjuta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om icke flytande föremål), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utösa, -hälla; fösa, kasta, nedslå, utsträcka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i liggande ställning):</text:span> se f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> f-di = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Strömma ut, framhwimla:</text:span></text:span> luna se per fenestras <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(inströmmade),</text:span> Vg.; segetem corbibus in Tiberim, L.; picem, Cs.; corpora septem humi; Numanum manu <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(nedskjuta);</text:span> agmina plenis se f-unt portis; apes f -untur circum lilia, Vg. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> (poēta) puro simillimus amni f-et opes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utbreda sina skatter)</text:span> Latiumque beabit divite lingua, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sprida, utbreda;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">refl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sprida, utbreda sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i sinl. och öfwerförd bet.):</text:span> f-re, quæ natura contracta sunt, Qu.; vitis in omnes partes nimia f-itur; quodam tempore homines fusi per agros vagabantur; justitia se in ceteras virtutes; orator se; virtutes et vitia crescere negant: attamen utrumque f-i quodam modo et dilatari putant; id non debet in omni oratione æquabiliter fusum esse; tactus toto corpore fusus est, C.; Elysii campi fusi in omnem partem, Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om härar: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slå,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= bringa i oordning, förströ):</text:span> hostium copias; exercitum; Latini fusi fugatique sunt, C.; exercitum f-it fugatque; fusi primo impetu et clamore hostes, L. <text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Alstra, frambringa, föda:</text:span></text:span> terra f-it flores, fruges, bacas, legumina; spici frugem; ova, piscium fetum; beluam te, non hominem mater, C.; tellus Neptuno equum; Maja Mercurium, Vg.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ljud, tal, sång (med lätthet, ymnighet och liksom owilkorligt): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gifwa ifrån sig, utstöta, låta utströmma, utösa, ösa ur sig;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i inspiration) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">uttala, dikta, sjunga:</text:span></text:span> inanes sonos; voces; vastum clangorem; poētarum more verba, C.; preces; ore loquelas, Vg.; opprobria rustica, Hor.; physicorum oracula; grave plenumque carmen; versus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūsus</text:span>, -ior, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flytande, ledig, jemn, lös; wid, widlyftig, ymnig:</text:span></text:span> genus dicendi liquidum, f-um, profluens, C.; corpora Gallorum candida et f-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> astricta = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fast, senig),</text:span> L.; toga, Su.; materia, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūse</text:span>, -ius, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Widlyftigt, bredt:</text:span></text:span> f-e dicere; hoc uberius disputantur et f-ius, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūsĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Flytande, smält, gjuten:</text:span></text:span> argilla, Cs.; aurum, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utbredning:</text:span></text:span> C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūsōrium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ränna:</text:span></text:span> coquinæ; balnearum, Pall.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūsūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smältning, gjutning:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūsus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utgjutande, -strömmande:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Affundo</text:span>, fūdi, fūsum, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gjuta till, på;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">strömma, flyta till, wid:</text:span></text:span> aquam rei; amnis oppido, Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> colonia amne a-sa = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid- i. e. delwis) kringfluten,</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Foga, sluta, sälla till; gifwa;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tränga sig intill:</text:span></text:span> equites cornibus a-bantur; vim vitalem a. alicui, T.; genibus alicujus a-i, Fl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumfundo</text:span>, fūdi, fūsum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gjuta ngt omkring;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Strömma omkring:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. lac c-itur Pn.; nubes c-sa repente se scindit, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kringgjuta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ngt med ngt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kringströmma:</text:span></text:span> cerā c. corpus <text:soft-page-break/>mortuum, N.; terra mari c-itur; aër terram c-it, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> eos dea multo nebulæ c-ūdit amictu, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om menniskor) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Strömma, skocka, sluta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig omkring -:</text:span> hostes c-untur ex reliquis partibus, Cs.; obviis (<text:span text:style-name="T4">dat.</text:span>) c-bantur sciscitantes, L.; tergis Germanorum c-di, T.; undique visendi studio Trojana juventus c-sa ruit, Vg. - variæ et undique c-sæ molestiæ, C.; collo parentis c-sus, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Omgifwa; kringhwärfwa, -ränna, omringa:</text:span></text:span> Pompejus præsidiis c-sus sedet; magna luce, crassis tenebris c-sum esse, C.; hostium concursu, copiis c-i, N.; eques c-ūdit, frontem pedites invasere, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confundo</text:span>, fūdi, fūsum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammangjuta -fösa, ösa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> unā multa jura, Pt.; cibum in venas; ignis se cum igne, C.; vinum in vasa, Col.; lacrimas suas cum alterius, Ov.; Alphēus undis Siculis (<text:span text:style-name="T4">dat.</text:span>) c-itur, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammansmälta, sammanslå,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> innerligt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förena, hopsätta; blanda, sammanblanda, inblanda:</text:span></text:span> oratio e pluribus c-sa videtur; hæc tria, genere c-sa, cogitatione distinguunt; decorum totum est cum honestate c-sum; cuperem utrumque, sed est difficile c.; in oratione omnes sunt quasi permixti et c-usi pedes; est id quidem in totam orationem c-endum, C.; duos populos in unum, in unum corpus c., L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i förwirring </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanföra, -blanda, förwirra, bringa i oordning (upplösa, förstöra, utplåna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en saks form):</text:span> vera cum falsis, C.: rusticus urbano c-sus, Hor.; patres (connubio plebis et patrum) jura gentium c-i rebantur; signa et ordines, L.; fas jusque, Ov., foedus, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">andligen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förwirra, bringa ur fattning, förbrylla, göra förlägen:</text:span></text:span> ipsum quoque c-runt dicentem; c-di animo, maerore, L., dolore, Pn., pudore, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confūsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förwirrad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i yttre och andlig men.); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bestört, förlägen:</text:span></text:span> onusti cibo et vino perturbata et c-a cernimus; oratio c-a, C.; strages, Vg.; vultus; animus; c-us animo L.; pavor c-ior, Pn.; spectandi (ludos) c-sĭmus et solutissimus mos, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confūse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I massa, utan åtskilnad; förwirradt, utan ordning:</text:span></text:span> partes argumentandi c. dispersimus: mox descripte digeremus; c. loqui; c-ius res acta est, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confūsaneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hoprörd, -blandad:</text:span></text:span> doctrina, Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confūsim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span> = confuse, Varr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confūsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammansmältning, -blandning, -slående:</text:span></text:span> virtutum conjunctio et c.; suffragiorum, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förwirrad blandning, förwirring, upplösning:</text:span></text:span> religionum, temporum, vitæ, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">andlig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förwirring, bestörtning, förlägenhet:</text:span></text:span> oris, T.; (animi), Pn., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Inconfūsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ordnad, oförbryllad, -willad:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēfundo</text:span>, fūdi, fūsum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gjuta, hälla,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (tappa) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ösa ned, af:</text:span></text:span> aliquid in vasa, Col.; vinum; Copia fruges pleno cornu Italiæ; mero d-so <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(medelst libation)</text:span> prosequi aliquem, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Diffundo</text:span>, fūdi, fūsum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gjuta, låta rinna, sprida</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt skilda håll;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">refl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">strömma, sprida sig:</text:span></text:span> sanguis per venas d-itur in omne corpus; aqua tepefacta se d-it, C.; vina d-sa (sc. in amphoras e dolio, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">uttappadt),</text:span> Hor., Juv.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sprida, utbreda;</text:span></text:span> luce d-sa; C.; radices arbor, Varr.; venatrix comas dederat d-re ventis, Vg.; dii vim suam longe lateque d-unt C.; bella et paces longum in ævum d. (scribendo), Hor.; morbus d-itur a capite, oratio in immensum, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra upprymd, glad;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">blifwa glad:</text:span></text:span> animum alcui; vultum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wisa ett gladt ansigte),</text:span> Ov.; virtus et bonis amici d-itur et incommodis contrahitur, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Diffundĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sprida, förskingra:</text:span></text:span> ea, quae ipsus optimă omnis labores invenisset perferens, amoris vi d-ri ac didier (a filio), Pt. prol. ad Mercat. 54.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Diffūsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wida utbredd, widsträckt; stor:</text:span></text:span> platanus patulis d-a ramis; error d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(allmän);</text:span> benevolentia, C.; meritum d-ius, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spridd, oordnad:</text:span></text:span> jus civile, quod nunc d-um et dissipatum est, in certa genera cogere, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Diffūse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ströwis, utan ordning:</text:span></text:span> res d. et disperse dictæ, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Diffūsĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utsträckt, utbredd:</text:span></text:span> aether, Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Diffūsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: animi, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upprymdhet,</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effundo</text:span>, fūdi, fūsum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utgjuta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Strömma ut, strömma öfwer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sina bräddar:</text:span> sanguinem pro patria; lacrimas; mare nec redundat nec e-itur, C.; lacrimas; imber nubibus e-sus; Nilus stagnans e-so flumine, Vg.; amnis e-itur in oceanum, super ripas, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">act.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utskaka, ut-, afkasta, utdrifwa, -wräka, -ösa, (i massa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">i hast) utföra:</text:span></text:span> anulos; vim telorum in alqm; equus equitem; equo e-i, L.; animam e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppgifwa);</text:span> auxilium alicui castris apertis, Vg.; saccos numorum in deserto Aristippus, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Strömma, rusa ut:</text:span></text:span> se in agros, Cs.; se civitas ad aliquem, C.; currus carcere e-itur, Vg.; hostes plenis repente portis e-si, L.; oppido e-sum est vulgus, Sa.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utösa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förslösa, -spilla, uttömma, plundra:</text:span></text:span> bona per luxuriam; fortunas; collectam gratiam; ærarium, C.; laborem, Vg.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Alstra, frambringa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (rikligt):</text:span> segetes non solum fruges e-unt, sed etiam herbas inimicissimas frugibus; ea ætas hanc copiam oratorum e-udit, C.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Säga ut; yttra, utösa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ord l. tankar och känslor i ord:</text:span> e-udi vobis omnia, quæ sentiebam; testis e-udit omnia, quæ voluit; odium C.; iram, furorem in aliquem, L.; voces, Vg.<text:line-break/>f. se e. l. e-di, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utgjuta, -tömma sig i; hängifwa sig åt -, wara omåttlig i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> nos lacrimis e-si <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(simmande i),</text:span> Vg.; ad preces <text:soft-page-break/>lacrimasque; ad luxuriam; in licentiam, L.; in nos; in aliqua libidine se continere, in alia e-re, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effūsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wid, widsträckt:</text:span></text:span> e-um late mare, Hor.; incendium; cædes, L.; loca, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om härar o. s. w.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upplöst, oordnad, spridd; hejdlös</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om flykt); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wild, blind;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Omåttlig, ohejdad:</text:span></text:span> e-os hostes invadere, Sa.; occasio multos simul et e-os adoriendi; improvidi e-o cursu insidias superaverunt; lætitia; licentia, L.; studium e-simum, Su.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slösande, slösaktig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">act.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bet.):</text:span> quis in largiendo e-ior?, C.; honores; largitio, N.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effūse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Widt och bredt, widt omkring:</text:span></text:span> ire, Sa.; vastare; is finis tam e. vagandi Etruscis fuit, L. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ohejdadt; blindt, utan återhåll; omåttligt:</text:span></text:span> multo e-ius (quippe vera fuga) oppidum repetebant, L.; animus exsultat, C. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slösaktigt, utswäfwande:</text:span></text:span> domare; vivere, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effūsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utgjutande:</text:span></text:span> aquæ, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">menniskors </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utströmmande:</text:span></text:span> hominum ex oppidis, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utkastande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af penningar; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">slösande, slöseri:</text:span></text:span> e-es pecuniarum, quæ fiunt ad multitudinem leniendam; ejus in alios e-io, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hänförelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af glädje):</text:span> animi e. in laetitia, in dolore contractio, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infundo</text:span>, fūdi, fūsum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingjuta, inhälla, ingifwa; gjuta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på l. öfwer:</text:span> in vas alqd.; sororis filio venenum, C.; sincerum est nisi vas, quodcunque i-is, acescit; alicui poculum, Hor.; i-am his commixta grandine nimbum, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Begjuta:</text:span></text:span> olivam aceto, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sinlig men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ösa, kasta i, på, öfwer, in:</text:span></text:span> hordea jumentis, Juv.; agmina in Græciam, Ct. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Införa, insmyga;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">intränga, insmyga sig:</text:span></text:span> vitia in civitatem principes; in aures orationem; in alienum genus i-i; in civitatem peregrinitas, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infundĭbŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tratt:</text:span></text:span> Cato, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Qwarnskruf:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infūsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingjutande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lavement):</text:span> Pn. -<text:line-break/>(<text:span text:style-name="T2">Infūsus</text:span>), <text:span text:style-name="T4">abl.</text:span> u, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ingjutande, begjutande:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Interfundor</text:span>, fūsus, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rinna, strömma emellan:</text:span></text:span> Styx i-sa coërcet, Vg.; i-sa nitentes vites aequora Cycladas, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bestänkas med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt (i mellanrum):</text:span> genas maculis i-sa, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Offundo</text:span>, fūdi, fūsum, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gjuta, sprida, utbreda för, framför, öfwer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i eg. o. bildl. uttr.):</text:span> aquam, Pt.; nobis aër crassus o-itur; noctem rebus; tenebras reipublicæ; animis caligo o-sa est, C.; oculis caliginem; pavorem hostibus, L.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(Öfwergjuta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> något med något), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skymma, fördunkla; träffa, slå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngns sinne med ngt:</text:span> luce solis lumen lucernae o-itur; meum pectus memoria ejus o-udit, C.; pavore o-sus, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfundo</text:span>, fūdi, fūsum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwergjuta:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerstänka, fukta, bada, dränka:</text:span></text:span> aquā alqm., C.; cruore p-sus, L.; greges flumine p. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bada);</text:span> sanguine currum p.; vestes ostro p-sae <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(färgade),</text:span> Vg.; puer liquidis p-sus odoribus, Hor.; cubiculum sole p-itur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwerströmmas af -),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> studiis p-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(blott fuktas),</text:span> non tingi, Sen.; papavera p-sa somno <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dränkta i sömn</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fulla af sömngifwande kraft),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Betäcka, -kläda, beströ:</text:span></text:span> tecta auro, Sen.; canitiem pulvere, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om känslor: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerfara, öfwerströmma,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (kittla), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">genomtränga; fatta, betaga;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bada, simma i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -;</text:span> cor frigore leti p-sum Lucr.; horror me p-udit; animum voluptate; sensus jucunditate p-untur, C.; animum religione, metu p., L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfūsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwergjutning:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfūsōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ytlig:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prŏfundo</text:span>, fūdi, fūsum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fram-, utgjuta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (rikligt, utan aktsamhet l. återhåll, jfr.</text:span> projicio), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">låta framströmma:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> sanguinem suum; vim lacrimarum; lacrimae se, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kasta framåt, kullslå, framkasta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">, framskjuta, framstöta (ljud);</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skjuta fram, störta fram, bryta fram:</text:span></text:span> præcipitem in terram p-i, Lucr.; vocem; clamorem; facilius in vitibus revocantur ea, quæ se nimium p-runt; nihil est in natura rerum, quod se universum p-at; voluptates - compressæ subito se p-unt, C.; multitudo se, Cs.; in questus se p-re, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sedl. hänseende: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Släppa lös, lemna fritt spel åt:</text:span></text:span> cavendum est, ne nimium omnia p-amus et ad turpitudinem delabamur, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utösa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngt:</text:span> odium in alquem, C. <text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utkasta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">offra, hängifwa, uppoffra; förspilla, förslösa:</text:span></text:span> divitias, Sa.; omnes vires ingenii animique p-udi; se totum in alqm; vitam pro patria; pecuniam in res; patrimonia effuse largiendo; laborem, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prŏfūsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utsträckt, lång:</text:span></text:span> cauda, Varr.; p-ior, Pall.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slösaktig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om personer och saker):</text:span> sui p., Sa.: sumptus; epulæ; nepos, C.; p-simus quisque, Su.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: (lössläppt, ej tillbakahållen), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hejdlös, tygellös, fri:</text:span></text:span> hilaritas, C.; libido p-sima, Su.; vox, Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prŏfūse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utan återhåll, strömwis:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frikostigt, rundligt:</text:span></text:span> ædes p. exstructa; dies festos p-sime celebrare, Su.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ohejdadt, blindt, widt och bredt:</text:span></text:span> eo p-ius omnibus modis quaestui ac sumptui deditus erat, Sa.; p. (prope fuse, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Mdvg)</text:span> tendentibus in castra consul obstitit, L.; p. laudare, Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prŏfūsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förslösande, slöseri:</text:span></text:span> divitiarum, Su.; nimia, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfundo</text:span>, fūdi, fūsum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gjuta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (kasta) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillbaka;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">återströmma, -swalla, swalla </text:span></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fram och åter:</text:span></text:span> stellæ vapores trahunt ex terra et r-unt, C.; tenebrosa palus Acheronte r-so; Oceanus r-sus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som strömmar tillbaka i sig sjelf, i krets);</text:span> imis vadis stagna r-sa sentit Neptunus; alga illisa lateri scopuli r-itur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(swallar, kastas af wågen tillbaka),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>2. refundi = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">utbreda sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (bakåt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">inåt landet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr.</text:span> reductus): campi, Sil.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">återkasta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">återställa:</text:span></text:span> Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">uppskjuta, förkasta:</text:span></text:span> Cd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfūse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: r-ius egesta humus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(löst?),</text:span> Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfūsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillbakaströmmande:</text:span></text:span> humoris, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Suffundo</text:span>, fūdi, fūsum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gjuta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (utbreda) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">under, inunder; hälla in, fylla på;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">strömma inunder:</text:span></text:span> aquam, Pt.; animum dicunt esse sanguinem cordi s-sum, C.; ruborem virgineum ore, Vg.; merum in os mulæ, Col. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> cibo s-re vires, Varr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Under, inunder fukta, begjuta,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> fylla med en wätska:</text:span> oculos lacrimis s-sa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med ögonen fyllda af tårar),</text:span> Vg.; rubore s-di = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rodna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af blodets uppstigande),</text:span> L., Ov., Pn.; tepido rore s-it lumina, Ov. <text:line-break/>3. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Färga, genomdränka; genomtränga, fylla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt, isynn. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: agricola minio s-sus, Tib.; oculi s-untur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(få starr),</text:span> Sen.; æther calore s-sus, C.; homo felle s-sus, Pn.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> animus s-sus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(genomträngd af)</text:span> malevolentia, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Suffūsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. underströmning, genomsprängning:</text:span> fellis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gallsjuka);</text:span> oculorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(starr),</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sŭperfundo</text:span>, fūdi, fūsum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gjuta, ösa (kasta)</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt öfwer ngt;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">refl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">strömma öfwer,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i eg. o. oeg. men.:</text:span> unguentum alicui rei, Pn.; terra s-sa scamnis, Col.; vim telorum, T.; circus s-so Tiberi irrigatus; gens montibus s-sa; s-ens se lætitia, fama, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Begjuta, öfwergjuta; öfwerhölja:</text:span></text:span> rem oleo, Col.; nube ipsa operient ac s-ent equites equosque, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sŭperfūsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gjutande, utbredande öfwer:</text:span></text:span> aquarum, Amm.; pavimenti, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Transfundo</text:span>, fūdi, fūsum, 3.; 1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gjuta, ösa öfwer:</text:span></text:span> (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i annat rum):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> alqd in vasa, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerflytta; utbreda:</text:span></text:span> suas laudes in alqm.; amorem in aliam; studia latius, C.; eorum mores in Macedonas, Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Transfūsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ösning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i annat kärl (omtappning), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förflyttning:</text:span></text:span> Pn., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fundŭlae,</text:span> ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Återwändsgränd:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fundulus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fundus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fundus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Botten:</text:span></text:span> armarii; largitio f-um non habet, C.; Nereus imo ciet æquora f-o; res Phrygias vertere f-o, Vg.; sera est parsimonia in f-o, Sen.<text:line-break/>2. = quod mitti potest fundā, Qu. VIII. 6. 73. (inc. l.)<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grundegendom, jordegendom, jordagods:</text:span></text:span> optimus; obire f-os <text:soft-page-break/>suos, C.; haec est nostri f-i calamitas, Ter.; cultus, paternus, Qu.<text:line-break/>4. = auctor, Paul. Diac. p. 89. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som antager, godkänner en sak:</text:span> populus f. fit legis Romanae = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">antager den till efterlefwande, efterföljd:</text:span> C. pro Balbo VIII. 21. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i privata förhållanden:</text:span> is mihi conveniundus, ut, quae cum filio egi, ei rei f. sit pater potior, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fundĭtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Från grunden; i grund, alldeles:</text:span></text:span> perdere, Pt.; perire, Ter., Hor.; pessum dare, Lucr.; ædificium f. delere, tollere; interire; alqm perdere,; fidem tollere; id amicitiam f. evertit, e vita tollit; f. repudiare alqd, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På bottnen:</text:span></text:span> subsidere, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fundo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förse med botten; grunda, grundlägga:</text:span></text:span> navem, Pt.; arcem, Vg. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i materiel men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fästa, fastgöra:</text:span></text:span> ancora dente tenaci f-bat naves, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grunda, grundlägga, befästa; säkert nedlägga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om penningar), placera:</text:span> rempublicam; disciplina accurate non modo f-ta, sed etiam exstructa; illud maxime imperium nostrum f-vit; nihil religione testatum, nihil veritate f-tum, C.; urbem legibus, Vg.; pecunia f-ta nitidis villis, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fundātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Säker, fast:</text:span></text:span> familiæ f-issimæ ruinæ, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fundāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: (Vg.; Ov.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fundāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grundwal, grund:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i egentl. uttr.:</text:span> agere f-a ædificii; ponere, jacere; alqd constituere f-is, C.; f-a locare; f-ina ponere favis, Vg.; f. subdere per solidum, T.; arcem a f-is disjicere, N.; locare f-a in loco stabili, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttr.:</text:span> f. justitiæ fides; f. virtutum; philosophiæ; f-a pacis, defensionis, causæ, libertatis; virtutum f-a in voluptate tamquam in aqua ponere, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fundātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: ædium Vitr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fundātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grundläggare:</text:span></text:span> urbis, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fundŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kolf:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Korf:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prŏfundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Djup:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> mare, C.; pontus; Manes, Vg.; p-æ altitudinis convallis, Vg.; Tartara, Sen.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Djup, bottenlös, omätlig:</text:span></text:span> libido; avaritia, Sa.; gurges, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Djup</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = som sträcker sig långt inåt l. uppåt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hög:</text:span></text:span> silva, Lucr.; caelum, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prŏfundum</text:span>, i <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Djup:</text:span></text:span> esse in p-o aquæ; jacere se in p-um; natura veritatem abstrusit in p-o, C.; vastum p., Sil.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prŏfunde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Djupt:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prŏfundĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Djup, djuphet:</text:span></text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Funebris, Funer. . ., Funest. . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Funus.<text:line-break/>Funetum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Funis.<text:line-break/>Funginus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fungus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fungor,</text:span> functus sum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(påwerkas,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> afficieras) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lida, (utstå), genomgå, njuta</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T4">re,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sällan</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">rem</text:span>): fortunas suas, Pt.; quodcunque per se erit, aut faciet quid aut aliis fungi debebit agentibus ipsum: at facere et f-i sine corpore nulla potest res; inane ab ictu non f-itur hilum; animus contagibus corporis multa mala f-itur, Lucr.; laboribus; ter ævo f-tus Nestor, Hor.; morte, fato, vitā f-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= dö),</text:span> Ov., Val.; simulacra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> corpora f-ta sepulcris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= begrafna);</text:span> dapibus f-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(njuta),</text:span> Ov.; fato, Qu.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förrätta, fullgöra, öfwa:</text:span></text:span> more barbarorum (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">följa),</text:span> N.; muneribus corporis; munere interpretis; oculo f-untur munere suo; perfecto justitiæ f-i officio; officiis servorum f-i; in omni munere f-do, C.; boni viri officium f-i, Ter.; f-ar vice cotis; virtute f-i, Hor.; virtute; rhetoris officio, Qu.; partibus judicis, Pn.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i politiska förhåll.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bekläda, förwalta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett embete:</text:span> munere, Cs.; ædilitate, C.; consulatu, Su.; honoribus; militare munus, N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utgöra, erlägga, bestrida:</text:span></text:span> statuendum est, quid aratorem in rep. muneris f-i et sustinere velitis, C.; eo sumptu respublica f-itur, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Functio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förrättande, -ning:</text:span></text:span> muneris vel corporis vel animi, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēfungor</text:span>, functus, 3: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwerstå, stå öfwer, utstå, lida</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T4">re</text:span>): periculo, C.; corpora morbis d-ta salubriora esse coeperunt; poena non levi; proelio; curā, L.; malis, Su.; vita d-ta corpora <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= döde),</text:span> Vg.; temporibus suis d-tus, Hor.; morte d-tus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och absol.</text:span> d-tus = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">död,</text:span> Ct., Ov., Su.<text:line-break/>2. d-i <text:span text:style-name="T4">aliqua re</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Komma ifrån ngt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på bekostnad af, för priset af ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">göra sig fri</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med offret af - -:</text:span> mendacio, C.; unius poenā patribus d-dum erat; civitas d-ta est plurimorum morbis, perpaucis funeribus, L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fullgöra; bekläda; erlägga, betala:</text:span></text:span> imperio regis, L.; honoribus; tribus decumis pro una, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēfunctōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som göres blott för att komma ifrån saken, ss.</text:span> opus operatum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">deraf), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slapp, likgiltig:</text:span></text:span> ictus, Petr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēfunctōrie</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfungor</text:span>, functus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genomgå, utstå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">njuta,</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">aliqua re</text:span> l. <text:span text:style-name="T4">aliquid</text:span>: omnia p-tus vitai praemia marces, Lucr.; molestiā; bellō; periculis; bonis omnibus, C.; curā; fato, L., epulis, Ov. - <text:span text:style-name="T4">part. præt.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bet.:</text:span> memoria p-ti periculi, C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Alltjemnt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">till slut förrätta, fullgöra, bekläda:</text:span></text:span> dum in corpore inclusi sumus, munere quodam necessitatis et gravi opere p-imur; honoribus amplissimis et laboribus gravissimis; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.:</text:span> judices se jam p-tos esse arbitrabantur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fullgjort sitt wärf),</text:span> C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfunctio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fullgörande, förrättande; beklädande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till slut):</text:span> laborum p., dolorum perpessio; primus annus a p-e honorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hans embetsmannabanas afslutande),</text:span> C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfunctōrie</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lösligen:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fungosus, Fungulus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fungus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fungus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swamp, murkla:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> f-i ita conditi, ut nihil possit esse suavius, C.; f-orum origo ex pituita arborum, Pn.; pratenses, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pundhufwud, stock, dumhufwud:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hopgyttring</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af den brinnande weken i en lampa:</text:span> putres concrescunt f-i, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fungīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swamp-:</text:span></text:span> pol iste f-o genere est: capite se totum tegit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om en mska med bredskyfwig hatt),</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fungōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swampig, pipig.</text:span></text:span> medulla, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fungŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liten swamp:</text:span></text:span> Apic.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Funiculus, Funirepus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Funis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fūnis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>, Lucr.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr.</text:span> Qu. I. 6. 5. 8.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lina, tåg, rep:</text:span></text:span> f-es, qui antennas ad malum destinabant, Cs.; f. laxus, contentus; tortum sequi, ducere f-em <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gå i ledband, föra l. styra det),</text:span> Hor.; cannabinus, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūnālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: equus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sidohäst,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> eg. som går i lina, (ej under ok):</text:span> Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūnāle</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tåg, streck:</text:span></text:span> L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fackla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af rep):</text:span> crebro f-i et tibicine delectabatur Duilius, C.; noctem f-ia vincunt, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lampställning, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Candelaber:</text:span></text:span> f. densum lampadibus coruscis, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūnambŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: (ambulo) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūnĭrēpus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: (repo); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lin- (-krypare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">), -wandrare, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">-dansare:</text:span></text:span> Ter., Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūnētum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Löfsal, topphäck</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af winträd):</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūnĭcŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Streck, litet rep:</text:span></text:span> C.; Qu. I. 6. 6.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fūnus,</text:span> ĕris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jordefärd, likbegängelse, sorgetåg,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">begrafning:</text:span></text:span> in f-us prodire; f. procedit, Ter.; indicere, facere, ducere, ornare f.; venire in, convenire ad f.; exsequias f-is prosequi; paterno f-i justa solvere; f. funestum, perluctuosum; maeror f-is, C.; Dionysius vidit nullius ex suis f., N.; celebrare f. alicui, L.; tria f-a concurrunt in foro, Hor.; dicique beatus ante obitum nemo supremaque f-a debet, Ov.; instauramus Polydoro f., Vg.; portā triumphali ducebatur f. Augusti (Ann. I. 8 ff.); f-um nulla ambitio apud Germanos, T.; quum semel infernas intrarunt f-a leges, non exorato stant adamante viae, Ppt. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lik; död, dödsfall, manfall, förlust; undergång, förderf:</text:span></text:span> lacerum, Vg.; juvenum et senum mixta densentur f-a, Hor.; - crudeli f-e exstingui; ut te post multa tuorum f-a - aspicimus!, Vg.; civitas defuncta est plurimorum morbis, paucis f-bus, L.; quanta f-a moves Dardanæ genti?, Hor.; discessus meus dicitur f. reipublicæ, C., regina (Cleopatra) Capitolio f. parabat, Hor.; Gabinius et Piso, duo reipublicæ portenta ac paene f-a, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūnĕbris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: till likbegängelse hörande, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Begrafnings-:</text:span></text:span> epulum, vestimentum, contio, C.; justa, ludi, L.; pompa, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dödsbringande, förödande, förderflig:</text:span></text:span> bellum, Hor.; malum populis f., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūnĕrālis</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūnĕreus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span> = funebris:<text:line-break/>a. frons, fax, Vg.; ludi f-es, Ter.<text:line-break/>b. torris Altheæ, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūnĕro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utföra till grafwen, jorda, begrafwa:</text:span></text:span> f-ri sestertiis M, Pn.; f-tus amplissime est, Su.<text:line-break/>2. prope f-tus (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dödad)</text:span> arboris ictu, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūnestus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som hör till likbegängelse l. sorgeskrud:</text:span> tæda, Vg.; fax, C.; capilli, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">der lik finnes, deraf:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af lik) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oskärad, oren, menlig:</text:span></text:span> quæ finis f-æ familiæ, (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på sorgen efter afliden);</text:span> ignes nefarios et f-os templis deorum inferre, C., f-ā familiā dedicare eum templum non posse, L.; domus, Ov.; principes, Pn.; dies f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(olycksdag)</text:span> cladis Alliensis, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Af farsot hemsökt; ödelagd, öde, utdöd:</text:span></text:span> agri Atheniensium, Lucr.; annales velut f-i præter nomina magistratuum nihil suggerunt, L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Olycksbringande, förderflig, sorglig:</text:span></text:span> dies senatui, reipublicae pestis; victoria orbi terrarum f-a; auctio; ensis, C.; bellum; nuptiæ, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūnesto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oskära:</text:span></text:span> deorum aras humanis hostiis; contionem contagione carnificis, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fuo,</text:span> fui, fŏre, <text:span text:style-name="T4">part. fut.</text:span> fŭtūrus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blifwa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> defectivt verbum, hwilket mest brukas att ersätta de bristande perfect- och supinformerna af</text:span> esse, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">neml.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T4">præs. conj.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr Neue, lat. Formenlehre</text:span> p. 465): (fuam), fuas, fuat, fuant = sim <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o. s. w.:</text:span> obsecro, ne matri adversus fuas, Liv.; quid fuat (= futurum sit) me <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af mig),</text:span> nescio, Pt. Mil. 299. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Fl.; ofta hos</text:span> Pt. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Ter. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i uttrycket</text:span> fors fuat = forsitan: Ter. Hec. IV. 3. 4.; Tros Rutulusve fuat, nullo discrimine habebo, Vg.; Lucr.; L. in prisca formula XXV. 12.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T4">inf. præs.</text:span> fore = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skola wara</text:span></text:span> (futurum esse) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">blifwa.</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="T4">impf. conj.</text:span> forem = essem: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wore, skulle wara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (äfwen i periphrastiska tempora):</text:span> immortales mortales flere si foret fas, flerent divae Camenae Naevium poētam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(saturnisk vers), Naevii grafskrift;</text:span> quid foret Iliae Mavortisque puer, si taciturnitas obstaret meritis invida Romuli, Hor. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr Madv. lat. Sprogl.)</text:span> <text:line-break/>4. fūvi (Enn. ap. C. de Or. III. §. 168), fūi (Pt. Mil. 755 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Fl.), wanl.</text:span> fŭi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med deraf härledda tempora),</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">perf.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o. s. w. till</text:span> esse = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blef, war; har blifwit; har warit:</text:span></text:span> nos sumus Romani, qui fuvimus ante Rudini, Enn. ap. C.; quid opus fūit istoc tanto sumptu nostra gratia?, Pt.; bis post Numam Janus clausus fuit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(har warit);</text:span> posita fuit statua Navii in gradibus curiae, L.; qualis tum patronus fuit justitiae contra accuratam orationem Phili, C.<text:line-break/>5.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭturus</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adj.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blifwande, kommande, tillkommande:</text:span></text:span> non modo praesentia, sed etiam f-a bella delevit; f-o oratori opus est -, C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">periphrastiskt till bildande af former för relativa futura i finita modi och inf. (jfr för öfrigt</text:span> Sum).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Sammansättningarna af</text:span> Fore <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Sum.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fūr,</text:span> fūris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjuf:</text:span></text:span> nocturnus, diurnus, C.; f-es estis ambæ, Pt.; quid domini facient, audent quum talia f-es (ɔ: servi)?, Vg.; f., latro, adulter, Hor.; f. es, Pedio, Ps.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūrīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: forum f-um, non coquinum, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūror</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stjäla:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> in f-do manibus uti; f. alicui aliquid, ab aliquo, C.; ex Capitolio alqd, Su.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. (= med orätt tillegna sig, undandraga ngn ngt o. s. w.):</text:span> civitatem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(borgare-rätt),</text:span> C.; fessos oculos labori f., Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūrātrīna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjufweri:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūrax</text:span>, ācis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjufaktig:</text:span></text:span> servus; manus f-simæ, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūrācĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjufaktighet, böjelse för att stjäla:</text:span></text:span> auri, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūrācĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjufaktigt:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Suffūror</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smått stjäla, snatta:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Furtim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förstulet, oförmärkt, i smyg:</text:span></text:span> lagenæ f. exsiccatæ; senatus consultum f. factum, C.; humor in genas f. labitur, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Furtīvus</text:span>. <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stulen, undansnappad:</text:span></text:span> mercari virgines f-as, Pt.; res, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förstulen, lönlig, hemlig:</text:span></text:span> amor, Vg.; iter, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Furtīve</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förstulet:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Furtum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjufgods, stulet ting:</text:span></text:span> f-a Syracusis exportare sine portorio, C.; f-a ligurrire, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stöld, tjufweri, snatteri:</text:span></text:span> f-i se alligare, Ter.; f. apertum erat; f. facere, C.; f. jocosum, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smygande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hemlighållande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">list, knep:</text:span></text:span> f-o lætari inani; rem abscondere f-o; belli f-a, Vg.; cessationis f-a quærere, C.; noctis f-a, Pt.; alicujus f-a deprehendere, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stulen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lönlig älskog, umgänge:</text:span></text:span> dulcia Veneris f-a, Vg.; e f-o genitus, Sil. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Furtĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjufaktig:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūruncŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liten tjuf:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blemma:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Knöl på träd:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Trĭfur</text:span>, fūris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stortjuf:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Furacitas, - citer, Furatrina, Furax <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Furor, Fur.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Furca,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(redskap att lyfta ngt ned) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjufwa, tjuga, gaffel:</text:span></text:span> bicornis, Vg.; f-<text:soft-page-break/>is detrudere, Cs.; naturam f-ā expellas, tamen usque recurret, Hor.; bicorni f-ā levare (lardum e tecto pendens), Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stötta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (klufwen l. twåhornad), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bock</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hwaraf ngt stödes l. uppbäres):</text:span> f-is sublevare retia; rei subdere f-as, Pn.; f-æ spectacula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bänkarne på circus)</text:span> sustinentes, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">straff-redskap: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sax</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hwari hufwudet instacks) (Marquardt</text:span> V. 1. 192); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kåk, galge:</text:span></text:span> f-am ferentem per circum duci et virgis cædi. C.; cervicem f-æ inserere, Su.; sub f-a vinctum cædere, L.; sub f-am ire, Hor.; figi in f-a, Pn.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bergsklyfta, paß:</text:span></text:span> F-æ Caudinæ, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Furcĭfer</text:span>, fĕri <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som får bära saxen), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Galgfågel:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Ter., C., Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Furcŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stöd, stötta:</text:span></text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Furcilla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjufwa:</text:span></text:span> f-is extrudi, C., ejici præcipitem, Catl.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Furcillo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gifwa formen af en tjufwa (ett</text:span> V): Varr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stödja:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Bĭfurcus</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Trĭfurcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med twå, tre horn l. spetsar:</text:span> vallus b., L.; ramus b., Ov.; stirps t., Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Bĭfurcum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twåudd; winkel:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Trĭfurcĭfer</text:span>, fĕri, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(trefaldt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Erkeskälm:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Furenter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Furo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Furfur,</text:span> ŭris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kli:</text:span></text:span> alere sues f-e, Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fnas, skabb:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Furfŭreus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är af kli:</text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Furfŭrōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kli-artad l. -färgad:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Furia, Furial. . ., Furibundus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Furo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>ūrīna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en romersk gudomlighet:</text:span> Varr. <text:line-break/>Fūrīnālis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: flamen, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Furinas prest,</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūrīnālia</text:span>, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hennes högtid:</text:span> Enn., Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Furinus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fur.<text:line-break/>Furio, Furios. . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Furia, Furo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>ūrius, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn på en romersk</text:span> gens, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwartill M. Camillus hörde.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūriānus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Furnaria <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Furnus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">F</text:span>urnius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn på en romersk</text:span> gens.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Furnus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> ferveo?) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ugn;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sersk.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bakugn, bageri:</text:span></text:span> panem torrere in f-o, Pt., Ov., Pn.; f-os et balnea laudare ut fortunatam plene praestantia vitam; a f-o lacuque redeuntes pueri anusque, Hor.; balneolum Romae, Gabiis conducere f-um, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Furnāria</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bageri:</text:span></text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Praefurnium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ugnshål:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fŭro,</text:span> (fŭrui), 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. bete sig såsom </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förryckt, ursinnig, rasa; yra, swärma</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af sinnesrubbning l. af tillfällig sinnesrörelse): </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om menniskor:</text:span> Solon, quo vita sua tectior esset, f-re se simulavit; insanire et f. omnibus videtur; Alcmæonem, Orestem, Ajacem f-re (non insanire) dicimus; f. et bacchari; valetudinis vitio (melancholici) f-unt; is audaciā f-it; Pansa de Clodio; f-it, se vexatum esse <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(deröfwer att),</text:span> C.; recepto amico dulce est f-re; Inachiā f-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(swärma för),</text:span> Hor.; f-it Dido <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af kärlek);</text:span> f-it Sibylla, Vg.; Empedocles, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om andra subj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rasa:</text:span></text:span> venti; ignis, Vg.; stella vesani leonis, Hor.; freta, Ct. - copia argenti f-uit vita, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭrenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I raseri, wansinnigt:</text:span></text:span> irasci, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭria</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">plur.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Yra, galenskap, raseri, (förbittring; fräckhet):</text:span></text:span> in f-as agitari; justis f-is surrexit Etruria; ob Ajacis noxam et f-as, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hämnde-, plågoande, Furia;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mera sällan tänkt ss. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">frestare,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> frestande l. förförande </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">djefwul):</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> F-æ deæ speculatrices et vindices facinorum ac scelerum; (impios) agitant insectanturque f-æ non ardentibus tædis, sicut in fabulis, sed angore conscientiæ et fraudis cruciatu, C.; f-æ sororis ac viri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hämndandar),</text:span> L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> Tarquinius Superbus muliebribus instinctus f-is, L.; illa pestis ac f. patriæ, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭriālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som härleder sig fr. Furierna, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Furie-lik, djefwulsk:</text:span></text:span> cædes, Ov.; voces f-es in contionibus mittere, C.; sacerdotes incessu f-i milites turbavere; carmen f-e, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭriālĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Som en furia; djefwulskt:</text:span></text:span> odisse, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭrio</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra ursinnig, försätta i raseri</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">yra:</text:span></text:span> libido equas, Hor.; mens f-ta, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭriōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Galen, förryckt, ursinnig, rasande, yrande:</text:span></text:span> si f. escit -, XII. Tabb.; vecors, f., mente captus; mulier non morbo, sed scelere f-a; homines f-i, vinolenti <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> siccus, sanus), C.: bello f-a Thrace, Hor.; contiones f-simæ, C.; amor f-ior, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭriōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ursinnigt:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭrĭbundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Yrande, swärmande; rasande, ursinnig:</text:span></text:span> hariolorum f-æ prædictiones; homo, C.; leo, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭror</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ursinne, galenskap, raseri</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. sjukdom och ss. öfwergående effect):</text:span> f. est mentis ad omnia cæcitas (insania est stultitia sanitate vacans); f. effrenatus et præceps; inflammatus; f. Cethegi in cæde bacchantis; captus f-e; in f-em agi; f. considit; redire ad f-em, C.; f. Belgarum rebellantium, Cs.; ira f. brevis est; caecus, Hor.; hos inter medius venit f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rasande fiendskap),</text:span> Vg.; f. auri, Sen.; quis f., o socii, quae tanta insania, cives, gentibus invictis Latium praebere cruorem?, Luc.; f. caeli, Catl.; sistere f-em, St.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hänförelse,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> inspirationens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">yra:</text:span></text:span> sine f-e negat Democritus quenquam magnum poētam esse, C.; f. Sibyllae, Vg.; fatidicus, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kärleksyra, -förwillelse:</text:span></text:span> Didus, Vg.; mille puellarum, puerorum mille f-es, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Interfŭro</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rasa emellan:</text:span></text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perfŭro</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rasa fram, igenom</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> incensus, Vg.; domum, St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Praefŭro</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wildt rasa:</text:span></text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Furor (oris) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Furo.<text:line-break/>Furor (ari), Furt. . ., Furunculus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fur.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Furvus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swart, mörk, hemsk:</text:span></text:span> hostiæ, Val.; antra, Ov.; Proserpina, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fuscator <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fusco, Fuscus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fuscĭna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Treudd, treuddigt spjut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. attribut för Neptunus l. ss. gladiatorswapen):</text:span> deo dant f-am, C.; sumpta f-a omnes interemit, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fuscitas, Fusco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fuscus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fuscus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mörk, swart:</text:span></text:span> nubila, Ov.; cornix, C.; f-æ noctis alæ, Vg.; Nilus, Pn.; vestis, Mt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om röst: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oklar, hes:</text:span></text:span> vox, C., Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fuscĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fusco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mörkfärga, swärta, fördunkla:</text:span></text:span> cutem olivo, St.; corpora campo, Ov.; diem, Vfl.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fuscātor</text:span>, ōris <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fördunklar, skymmer:</text:span></text:span> Luc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infuscus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swartaktig:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Infusco</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swärta, färga swart, förmörka:</text:span></text:span> vellera; arenam sanie, Vg.; aquam, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ljud: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fördunkla:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Besmitta, förderfwa, skämma:</text:span></text:span> eos barbaries <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i språket)</text:span> non i-verat; vicinitas malevolentiā non i-ta, C.; saporem, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Praefuscus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mycket mörk:</text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Suffuscus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mörklett; swartaktig:</text:span></text:span> T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Suffuscŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Fuse, Fusilis, Fusio, Fusorium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fundo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fusterna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfre delen af en gran:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fustis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stake; käpp, prygel:</text:span></text:span> recisos f-es portare domum; f-em impingere alicui; vertēre modum formidine f-is; f-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> f-bus agere, repellere, mulcare alqm, vapulare, C.; f-e coërcere pueros, Hor.; f-e cædere, percutere, Vell.; f-i necare, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fustim</text:span>, (<text:span text:style-name="T4">acc.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss.)</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: f. necare (inc. lectio), Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fustĭtŭdĭnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: insulæ (ubi homines f-e tunduntur), Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fustuārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prygelstraff</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i arméen):</text:span> C., L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Fusura, Fusus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(adj. och subst., gen.</text:span> us) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fundo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fūsus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> fundo?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ten, nåck</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (den delen af sländan, på hwilken det spunna garnet nedflyter):</text:span> versare pollice f-um, Ov.; f-is pensa - devolvere, Vg.; f-i Parcarum, Vg., Catl.; torquere f-um; lanam f-o tenuare in fila, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fūtĭlis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enl.</text:span> Fs. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">besl. med</text:span> fundo: f-es sunt, qui silere tacenda nequeunt, sed ea effundunt):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lös, slapp, skör:</text:span></text:span> glacies, Vg.; canis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(löslifwad),</text:span> Phdr.; ictus, Su. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Usel, obetydlig fåfänglig; grundlös, otillförlitlig, characterslös:</text:span></text:span> servus, Ter.; sententia; alacritas; haruspex; homines sordidos, vanos, f-es odi C.; auctor, Vg.; competitor, Gell.; res f-es et frivolæ; causa, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūtĭle</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förgäfwes:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fūtĭlĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grundlöshet:</text:span></text:span> hæc sunt plena f-is, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(Fūtio,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">obsol.</text:span> Prisc.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effūtio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utsqwallra; frampladdra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wräka af sig):</text:span> foris alqd, Ter.; ex tempore alqd; temere de mundo; vaticinia temere e-ta, C.; versus leves, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fūtis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: = vas aquarium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> fundo): Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(Fūto,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">obsol.</text:span> Futare id est arguere (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">beslå, wederlägga),</text:span> Fs.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confūto</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dämpa, nedslå, kufwa:</text:span></text:span> coquus ahenum (fervens) truā, Varr.; dolores aliqua re; audaciam alicujus, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wederlägga, häfwa:</text:span></text:span> dictis alqm, Ter.; argumenta Stoicorum; opinionem; levitatem C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confūtātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wederläggning:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfūto</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: med handling l. ord </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillbakaslå, tillbakawisa, afwisa:</text:span></text:span> nationes bello; cupiditatem, libidinem, conatum, bonitatem alicujus, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med skäl </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wederlägga:</text:span></text:span> domesticis testibus alqm; contraria r., nostra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(påståenden)</text:span> confirmare; oratio re magis, quam verbis r-ata; maledicta alicujus, C.; id res r-at, Lucr.; oratione alqm, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfūtātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wederläggning:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfūtātōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som tjenar till, innehåller wederläggning:</text:span> Jct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕfūtātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">abl.</text:span> -u: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wederläggning:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fŭtuo,</text:span> 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Öfwa samlag, besofwa:</text:span></text:span> Hor., Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭtūtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭtūtor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Fŭtūtrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Confŭtuo</text:span>, 3. = futuo <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēfŭtūtus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Diffŭtūtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: futuendo corruptus: Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Effŭtuo</text:span>, 3.: aurum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">genom otukt förslösa,</text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Futurus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Fuo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>abăli, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkslag i Gallien:</text:span> Cs. b. G. VII. 7.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Găbălus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Galge; galgfågel:</text:span></text:span> Varr., Cap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gābătae,</text:span> ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skål, fat:</text:span></text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ăbii, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Latium.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Găbīnus <text:line-break/>(Găbiensis, Pn.), <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gabinsk, Gabinare.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ăbīnius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">romerskt slägtnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Găbīniānus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ādes, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad (phoenicisk coloni) i Spanien = Cadix.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gādītānus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">pl.</text:span> -i, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Gaditanerne.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gaesum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">galliskt spjut:</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ætūlus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gætūli, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folk i Africa:</text:span> fera G. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">elephant,</text:span> Juv.; gentes G-æ, Pn. <text:line-break/>Gætūlia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gajus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cajus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ălæsus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i södra Italien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ălătæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Galater (grekiskt namn på Celterne = lat.</text:span> Galli <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> Celtæ), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">isynn. de i Asien bosatte.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gălătia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det asiatiska) Galatien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gălătĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ălătēa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f..</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grekiskt namn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gălaxĭas</text:span>,ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en ädelsten:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wintergatan:</text:span></text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>alba, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enl.</text:span> Su. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. = mal):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">galliskt namn:</text:span> Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">cognomen för en afdelning af</text:span> gens Sulpicia; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dertill hörde</text:span> Serv. Sulp. Galba, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den sjette af Roms imperatorer</text:span> T. <text:line-break/>Galbiānus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Galbănum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en art wälluktande gummi (galban) och busken, hwaraf den fås:</text:span> faces g-o illitæ, Su.; dat g. Syria e ferula, quam (modo) ejusdem nomine, modo stagonitin appellant Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Galbăneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: odores, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Galbănus,</text:span> l.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Galbĭnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gröngul, ljusgrön:</text:span></text:span> Juv. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">omtalas ss. en af allwarsamt folk skydd färg på kläder - deraf:</text:span> fuscos habet colores (vestis), mores g-os, Mt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Galbănātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">klädd i ljusgrönt:</text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Galbĭna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn på fågel:</text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Galbeum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">armband:</text:span> Cato. <text:line-break/>b. = lanā involuta remedia, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Galbianus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Galba.<text:line-break/>Galbin. . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Galbanus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Galbŭla,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Galgŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gulspink:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Galbŭlus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">cypreßnöt:</text:span> Varr. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en fågel:</text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gălea,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hjelm, stormhatt:</text:span></text:span> aenea, C.; aurea; insignis conus g-æ, Vg.; ferina (e pellibus), Vfl.<text:line-break/>2. Africana (gallina) rutilam g-am et cristam capite gerit, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Găleāria</text:span>, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: ante g-ribus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(peruker?),</text:span> non personis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(masker)</text:span> utebantur (histriones), ut qualitas coloris indicium faceret aetatis, quum essent aut albi (senes?) aut nigri (adolescentes liberi) aut rufi (servi; cfr Ter. Phormio I. 2.: si quis me quaeret rufus -), Diom. Gramm. p. 489 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Keil;</text:span> g-ia a galearum similitudine dicta, Paul. Diac. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> galērus).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Găleo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Påkläda hjelm;</text:span></text:span> milites g-ri jubet, Cs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Găleātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hjelm-klädd, - rustad:</text:span></text:span> Minerva, C.; g-um sero duelli poenitet, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Găleŏla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. liten hjelm) hjelmformigt dryckeskärl:</text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gălēna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blyglans:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ălĕōtæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags teckentydare på Sicilien:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gălērus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sällan -</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gălērum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hufwa, låg hatt:</text:span></text:span> g. est sacerdotis pileus ex pelle cæsæ hostiæ, Serv.; flavo g-o abscondere nigrum crinem, Juv.; g. gladiatoris, Su.; Neronis (faciem dissimulantis) g., Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gălērĭcŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hufwa:</text:span></text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Peruk:</text:span></text:span> Su. Otho 26. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gălērītus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klädd i hufwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">stormhatt:</text:span></text:span> Ppt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gălērīta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tofslärka:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Galgulus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Galbula.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ălĭlæi, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inw. i</text:span> <text:line-break/>Galilæa, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett landskap af Palæstina.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Galla,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Galläple:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Gallus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>allæcus, l, <text:line-break/>Gallăĭcus <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn på ett folkslag i Spanien (Gallicier):</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gallæcia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Gallicien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gallia, Gallicanus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Gallus. <text:line-break/>Gallicinium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> IV. Gallus.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Gallicus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Gallus.<text:line-break/>Gallin. . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> IV. Gallus.<text:line-break/>Gallo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Gallus.<text:line-break/>Gallogræci, -græcia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Gallus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>allus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>alla, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">pl.</text:span> -i, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Galler</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om personer äfwen ss. adj.: gallisk:</text:span> Cs. b. G. I. 42. V. 48.), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">latinska benämningen för Celterne i Italien, Frankrike, Asien m. m. (gr.</text:span> Celtæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> Galatæ): Cs., C., T. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i inskränktaste mening namn för det folk, som bodde mellan Sequana och Garumna.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>allia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gallien,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> landet mellan Pyrenæerne och Rhen</text:span> (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Frankrike, Belgien och en del af Holland samt Schweitz):</text:span> G. omnis, tota, Cs. b. G. I. 1. 7. VI. 11. 13. <text:line-break/>2. G. ulterior <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> transalpina = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">romerska provinsen G. före Cæsars krig, d. w. s. landet mellan Alperna och Rhodanus:</text:span> Cs. b. G. I. 10.<text:line-break/>3. G. citerior l. cisalpina = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">norra Italien mellan Alperna och Rubicon:</text:span> Cs. b. G. VI. 1. <text:line-break/>Gallĭcus <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gallisk:</text:span></text:span> vocabulum G-um alauda, Su.; bellum G-um, Cs.; ager G. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i Italien),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gallĭca</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gallisk sko (galosch):</text:span> C. <text:line-break/>Gallĭcānus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gallisk (som hör till l. finnes i</text:span> G. cisalpina): legiones; ager, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>allogræci, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Galaterne i mindre Asien:</text:span> L. <text:line-break/>Gallogræcia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: L., Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>allus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Cybeles prest, från Phrygien:</text:span> Su.; Ov. Fasti IV. 361.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gallo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">part.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gallans</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fanatiskt swärmande, ss. en</text:span> Gallus: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">III. <text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>allus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Phrygien:</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">IV. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Gallus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tupp, hönstupp, hane:</text:span></text:span> g. gallinaceus; g. cantat ante lucem, C.; g. in suo sterquilinio plurimum potest, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gallĭcĭnium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: (cano): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hangäll</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. tid):</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gallīna</text:span>, ae, f.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Höna:</text:span></text:span> parit ova, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gallīnāceus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af hönsslägtet l. af höns, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Höns-:</text:span></text:span> gallus; fel, C.; pullus, Varr. - <text:span text:style-name="T4">Subst.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gallīnāceus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hönstupp:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gallīnārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är för l. har att göra med höns, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Höns-:</text:span></text:span> curator <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hönswaktare),</text:span> Varr.; vas, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gallīnārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hönsgård, -hus:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gamba,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hof:</text:span></text:span> Veg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gambōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjockhofwad:</text:span></text:span> Veg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ămēlio, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">månad i attiska calendern (15 Jan.</text:span><text:line-break/>15 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Febr.):</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gammarus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cammarus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gānea,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gāneum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Krog, källare; swirande, rummel:</text:span></text:span> g-arum nidor, C.; agere vitam in g-a, Pn.; abduci in g-um, Ter.; lubido stupri, g-æ, Sa.; inter g-am et stupra, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gāneārius</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: triclinium, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gāneo</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Krogkund, rumlare:</text:span></text:span> cincinnatus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>angărĭdæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">indiskt folk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>anges, is, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Indien:</text:span> Ov. <text:line-break/>Gangētĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gangētis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A. f.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gangraena,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kallbrand:</text:span></text:span> Lucil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gannio,</text:span> 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bjebba, gläfsa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: om hundar l. räfwar:</text:span> asini rudunt, canes g-unt, pulli pipant, Fs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: om mskor:</text:span> g-it et obloquitur, Catl.; quid ille g-it? Ter.; in secretam aurem g-re, Ps.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gannītus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bjebbande, gnällande:</text:span></text:span> canum, Lucr.; allatrare et g-bus lacessere, Mt.; morientis Nereidis g., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Obgannio</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Oggannio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bjebba emot, mumla:</text:span></text:span> alicui aliquid; ad aurem, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ăny̆mēdes, is, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Jupiters munskänk, af örnen röfwad på Ida, son af konung Laomedon i Troja:</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Găny̆mēdēus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ărămantes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folk i Africa.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gărămantĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gărămantis</text:span>, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: nympha G. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(garamantisk),</text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>argānus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg i Apulien.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gargānus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: G-um mugit nemus, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>argăphĭē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">orts-namn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>argăra, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg och stad i Mysien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gargărizo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gargărisso</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gurgla sig, gurgla:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gargărizātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gargărizātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gurglande:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>argettus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">demos i Attica.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gargettĭus = Epicurus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Garrio,</text:span> 4.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om naturljud: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Qwittra, qwaxa:</text:span></text:span> luscinia, Ap.; ranæ, Mt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om mskor: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pladdra, prata:</text:span></text:span> philosophi in gymnasiis; quidquid in buccam venit, g-re; plura, C.; nugas, Pt.; fabellas aniles, Hor.; alicui in aurem, Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Garrŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Qwittrande; pratsjuk, pratsam, sladderaktig; sqwallrare:</text:span></text:span> hirundo, Vg.; lingua; psittacus Ov.; mulier, Ter.; percontatorem fugito: nam g. idem est, Hor.; fama, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Garrŭlĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pratsamhet, -sjuka:</text:span></text:span> extemporalis, Qu.; Ov. Met. IV. 249.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gărum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: v. gr.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fisksås, caviar:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ărumna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Gallien, Garonne.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ărumni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Aquitanskt folkslag.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ates, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: id.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gaudeo,</text:span> gāvīsus sum, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Semidep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara glad, fröjda sig, wara förnöjd, glädja sig, tycka om, älska</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (saker):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> frustra; malis alienis, Ter.; in sinu g. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= inom sig),</text:span> Tib.; mihi g-o; voluptates opportunæ sunt, ut g-eas; tu isto bono g-e; bello suo; hoc scientiæ genere; prosperis rebus; jnstitiā et æquitate; oportet correctione g-re, delicto dolere; de aliqua re, C.; in aliqua re, Lucr.; g-o immortaliter, quod scribis, C.; g-o, quum te adspicio, Pt.; eum natum esse et nos g-emus et civitas, dum erit, lætabitur; g-bat Socrates, se causam moriendi nactum esse, C.; g-entem agros findere sarculo, Hor.; id g-o, Ter.; gaudia g-eo, Phdr. -; g. re, de re, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">inf.,</text:span> Ov.; g-es carminibus; g-ent cognomine molles auriculæ, Hor.; rapae g-ent frigore, Mt. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. i helsning</text:span> = gr. χαίρειν, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Må wäl:</text:span></text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gaudĭbundus</text:span> l.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gaudĕbundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glad:</text:span></text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gaudĭmōnium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fröjd:</text:span></text:span> Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gaudium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förnöjelse,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (inre) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fröjd, glädje:</text:span></text:span> quum animus ratione movetur et constanter, g. dicitur, quum inaniter exsultat, lætitia dicitur; g. maximum, incredibile; g-o efferri, exsultare, cumulari, compleri; afficere alqm g-o, C.; Latonæ pertentant g-a pectus; mala mentis g-a, Vg.; inane, Qu.; vana, Hor.; percipere, Pn.; grande, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sinligt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nöje, njutning:</text:span></text:span> deditus corporis g-is, Sa.; coenæ g-a, Juv., Ov.; pestiferum (S. Tarquinii) g., L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gaudiālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fröjdefull, ujutningsrik:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Pergaudeo</text:span>, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara högeligen glad:</text:span></text:span> p-o, te ab illo amari: C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>augamēla, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Assyrien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gavia,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en liten wattenfågel:</text:span> Pn., Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gaulus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spann; rundt fartyg:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Fs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gaunăcum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">pels af weßle-skinn:</text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>aurus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg i Campanien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gaurānus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gausăpa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gausăpe</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gausăpes</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gausăpum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Filt, fris-tyg,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> begagnadt ss. täcke, mantel m. m.:</text:span> coccina g-a involutus, Petr.; g-ĕ purpureo mensam pertergere, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. om skägget,</text:span> Ps.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gausăpātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Filtklädd:</text:span></text:span> Sen. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gausăpĭnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Af filt:</text:span></text:span> pænula, Mt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gausăpĭna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frismantel:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Gaza,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. persiske konungens) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skattkammare, bank, statskassa;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skatt, skatter, rikedom:</text:span></text:span> regiæ g-æ custos, Ct.; omni Macedonum g-ā potitus est Paulus, C.; Troïa g. per undas volvitur, Vg.; non g-æ neque consularis lictor summovet miseros animi tumultus, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>aza, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn på städer i Palæstina m. m.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>azăca, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Medien och Cappadocien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gazăcēnus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕbenna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(Cebenna, <text:line-break/>Cevenna): = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Cevennerbergen i Frankrike.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕdrōsi, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Gĕdrōsia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folk och land i Asien, wid Persiska wiken.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>eidunni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">germ. folkslag.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕla, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕlas ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad wid floden</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕlas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på Sicilien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gĕlāni, <text:line-break/>Gĕlenses, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inw. i G.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gĕlōus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: campi, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gelasco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gelo, Gelu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕlāsĭmus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: gr. nom. pr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(snyltgäst hos</text:span> Pt.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gĕlăsīnus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grop i kinden</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (s. blir synlig wid leende):</text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gelatio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gelo, Gelu.<text:line-break/>Gelenses <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gela.<text:line-break/>Gelicidium, Gelid. . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gelu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ellius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en romersk</text:span> gens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och deß medlemmar, sersk.:</text:span> A. Gellius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förf. från 2:dra seklet e. Chr.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gelo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gelu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕlōni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">scythiskt folk i södra Ryßland.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gelous <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gela.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gĕlu,</text:span> us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(<text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕlus</text:span>, us, Cato;<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.,</text:span> Lucr., Varr.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frost, Is:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> rura g-u claudit hiems; altum, Vg.; flumina acuto g-u constiterunt, Hor.; unda coit g-u, Ov.; g. jungit ripas; altitudo g-us, Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> tarda g-u senectus, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕlĭcĭdium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: (cado): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frost:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕlĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Isig, iskall, kall:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> aqua, C., Lucr.; fons; flumen, C.; pruinæ, nox, Vg., unda; Lycaeus; vultus mortui; mors; artus, Ov.; Hæmus, Hor. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> g-us per ima cucurrit ossa tremor, Vg.; o genus attonitum g-a formidine mortis, Or.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕlĭde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: senex res omnes g. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(slappt, matt)</text:span> ministrat, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēgĕlĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(köldslagen) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ljum, blid, töaktig:</text:span></text:span> aqua, Su.; Notus, Ov., ver, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Praegĕlĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ganska kall:</text:span></text:span> loca, L.; caelum, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕlo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intrans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frysa stelna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till is:</text:span> pruina, Pn.; venæ, St. - <text:span text:style-name="T4">impers.</text:span>: gelat = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det fryser:</text:span> Pu.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Komma att frysa, isas, stelna; göra islupen:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> caseus g-atur; lac g-tum, Col.; frigora g-ant alqd, Pn.; fluvius fessum g-at, Mt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> pavido g-antur pectore, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕlasco</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frysa:</text:span></text:span> vinum non, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕlātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frost:</text:span></text:span> magna g. secuta est, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumgĕlātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kringfrusen:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congĕlo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frysa ihop, stelna:</text:span></text:span> Ister; lingua cum duro palato, Ov. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">slappas, afkylas:</text:span></text:span> otio C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Komma att hopfrysa, isas, stelna;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">frysa, stelna:</text:span></text:span> cadentes pruinas ventus, Pn.; c-atur oleum; mare c-tum, Col.; in lapidem rictum serpentis c-are, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congĕlasco</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanfrysa:</text:span></text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congĕlātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Incongĕlābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. ej kan frysa, ej lägga sig:</text:span> mare, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕgĕlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upptina, -töa; wärma:</text:span></text:span> solum r-atur; frigora apricā aurā Zephyrus, Col.; manus r-ata, Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gemebundus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gemo.<text:line-break/>Gemell. . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Geminus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gĕmĭnus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twillingfödd, twilling</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pl.</text:span> g-i, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">twillingar:</text:span></text:span> fratres, C.; soror, Pt.; Ilia partum g-um edidit, L.; g-am dabit Ilia prolem, Vg.; fetus; catuli, Ov.; mater g-os internoscit, C.; Romulus et Remus g-i erant, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dubbel;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">twenne</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af lika art, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ett par:</text:span></text:span> g-um lucernæ lumen, C.; g-æ nuptiæ, Ter.; g-æ sunt somni portæ; g-i scopuli ad caelum minantur, Vg.; g-i ordines; g-ā ope <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med åror och segel),</text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dubbelgestaltad:</text:span></text:span> Chiron <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(centauren),</text:span> Ov. <text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Enahanda, alldeles lik</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">samme:</text:span></text:span> g-simus, Pt.; audacia, societas hereditaria g-a et simillima; improbitate g-us, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕmellus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twilling -:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> äfwen</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">Subst.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">twillingbroder, -syster:</text:span></text:span> fratres, Ov.; Castor g. Pollucis, Catl.; g-os conniti, eniti, Vg., Ov.<text:line-break/>2.<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dubbel:</text:span></text:span> legio (ex duabus facta), Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Enahanda lik:</text:span></text:span> cetera paene g-i; nugis et pravorum amore g., Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕmellĭpăra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: (pario): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Twillingmoder:</text:span></text:span> Latona, Ov. Met. VI. 315.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕmĭnĭtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Likhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (twillingars):</text:span> Pacuv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕmĭno</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intr.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blifwa dubbel:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dubbla, fördubbla; upprepa:</text:span></text:span> verba g-ta; victoria, L.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.:</text:span> g-at <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(slår om igen),</text:span> Ter.; facinus; honorem, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanslå; para:</text:span></text:span> acuta æra g-ant Corybantes; serpentes avibus (<text:span text:style-name="T4">dat.</text:span>) g-antur, Hor. -; agni tigribus, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕmĭnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fördubbling:</text:span></text:span> verborum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congĕmĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fördubbla, dubbla:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congĕmĭnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ingĕmĭno</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intr.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upprepas, mångfaldigas, fördubblas:</text:span></text:span> clamor; curæ; austri, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fördubbla; tidt och tätt upprepa:</text:span></text:span> vox i-ta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(echo),</text:span> Vg.; plausus, Vfl.; opes; i-ta nobilitas, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Septemgĕmĭnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sjufaldig:</text:span></text:span> Nilus, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Tergĕmĭnus</text:span> l.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Trĭgĕmĭnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A</text:span>,:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trilling-:</text:span></text:span> fratres, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tredubbel, -faldig:</text:span></text:span> Geryon t. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med tre kroppar),</text:span> Vg.; spolia; victoria, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gemisco, Gemitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gemo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gemma,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Knopp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (på wäxter), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">öga:</text:span></text:span> ad articulos sarmentorum exsistit ea, quæ g. dicitur, C.; turget in palmite g.; vitis protendit, tendit g-am, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ädelsten, juvel, perla:</text:span></text:span> pocula distincta g-is clarissimis; corona illuminata fulgentibus g-is, C., g-æ, marmor, ebur, Tyrrhena sigilla, tabellae, Hor.; g. legitur sub æquoribus, Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gemmeus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Af ädelsten;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. en knopp l. ädelsten; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lik en ädelsten:</text:span></text:span> trulla C.; sceptra; juga, Ov. - rotunditas, Pn.; prata florida et g-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(prålande),</text:span> Pn. ep.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gemmĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. för l. gömmer ädla stenar, perlor:</text:span> mare, Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gemmo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Knoppas, sätta knopp:</text:span></text:span> vites, C., Col., Varr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wara prydd med ädla stenar; skimra s. en ädelsten:</text:span></text:span> sceptra g-<text:soft-page-break/>antia, Ov.; herbæ g-antes rore recenti, Lucr.; saxa, St.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gemmātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Besatt med ädla stenar:</text:span></text:span> anulus, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gemmasco</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Knoppas:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gemmesco</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hårdna till en ädelsten:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōgemmo</text:span>, 1.: = gemmo 1.: Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gemmōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rikt besatt med ädla stenar:</text:span></text:span> monile, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gemmŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liten knopp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ädelsten:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Bĭgemmis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">twåknoppig:</text:span> Col. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med 2 ädla stenar:</text:span> anulus, Treb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Trĭgemmis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">treknoppig:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gĕmo,</text:span> ui, ĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. om tunga, pressade ljud:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af mskor: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sucka, stöna, klaga, beklaga sig,</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">intr.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: g-bant desiderio mei; lugere et g. pro aliquo; malum suum occulte; hic status omnium voce g-itur, C.; multa g-ens; casum Amyci secum g-it, Vg.; mors non est g-da; te g-unt, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af djur: (klaga), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kuttra; ryta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> o. s. w.:</text:span> turtur, Vg.; leo, Lucr.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af döda ting</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Knaka, dåna, genljuda,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sucka), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sorla:</text:span></text:span> antennæ, Hor.; cymba sub pondere; area tunsis frugibus; rota tractu, Vg.; Bospori g-entis litora, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕmĕbundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Suckande,</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕmisco</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Inch.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Börja sucka, klaga:</text:span></text:span> Cd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕmĭtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Suck, suckan; klagan:</text:span></text:span> urbis; urbe tota fiebat fletus g-que; abjectus, flebilis, lamentabilis, imbecillus; toto foro g., C.; dare g-um pectore ab imo; ducere; edere; extremos g-us ciere; g-u et irā invadunt, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af döda ting: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dån, genljud, sorl:</text:span></text:span> percussæ cavernæ (equi Trojani) g-um dedere; ingens pelagi g., Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕmŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klagande:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Adgĕmo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sucka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wid ngt:</text:span> malis nostris (<text:span text:style-name="T4">dat.</text:span>), Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumgĕmo</text:span>, 3.: ursus ovile, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tjuter omkring,</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congĕmo</text:span>, ui, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Samfäldt sucka; tungt sucka:</text:span></text:span> senatus frequens c-uit, C.; alqd <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwer ngt),</text:span> Lucr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Knaka:</text:span></text:span> ornus (icta bipennibus) supremum c-it, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ingĕmo</text:span>, ui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sucka, jemra sig öfwer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> in ea re civitas i-uit, C.; i-it et talia voce refert, Vg.; condicioni suæ, L.; morte alicujus, Ct.; laboribus, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ingĕmisco</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Inch.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Börja sucka:</text:span></text:span> quoties me viderit, i-et; pueri Spartiatæ verberum dolore laniati non i-unt; in aliqua re; alicui rei, C. - i-dum est, hostem judicatum esse Dolabellam. Quid i-is hostem D-am? C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕgĕmo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genljuda:</text:span></text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕmōniæ scalae, <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕmōnii gradus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. absol.:</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕmōniae, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">trappor bakom</text:span> carcer <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nedanför</text:span> Capitolium, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utför hwilka aflifwade förbrytare nedkastades:</text:span> corpus in G-as trahere, abjicere, T., Val.; in G-is gradibus abjectus, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gemulus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gemo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gĕna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kind:</text:span></text:span> pilosæ g-æ; g-æ ab inferiore parte tutantur oculos; subjectæ et leviter eminentes; muliebres lacerationes g-arum, C.; excubat amor in g-is Chiae; humor in g-as furtim labitur, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">poet.:</text:span> exurere, eruere g-as (= oculos), Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnuīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: dens, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">Subst.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gĕnuīnus i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kindtand:</text:span></text:span> C.; g-um frangere, Ps.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕnăbum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i</text:span> Gallia transalpina (G. Aurelianorum = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Orleans).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gĕnăbensis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕnăva l. <text:line-break/>Gĕnĕva, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Gallien = Genève.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕnauni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folk i Vindelicien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gĕnĕālŏgus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">författare af slägt-register, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Genealog:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĕālŏgĭa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slägtregister:</text:span></text:span> Mess. Corv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gĕner,</text:span> ĕri, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gr.</text:span> γαμβρός <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> γαμέω): <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Måg, swärson:</text:span></text:span> soceri cum g-is non lavantur, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sons</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> eller </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">dotters måg:</text:span></text:span> T.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swåger:</text:span></text:span> N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōgĕner</text:span>, ĕri, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span> = gener b.: Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gener. . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Genus, Geno.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ēnēsāras, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sjön Genesareth i Palæstina:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gĕnĕsis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Födelse:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stjernornas ställning wid ngns födelse, ngns </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Födelseplanet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">nativitet:</text:span></text:span> imperatoria, Su.; inspicere alicujus g-in, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnethlĭăcus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som ställer ngns horoskop, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Astrolog:</text:span></text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnethlĭăcon</text:span>, i. <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Födelsedags-qwäde:</text:span></text:span> St.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnethlĭŏlŏgĭa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">konsten att bestämma ngns födelseplanet:</text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Genetrix, Genetivus = Genit . . ., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Geno. <text:line-break/>Geneva <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Genava.<text:line-break/>Genial . . ., Geniatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Genius, Geno.<text:line-break/>Genicul . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Geno.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gĕnista,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en wäxt:</text:span> humiles, lentæ g., Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Genit. . ., Genius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Geno.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gĕno,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">præs.</text:span> fere obsol. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> gnascor, nascor), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gigno,</text:span> (gĭ-gĕno), gĕnui, gĕnĭtum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Föda, afla:</text:span></text:span> si filius mihi genitur, C. (ex testamento antiquo); animus non potest extra corpus durare genique, Lucr.; Cato sui generis initium ab se gigni et propagari voluit; Hecuba Alexandrum, Jupiter Herculem g-uit; pisces ova g-unt, C.; pellice g-tus, L.; ex nihilo nihil g-itur, Ps.; Venus Aenean g-uit; qui parentes te talem g-uere?, Vg.; Nocte g-tus, Ov.; alqm ex aliquo, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om naturen, jorden, wäxter) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frambringa, alstra;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">uppkomma:</text:span></text:span> ad majora nos natura g-uit et conformavit; omnia, quæ natura g-it, maturata pubescunt; ea, quæ terra g-it, quæ in terris g-untur; Plato ideas negat g-i et ait semper esse, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om Gud: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skapa:</text:span></text:span> deus hanc urbem gentibus, vos huic urbi g-uit; deus animum ex sua divinitate g-uit, C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med abstracta object: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frambringa, förorsaka; framkomma med; wäcka:</text:span></text:span> g-is nobis novas præceptiones; morbus ex valetutudinis perturbatione g-itur; permotionem animi g. et sedare; naturā g-itur amicitia, C.; ludus iras g-it, Hor.; fastidium, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gignentia</text:span>, ium <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">alstrande naturföremål = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wäxter</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wäxtlighet):</text:span> nuda g-ium loca, Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĭtābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Alstrande, befruktande:</text:span></text:span> aura, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĭtālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Alstrande, fruktsam, -bar; för afling</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">födelse tjenlig; skapande; födelse befordrande:</text:span></text:span> semen; arva, Vg.; corpora<text:span text:style-name="T4">;</text:span> partes corporis, Lucr.; hora anni Pn.; dii g-es, Enn.; Diana g., Hor.; procul hinc abeste mortes: haec vitae g-is est origo, St. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĭtāle</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">pl.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĭtālia</text:span>, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Födslolem, könsdelar:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĭtālĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på ett befruktande sätt:</text:span> semina seminibus g. misceri, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Antĕgĕnĭtālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">före födseln skedd:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĭtīvus</text:span>, (genet.) <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Medfödd:</text:span></text:span> nomen, Ov. Met. III. 33; nota, Su.<text:line-break/>b. casus g.: Qu., Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĭtor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĭtrix</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĕtrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fader; moder:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> ab optimo g-re procreatus, C.; dubio g-re creatus, Ov.; Aeneadum g-x Venus, Lucr.; g. Nisi, Vg.; genetricem occidit Orestes, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> nomina producit g. usus, Hor.; Græci vitiorum g., Pn.; Lemanus Rhodani, Aus.; o patria, mea g-x, Catl.; frugum g. Ceres, Ov.; vitiorum Aegyptus, Js.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĭtūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Födelse, börd; säd:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nativitet, födelse-constellation:</text:span></text:span> Su. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĭtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span> = genitura a.: Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skyddsande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Genius</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (eg. aflelse-gud:</text:span> naturalis deus uniuscujusque loci vel rei aut hominis, Serv.):<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">menniskas, isyn. en mans skyddsande, hwilken troddes följa i lif och död, njuta och lida, glädja sig och sörja med honom:</text:span> natale comes qui temperat astrum, humanæ deus naturæ, mortalis in unumquodque caput, vultu mutabilis, albus et ater, Hor.; g. Augusti, Ov.; per g-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid hans</text:span> g.) obsecrare alqm, Hor.; jurare per g-um, Sen.; sinister g., Ps. - indulgere g-o ɔ; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">göra sig goda dagar,</text:span> Pt.; curare g-um mero, Hor.; defraudare g-um ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lefwa knappt,</text:span> Ter.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">andra föremåls:</text:span> loci, Vg.; g. urbis Romæ, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Becker Röm. Alt,</text:span> I.; cur g-um Romæ mihi fingitis unum, quum portis, domibus, thermis, stabulis soleatis assignare suos g-os perqueomnia membra urbis perque locos g-orum milia multa fingere?, Prud. adv. Symm. II. 439 ff.<text:line-break/>c. habere genium, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hafwa skyddsgud, prægnant om en owanlig l. öfwernaturlig lycka l. gåfwor.</text:span> nemo mathematicus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stjerntydare)</text:span> g-um indemnatus habebit, Juv.; victurus g-um debet habere liber <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(der skyddsande prosaiskt uttryckt = den högre ingifwelsen, s. gifwit boken deß uppkomst och är borgen för deß fortlefwande),</text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕniālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till (aflelse) äktenskap hörande, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Äktenskaps</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fruktsam:</text:span></text:span> lectus g. C,; l. g. est, qui sternitur puellis nubentibus, in honorem genii, Serv., Paul. Diac.; lectus g. in aula est, nil ait esse prius, melius nil caelibe vita, Hor.; g. copia pecudum, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frodig, yppig, wäl försedd; åt glädje</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">njutning egnad,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (festlig, treflig):</text:span> uva; rus; festum, Ov.; hiems (quum ”mutua inter se læti convivia curant”), Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕniālĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rikligt:</text:span></text:span> festum agere, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕniātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Treflig, fryntlig:</text:span></text:span> vultu g., Cp. Ver.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gens</text:span>, gentis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. hwad s. har gemensam härkomst: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slägte:</text:span></text:span> hominum, Pn.; apum, Col.; ponti (i. e. pisces), Vg.; audax omnia perpeti g. humana ruit per vetitum nefas, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Folkstam, folkslag, folk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i ethnographisk mening, liks.</text:span> natio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">nationel</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> och</text:span> populus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">politisk,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ehuru skilnaden ej alltid strängt iakttages):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> qui g-es omnia mariaque et terras movet, ejus sum civis civitate caelitum, Pt.; g-es Italae, Enn.; propior societas est ejusdem esse g-is, nationis, linguæ; nulla g. tam fera est - cujus mentem non imbuerit deorum opinio; consensus omnium g-ium est lex naturæ; Cilicum g.; ubinam g-ium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i werlden)</text:span> sumus; ubique g-ium; jus g-ium, C.; Suevorum g., Cs.; g. universa Trojanorum et Henetorum Veneti appellati; Aequorum g., L.; g. Gallica natura bellicosa, Sa.<text:span text:style-name="T4">;</text:span> tantæ molis erat Romanam condere g-em, Vg.; Germani nationis nomen, non g-is, T. Germ.2. <text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">främmande folk, (barbarer):</text:span> solus apud g-es praestat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om Scipio Afr.),</text:span> Naev.; duret g-bus, si non amor nostri, at certe odium sui, T. Germ. 33. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">deraf hos kyrkofäder = hedningar.</text:span><text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">poet. = land:</text:span> Italiam dixere ducis de nomine g-em, Vg. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slägt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (eg. blott patricisk l. åtm. adlig</text:span> (nobilis), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sig innefattande flera</text:span> familiæ): (g. Cornelia, f. Sullana); (Claudii) Marcelli ab liberti filio stirpe (i. e. familia), Claudii patricii hereditatem g-e ad se redisse dicebant; g. Tarquiniorum, C.; hunc unum plurimae g-es <text:soft-page-break/>consentiunt primarium populi esse virum, Iscr.; g. julia; patres minorum gentium (a Tarquinio in patres lecti), L.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl..</text:span> dii minorum g-ium, C.; g. Domitia, Su.; homo sine g-e, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">poet. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">afkomling,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> frände:</text:span> Aeneas, deûm g., Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gentĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Folkslaget tillhörig; nationel:</text:span></text:span> mos, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gentīlĭcius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett folkslag tillhörig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nationel:</text:span></text:span> vocabulum, Gell.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en slägt tillhörig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slägt-:</text:span></text:span> sacrificia, C.; sacra; nota, L.; funus; hoc est ei g-um, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gentīlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Folkslaget, nationen tillhörig; folkets;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. tillhör samma folk, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">stamslägtad:</text:span></text:span> levitas; nationes, T.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">stamförwandt:</text:span></text:span> g. alicujus, Gell.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. hör till slägten, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slägt-;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som hör till samma slägt, har samma slägtnamn: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">stamförwandt:</text:span></text:span> g-es sunt, qui eodem inter se nomine sunt, ab ingenuis oriundi, quorum majorum nemo servitutem servivit, qui non sunt capite deminuti; meus g. (Tullius), C.; servi dominorum g-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. bära sina herrars namn, t. ex.</text:span> Marcipor = Marci puer), Pn.; g-e nomen; id fuit g-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(slägtdrag)</text:span> in illo, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gentīlĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stamslägtskap, stamförwandtskap:</text:span></text:span> jus g-is, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slägt:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gentīlĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">folkets</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sed l. på </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">folkets</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> språk:</text:span> Sol.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnuīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Infödd, -hemsk; äkta:</text:span></text:span> ars non transmarina et importata, sed g-a et domestica, C.; fabula g-a Plauti, Gell. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnuīne</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppriktigt:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnus</text:span>, ĕris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Härkomst, börd:</text:span></text:span> contemnere g. alicujus, extollere suum; g-e et ingenio divino esse; forma, vires, opes g., non habent in se veram laudem, C.; g. ducere Olympo, Vg.; g. nisi cum re vilius algā, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slägte; folkslag; slägt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> poet. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">afkomma; afkomling:</text:span></text:span> ova parire solet pennis g. condecoratum, Enn.; universi g-is humani societas; immensa societas humani g-is; animantium g-a; g-a bestiarum; virtutes non tam ipsis, qui habent, quam g-i hominum fructuosæ, C.; hominum g.; si g. humanum - temnitis, Vg.; durum g. sumus experiensque laborum, Ov.; g. ferarum, Lucr.; virtus propria Romani g-is, C.; Sabini, quo g-e nullum incorruptius fuit, L.; Aborigines g. hominum agreste, Sa.; g. Macedonum, N.; quo de g-e natus est? g. est pollens et honoratissimum, Pt.; natus g-e nobili, regio, malo, C., amplissimo, Cs., summo, N., regio, Hor. - audax Iapeti g. (= Prometheus); sive tu g. neglectum - respicis auctor (i. e. Romanos Mars); piscium et summa g. hæsit ulmo, Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slag, klaß:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> g. ferratile <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om slafwar i kedjor),</text:span> Pt.; antiquissimum g. e doctis poētarum; duo sunt in republica hominum g-a, qui - -; g. latronum, amicorum, vitæ; novum literarum g.; rerum publicarum; g. orationis forense, æquabile et c., C.; copias omnium g-um parat, Sa.; omne copiarum g.; g. scripturæ leve, N.; florum, ingeniorum, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i philosophisk men., i mots. till</text:span> pars, forma (species): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Slag, slägtbegrepp; det allmänna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (saken, begreppet i allm.):</text:span> g. sui <text:soft-page-break/>similes, specie differentes plures partes complectitur; sine personis et temporibus de universo g-e quærere; infinita g-is quæstio; ultimum g. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(allmännaste slägtbegreppet),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">abstr. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wäsende, beskaffenhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (qualitet, i mots. till quantitet, namn); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sätt; hänseende, fall, förhållande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> o. s. w.:</text:span> divitiæ genere, non numero cernuntur; hæc ad cujusque virtutis g. accommodantur; hæc, g-e confusa, cogitatione distinguuntur; hic recte nomine, g-e melius ille; g. vivendi, furandi; in aliquo g-e peccare; in hoc g-e duo vitanda sunt, C.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gramm. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kön, genus:</text:span></text:span> Varr., Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĕrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. tillhör, rör slägtet l. slaget, sakens begrepp i allm. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Allmän:</text:span></text:span> homo g-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det allmänna)</text:span> est, Alcibiades speciale, Sen.; quum de genere negotii controversia est, constitutio g. dicitur; g-e quiddam decorum, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĕrālĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I allmänhet, till begreppet:</text:span></text:span> tempus g. definire difficile est, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĕrātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Efter slägten, folk, klasser; slägtwis, folkwis, klaßwis:</text:span></text:span> g. secla propagant; g. secla referunt naturam parentum, Lucr.; g. componere (ea, quæ in jure civili versantur) C.; Cæsar omnibus g. gratias egit, Cs.; proprios g. discite cultus, agricolæ, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med afseende på slaget, det hela; i allmänhet:</text:span></text:span> singillatim potius quam g. dicere; g. complecti, exponere alqd, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĕro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om mskor och djur: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afla, föda:</text:span></text:span> Herculis stirpe g-tus; populus Romanus a Marte g-tus, C.; Oebalum Telon g-asse fertur; g-do sufficere prolem (animalium), Vg.; (equa) in primo initu g-re coepit, Pn. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om gudar, naturen, jorden, odlaren) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skapa, frambringa, alstra:</text:span></text:span> hominem g-vit et ornavit deus; non ita sumus a natura g-ti; homines hominum causa g-ti sunt, C.; Jubæ tellus g-at leones, Hor.; lactucam Gades, Col.; terra (ea) rhinocerotas, Ct.; amor florum et g-di mellis, Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i andl. mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frambringa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (producera):</text:span> etiam tenuis ingenii vena alqd, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĕrasco</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Framkomma, födas:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĕrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Alstring:</text:span></text:span> avium, hominum, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĕrātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fader, uppfödare:</text:span></text:span> C.; equorum g. Acragas, Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĕrātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: Mela.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĕrōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ädelboren, högättad, af ädel stam, race, slag; ädel:</text:span></text:span> virgo g-a et nobilis; stirps, ortus minime g.; Pyrrhus rex g., C.; pater fuit g., N.; petitor g., Hor.; miles g. (Fabii), Ov. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. (till skick l. art) = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ädel, förnäm; hög</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sinnad):</text:span> natura ipsa et quædam g-a virtus respuit, ne dolorem summum malum diceres; forma (Cæsaris) magnifica et g-a quodam modo, C.; Alexander g-i spiritus imperator, Pn.; non regi mentis potest g. ardor, Sen. Oct.<text:line-break/>c. = qui potest generare, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skämtsam anwändning af</text:span> Ap. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĕrōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På ädelt sätt:</text:span></text:span> Cleopatra g-ius perire quærens, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĕrōsĭtas</text:span>, ātis. <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ädelhet, ädelt blod; ädel stam, race:</text:span></text:span> tauri, ovis, Pn., vitis, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Bĭgĕner</text:span>, ĕra, ĕrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tweslägtad, af blandad race:</text:span></text:span> muli et hinni b-i, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congĕner</text:span>, ĕris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af samma slägte l. slag:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congĕnĕrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">född tillsammans; af samma stam:</text:span> porci; analogon et analogia non idem est, sed c-um, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēgĕner</text:span>, ĕris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wanslägtad, wanartad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i physisk och moralisk mening), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">usel, feg:</text:span></text:span> sanguis, Sen.; canes, Pn.; proles, Luc.; animus; Neoptolemum d-em (esse) patri referre memento, Vg.; d. o populus, Luc.; d. patriæ artis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. wanslägtats från - -),</text:span> Ov.; d. ad pericula; preces d-es, T.; virtutis alicujus, Sil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēgĕnĕro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wanslägtas, urarta; förnedra sig:</text:span></text:span> poma, Vg.; vites in feritatem, Pn.; a majorum virtute; a Stoicis, C.; a familia imperiosissima, L.; ad theatrales artes, T.; d-atum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det att han wanslägtats, hans nedrighet)</text:span> in aliis huic quoque decori offecit, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utskämma, göra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skam; förswaga:</text:span></text:span> propinquos Ppt.; palmas equus d-at (alii: d. ad palmas), Ov. - Venus animos (canum) d-at, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ingĕnĕro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frambringa, inplanta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hos; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">plantera:</text:span></text:span> natura i-at præcipuum amorem in <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till)</text:span> eos, qui procreati sunt; homini cupiditas scientiæ i-ta; familiæ i-ta frugalitas, C.; societatem alicui, L.; = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">plantera,</text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōgĕnĕro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Framföda, -bringa:</text:span></text:span> non p-nt aquilæ columbam, Hor.; fetus apes, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōgĕnĕrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: mularum, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕgĕnĕro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ånyo föda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">frambringa, -alstra:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> nævos, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Likna:</text:span></text:span> patrem, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congĕnĭtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">född l. framkommen tills. med ngn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Medfödd:</text:span></text:span> pili, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēgignor</text:span>, ni: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wäxa ut, fram:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Indĭgĕna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">c.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Inföding, infödd, inhemsk:</text:span></text:span> non i., sed advena, L.; Germanos i-as esse crediderim, T.; Fauni i., Vg.; deus, Ov.; vinum i., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Indĭgĕnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: id.: Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">(<text:span text:style-name="T2">Ingĕno</text:span>), gĕnui, gĕnĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Alstra på; inplanta uti, i födseln gifwa:</text:span></text:span> herbas rupibus, Luc.; ingenitur cupido, Man.; natura homini i-uit veri cupiditatem, C. - <text:span text:style-name="T4">part.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ingĕnĭtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">medfödd:</text:span> sterilitas, Col.; virus corpori i-tum, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ingĕnium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. (i physisk, moralisk, psychologisk men.): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Medfödd art, natur</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (character); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lynne, skaplynne; smak, böjelse, sinne:</text:span></text:span> soli, Pn.; lactis; ligni, Gell.; militia aspera i-o loci caelique, T.; crines suo <text:soft-page-break/>i-o flexi, Petr.; suum quisque noscat i. acremque se et bonorum et vitiorum judicem præbeat; multiplex et tortuosum i.; in joco probi i-i lumen eluceat, C.; is redit ad suum i.; pudicum; i. proclive ad libidinem a labore; esse leni i-o in alqm; conflictari cum talibus i-is, Ter.; i. avidum, mobile, vanum, malum, pravum, virile, Sa.; credo ejus animum suopte i-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af naturen)</text:span> temperatum virtutibus fuisse; vivere suo i-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(efter sitt lynne, sin smak);</text:span> Volscis redit suum i., L.; come, N.; Vitellio segne, Galbæ medium i., magis extra vitia, quam cum virtutibus, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt: intellectuella </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Anlag; hufwud, gåfwor, natur</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(-gåfwor), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">snillegåfwor</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (snille i mots. till hjerta, character l. till förwärfwade egenskaper, konst o. s. w.):</text:span> quod in pomis, itidem in i-is esse ajunt: quae dura et acerba nascuntur, post fiunt mitia et jucunda, Acc. ap. Gell.; animi et i-i celeres motus; hoc animi (magni, sc. non perturbari in rebus asperis), illud etiam i-i magni est præcipere cogitatione futura; magni animi et splendidissima i-a; maxima i-a altissimique animi; doctrinæ et i-i gloria; ratio (ars), i.; magnum, acre, divinum, eximium, præstans, excellens, acutissimum; tuum i. valde admirabatur; præditus maximo i-o; præditi summis i-is; i-i bonitas; excellens i-i magnitudo; acies i-i; i-i vis incredibilis, singularis; i. non defuit; i-o valere, abundare; ea non sunt nostri i-i; i. tardum; mihi rectius videtur i-i quam virium opibus gloriam quærere; pars i., alii corpus exercebant; corpus infirmum, i. sapientiā validum; magna scriptorum i-a provenere; magnitudo sceleris omnium i-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(föreställning)</text:span> exsuperabat; i. ubi intenderis, valet, Sa.; i. docile, aptum ad artes; i-i facultas, N.; ingenium misera arte fortunatius credit Democritus, Hor.; Callimachus i-o non valet, arte valet, Ov.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snille, förmåga;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om saker: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">uppfinning, qwickhet:</text:span></text:span> (Cic. de Fin. I. §. 7): i., quod - insenuit libris, statua taciturnius exit; i-iis non ille favet plauditque sepultis, nostra sed impugnat, Hor.; nostrorum temporum i-a, Pn. ep.; coenarum i., Pn.; am bigebat Nero, quonam modo noctium suarum i-a innotescerent, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ingĕniātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Artad, utrustad:</text:span></text:span> lepide i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> improbus), Pt.; ad astutiam, Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ingĕniōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: af naturen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tjenlig, skicklig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngt:</text:span> ager ad segetes; vox (psittaci) mutandis sonis, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wäl utrustad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på hufwudets wägnar, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">med godt hufwud; talentfull;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> serskildt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fintlig, qwick:</text:span></text:span> homo; omnes i-os Aristoteles ait melancholicos esse; i-i in morbum incidunt tardius, quam hebetes, C.; simulatio est ad excogitandum i-or; miracula i-a, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ingĕniōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: tractantur ista i. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med talent),</text:span> disputantur eleganter <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med grundlighet),</text:span> C.; declamare, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Pĕringĕniōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serdeles begåfwad, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med mycket godt hufwud:</text:span></text:span> homo, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ingĕnuus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Naturlig:</text:span></text:span> indoles, P<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">t.;</text:span> color, Ppt.; fons, Lucr.; genæ, Ov.; tophus, Juv.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Friboren</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mots.</text:span> servus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o.</text:span> libertinus):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> homo i. et liberaliter educatus; i. puer, materfamilias, civis <text:soft-page-break/>Romanus, C.; homo, L.; i-i oculi manusque; liber et i., Hor.; malo i-am, quam libertinam, Mt. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.</text:span> <text:line-break/>α. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">En friboren wärdig; ädel; ärlig:</text:span></text:span> vita; artes; illiberalis et i. jocus, jocandi genus; nihil i-i habet officina; animus; magis i-i est aperte vel odisse quam fronte occultare sententiam; timiditas i-a, C.; vultus; pudor, Juv.; amor, Ov.<text:line-break/>β. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förwand, förklemad, weklig:</text:span></text:span> vires invalidæ i-æque, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ingĕnue</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som det anstår en friboren; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ärligt:</text:span></text:span> educatus; aperte et i. confiteor, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ingĕnuĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fri börd; friborenhet:</text:span></text:span> jus, ornamenta i-is, C.; adolescens memor i-is, L.; asseri in i-em, Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ädelhet, ädelt sinne:</text:span></text:span> præ se ferre i-em et probitatem quandam; præstare i-em suam verborum turpitudine vitanda, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Postgĕnĭti</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Efterkommande:</text:span></text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Praegigno</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">frambringa:</text:span> Pt. (inc. l.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōgigno</text:span>, gĕnui, gĕnĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frambringa, föda, alstra:</text:span></text:span> is, qui illud lumen p-uit; res ex seminibus p-untur, C.; te feræ p-uerunt, Ov.; Enceladum terra, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōgĕnies</text:span>, ēi, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: (non plurimum refert, nulla haec an praedura sint. Nam quid progenies genitivo singulari faciet?, Qu.):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(framfödande) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ursprung, härkomst:</text:span></text:span> antiquitas ab ortu et divina p-e propius aberat, C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afkomma, -föda:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">collectivt: (ättlingar, söner, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">slägte):</text:span></text:span> credendum est priscis viris, qui se p-em deorum esse dicebant; nepotum, liberorum p-em, C.; nos tua p.; p-m Trojano a sanguine duci audierat, quæ - -, Vg.; nos daturi sumus p-em vitiosiorem, Hor.; jam nova p. caelo demittitur alto, Vg.; vitis, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss.</text:span> nomen unitatis: p. Phaĕthon, non infitianda parenti, Ov.; Sicinius p. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(afkomling)</text:span></text:span> ejus, qui primus tribunus plebis creatus est, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōgĕnĭtor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stamfader:</text:span></text:span> N., Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕgigno</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åter frambringa, alstra:</text:span></text:span> membra consumpta, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ūnĭgĕna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">c.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Född af en</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (samma moder); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">broder, syster:</text:span></text:span> Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Geno.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gentiāna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en wäxt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Baggsöta:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gent . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se för öfrigt</text:span> Gens, Geno.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gĕnu,</text:span> us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Gĕnus, us <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: inc.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Knä:</text:span></text:span> g-u terram tangere, C.; g-a flectere, Pn., Ov.; submittere, Pn.; ponere g-a, procumbere in g-a, Ct.; advolvi g-bus alicujus, L.; g-a alicujus, T.; amplecti g-a, hærere g-bus alicujus; g-a labant, Vg.; g-bus tremere, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĭcŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">litet </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Knä:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på mskor och djur: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Led, knälägg:</text:span></text:span> puerorum, Varr.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på wäxter:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĭcŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Winkel:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĭcŭlātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Knä-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ledformigt:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĭcŭlātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. ligger på knä, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Knäböjande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (en stjernbild):</text:span> Vitr. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Försedd med knä</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">led; krökt:</text:span></text:span> culmus, C.; arundo, Pn.; meatus Tibridis, Amm. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnĭcūlōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">full af leder l. knän:</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ingĕnĭcŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">knäböjande (om stjernbilden</text:span> Engonasin): Man.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ingĕnĭcŭlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">falla på knä:</text:span> Lpd.; se i., Hyg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ingĕnĭcŭlātus</text:span>, = ingeniculus: Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕnuālia</text:span>, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Knäband:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕnua, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Genua (Genova): stad i Italien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gĕnuātes, <text:line-break/>Gĕnuenses, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span> – </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>enūcius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Genuinus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gena <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Geno.<text:line-break/>Genus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Geno <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(och</text:span> Genu).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕnŭsus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Illyrien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gĕōgrăphĭa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jordbeskrifning,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> geographi:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕōgrăphicus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕōmĕtres</text:span>, l.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕōmĕtra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m..</text:span> v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jordmätare) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mathematicus:</text:span></text:span> g-æ non solent omnia docere, sed postulare, ut quædam sibi concedantur, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕōmĕtrĭa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Geometri, ren mathematik:</text:span></text:span> in summo apud Græcos honore g. fuit: itaque nihil mathematicis illustrius: nos metiendi ratiocinandique utilitate hujus artis terminavimus modum, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕōmĕtrĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mathematisk:</text:span></text:span> g-is rationibus non credere, quæ vim afferunt in docendo, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕōmĕtrĭca</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mathematiska satser; mathematik:</text:span> discere, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕōmĕtrĭcē</text:span>, es, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span> = geometria: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕorgos</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Landtbrukare:</text:span></text:span> Qu., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕorgĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. handlar om landtbruk:</text:span> carmen, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕorgĭca, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(grek.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">gen.</text:span> -ōn): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">titel på Virgilii poem om landtbruket.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕræstos, <text:line-break/>(Gĕræstus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: l. <text:line-break/>Gĕræston <text:line-break/>(Gĕræstum), i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">landtudde och stad på Euboea. –</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ergĭthus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Troas.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">G</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">ergovia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">galliskt stadsnamn. –</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ermălus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nordwestre delen af Palatinus:</text:span> Varr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr Dyer, Topogr. of Rome),</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ermānus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">Subst.,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">pl.</text:span> - ni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">German, germanisk, Germaner,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> inwånare i</text:span> <text:line-break/>Germānia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Germanien (Tyskland), begränsadt af Rhen, Donau,</text:span> Oceanus septentrionalis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Nordsjön och Östersjön) samt i öster af Sarmaternes och Dacernes land enl.</text:span> Tac. Germ.; C., Cs., Hor., Vg. <text:line-break/>b. G-a superior (prima) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> inferior (secunda), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">romerska provinser (l. delar af</text:span> Galliæ provinciæ) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wester om Rhen, tills. kallade</text:span> Germaniæ: T., Pn. <text:line-break/>Germānĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Germanisk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (s. tillhör l. rör Germanerne):</text:span> bellum, Cs. <text:line-break/>Germānĭcus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tillnamn för Tib. Claudius Drusus, Augusti stjufson, för hans son C. Cæsar, för Domitianus m. fl.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Germānĭciānus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: exercitus, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. Germanus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med härledningar se</text:span> Germen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Germen,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: (:geno = carmen: cano; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dessa</text:span> verba geno <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> cano <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äro i hela latinska språket de enda ord, af hwilka </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kunna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> bildas suffixformer, der</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">n</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">omedelbart sammanstöter med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Man kan således ej med Corssen, Beiträge zur latein. Formenlehre</text:span> p. 405, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förklara det wara emot latinets allmänna ljudlagar, att</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">n</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skulle framför</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">m</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfwergå till</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">r.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">I</text:span> carmen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">har wäl deßutom, liks. i</text:span> Casmena, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den urspr. consonanten warit</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">s</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kanske detsamma warit fallet med</text:span> germen: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr gr.</text:span> φάσμα <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af l. till verbet</text:span> φαίνω): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Brodd, knopp, wäxt-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fruktämne;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> poet.: animalisk </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">säd:</text:span></text:span> aliena ex arbore (in arborem) includere g;, Vg.; g. frondium se densat, Pn.; rami g-e graves, Luc.; uterum implere g-e, Ov.; maris g. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(perla),</text:span> Cd.; Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Germānus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> humanus (hominanus) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> homo):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i fråga om härkomst, slägtskap) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Naturlig, köttslig, äkta:</text:span></text:span> patria C.; frater, Pt., C.; soror g-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om halfsyster),</text:span> N. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">Subst.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Germānus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Germāna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Broder, syster:</text:span></text:span> Ter., Vg., Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sannskyldig, rätt, riktig, äkta:</text:span></text:span> nomen, Pt.; Campani; justitia; ironia; Stoicus g-simus; asinus g., C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(broderlig) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Helt lik, enahanda:</text:span></text:span> casus, Js.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Germāne</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppriktigt:</text:span></text:span> rescribere, C. (inc. l.)<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Germānĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Brödra-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">syskonskap; blodsförwandtskap; broderlighet; likhet, öfwerensstämmelse:</text:span></text:span> subit memoria g-is, L.; moveat te horum pietas, moveat g., C.; Bospororum duorum g. concors, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congermānus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanwuxen, fast förenad:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congermānesco</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wäxa tillsammans:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Germĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">intr.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Framskjuta, skjuta skott, slå ut:</text:span></text:span> fetus capillum, Pn.; g-at termes olivæ, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Germĭnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Germĭnātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congermĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wäxa, frodas:</text:span></text:span> cepe c. decedente luna, inarescit adolescente, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēgermĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skjuta fram, spricka ut:</text:span></text:span> pampini infra trunci corpus; sarmentum oculis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ögon),</text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Praegermĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">I förtid skjuta upp:</text:span></text:span> præflorere et p., Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōgermĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skjuta fram:</text:span></text:span> surculus, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕgermĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åter skjuta skott, telningar:</text:span></text:span> caule reciso, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕgermĭnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gĕro,</text:span> gessi, gestum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bära</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= uppbära, hålla, hafwa på sig;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">syn.</text:span> fero = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bära, bringa någorstädes hän):</text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg., i sinl. men.: </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om yttre, från den bärande skilda object:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> spolia ducis ferculo, L.; galeam in capite, vestem, N.; virginis arma, Vg.; terra (in foribus Solis caelata) viros urbesque g-it silvasque ferasque, Ov.; onus, Pn. - personam g. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bära en mask = spela en roll, repræsentera ngn:</text:span> ipsi quam personam g. velimus, in nostra potestate est; meminerit magistratus, se personam g-re civitatis, C.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> in oculis g. aliquem = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">omhulda,</text:span> Ter.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. om jorden l. wäxter: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bära</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">alstra:</text:span></text:span> violam nullo terra serente, Ov. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med kroppens lemmar, egenskaper, affectioner till obj. (hafwa):</text:span> vulnera; virginis os habitumque, Vg.; pallidiora g-ens buxo ora; juvenca nullum servitii signum cervice g-ens, Ov.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i osinl. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sköta, förwalta, leda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ett företag), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">föra, bedrifwa:</text:span></text:span> imperator neque facit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= åstadkommer, frambringar)</text:span> neque agit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= handlägger),</text:span> sed g-it (res), id est sustinet, translatum ab his, qui onera g-unt, quod hi sustinent, Varr.; res g. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(allmänt uttryck för practisk, isynnerhet offentlig werksamhet);</text:span> a rebus g-endis senectus abstrahit; iis, qui habent a natura adjumenta rerum g-darum, adipiscendi magistratus et g-da res publica est; se ad rem publicam et ad magnas res g-das accommodare; g. rempublicam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tjena staten, wara embetsman),</text:span> C.; rem publicam bene, egregie, male g., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wäl, lyckligt utföra statens wärf),</text:span> L.; g. consulatum, potestatem; male, bene negotium; malitiose rem mandatam; bellum inter se, cum aliquo; tutelam; rem suam male <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sina affärer),</text:span> C.; imperium, N.; <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">göras, ske, försiggå, gå:</text:span></text:span> hæc dum Romæ geruntur -; maximæ res g-untur multitudinis arbitrio, C., res gestæ l. gesta, ōrum = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">någons </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bedrifter, wärf; historia</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i obj. mening):</text:span> memoria rerum g-arum pop. Rom., L.; Atheniensium res g-æ magnificæ et amplæ fuere; res g-as scribere, Sa., g-a obscuriora, N.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om egenskaper, känslor, m. m.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hafwa, bära, antaga, wisa; befinna sig i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en ställning l. ett förhållande:</text:span> juravi linguā, mentem injuratam g-o; vos juvenes animum g-itis muliebrem, Enn. ap. C.; g. animum laude dignum; in hominis figura immanitatem beluæ g.; similitudinem aliquam speciemque sapientum g.; g. inimicitias, amicitiam cum aliquo; simultatem, C.; animum parem ad cetera g., supra fortunam g., Sa.; odium in Romanos; mixtum gaudio ac metu animum g.; fidem cum fortuna mutabilem, L.; ante annos animum virilem g. Vg.; pueri inter se iras, Ter.; res præ se g-it utilitatem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lofwar),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>morem g. alicui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(antaga sed, beteende åt ngn</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">någon till wiljes) </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">rätta sig efter ugn, göra ngn till wiljes:</text:span></text:span> C., Ter., Ov.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="T4">refl.</text:span>: se gerere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med adv.): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förhålla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">uppföra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skicka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bete</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig:</text:span> se g. turpissime, honeste, contumacius, elatius; ita se g., ut probetur fides; se pro cive g., C.; se more majorum; ut se victus g-ret, exploratum misit, Sa.; medium se g., L., - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hos sednare förf.:</text:span> g. alqm = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">uppträda bete sig ss.:</text:span> regem, Js.<text:line-break/>4. ætatem, annum g. = agere, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillbringa, lefwa:</text:span></text:span> Sulp. ap. C.; annum LXIX: mum, Su. - <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕrens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. sköter, förwaltar:</text:span> negotii g-ns <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= affärsman, i mots. till embetsmannaklassen, landtbrukare m. m.),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕro</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bärare:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕrŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bärare, dragare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till yrket):</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕrŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕrŭlĭfĭgŭlus</text:span>, (figulus, fingo), i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skämtsamt bildadt ord = medskyldig:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕrundium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grammatisk term, hwarmed</text:span> Grammatici <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">beteckna såwäl hwad wi kalla</text:span> gerundium, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som hwad wi kalla</text:span> supinum: g-a vel participialia infiniti vice funguntur, quod solet apud Græcos cum articulo conjungi, Prisc. p. 409 sqq. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">K.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gĕrundīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: modus = gerundivum: Serv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gesto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Frequ.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">pläga </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bära; gå med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> puerum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ss. barn)</text:span> alqm in manibus, Ter.; crimina g. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kringbära):</text:span> aliquem in alvo; anulum, Pt.; caput fixum in pilo g., C.; virginibus Tyriis mos est g. pharetram; non obtusa g-amus pectora Poeni, Vg.; arma humeris, L.; in utero g. (partum); collo alqd, Pn.; cibos et hortamina pugnantibus (Germanis feminæ) g-ant, T. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> in oculis g. alqm <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wara öm om ngn),</text:span> Ter. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intr.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Promenera i bärstol:</text:span></text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gestāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det s. ngn bär l. drager, ngns </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tyg, rustning, skrud, prydnad, wapen:</text:span></text:span> clipeus magni g. Abantis; hoc Priami g. erat - (sceptrum sacerque tiaras vestesque), Vg.; ista decent humeros g-a (i. e. arcus) nostros (Phoebi), Ov.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om en ädelsten),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det, hwari l. hwarpå ngt bäres, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bärdon, bär-redskap:</text:span></text:span> g-e sellæ provehi aliquo; in g-e sedem sumere, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gestātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Promenad i bärstol</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> och i allm. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lustfärd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i wagn, på skepp o. d.):</text:span> Su., Ce.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wäg (i en trädgård), der ngn promenerar i bärstol, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Allée:</text:span></text:span> Pn. ep.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gestātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bärare:</text:span></text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gestātōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: sella <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwari ngn bäres),</text:span> Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gestātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bärning:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gestĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ofta bära, pläga bära:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Enn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gestor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bärare:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gestus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sätt att föra l. röra kroppen och deß delar: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Later, åthäfwor, åtbörder,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (naturl. och konstmässig) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">mimik, gesticulation</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T4">plur.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blott ss. tillhörande flera subject):</text:span> a forma removeatur omnis viro non dignus ornatus et huic simile vitium in g-u motuque <text:soft-page-break/>caveatur; vox et g. subito sumi et aliunde arripi non potest; g. tardus, acer, instans, sedatus; agere g-um humeris; peccare in g-u; in scena agere g-um; discere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(studera)</text:span> g-um; nescire g-um; in oratore summorum actorum g. requirendus est; nonnulli histrionum g-us non vacant offensione, C.; g-um accommodare, componere ad alqm, Qu.; (figuras orationis) Græci quasi aliquos g-us orationis appellant, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gestĭcŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: Tert. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gestĭcŭlārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gestĭcŭlāria</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(åtbörds-, skådespelare) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pantomim:</text:span></text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gestĭcŭlor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Med åtbörder föreställa ngt; spela pantomim:</text:span></text:span> jocularia carmina g., Su. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gestĭcŭlātio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Åtbördsspel, mimik:</text:span></text:span> digitorum: Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gestĭcŭlātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">pantomimspelare:</text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gestio</text:span>, 4.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (häftiga) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">åtbörder, spritta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af lust; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">blifwa wild, yr:</text:span></text:span> nimia voluptate; equus equæ contrectatione; animi negotiis et opere defessi quasi g-unt; lætitia g-ens, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Trå efter, åtrå, åstunda:</text:span></text:span> alqd delere, omnia scire, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Praegestio</text:span>, 4.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">På förhand</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i förkänslan) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">längta efter</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> p-o jam videre - -, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mera ha lust till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> ludere, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gestuōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med lifligt åtbördsspel, gesticulerande:</text:span> Gell., Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Aggĕro</text:span> <text:line-break/>(adgĕro), gessi, gestum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bära, lägga, foga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till:</text:span> aquam, Pt.; ingens tumulo tellus a-itur, Vg.; intendere vera, a-re falsa (crimina), T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Aggestus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bärande, forslande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ett ställe, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillförsel:</text:span></text:span> pabuli; tutus copiarum, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumgesto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(beställsamt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kringbära:</text:span></text:span> epistolam, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congĕro</text:span>, gessi, gestum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bära (draga, kasta) tillsammans, sammanföra, -skaffa; hopa, samla:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> penum in cellam ad alqm, Ter.; frumentum, Varr.; grana in os alicujus l. alicui; maximam vim auri et argenti in regnum suum; alicui viaticum, C.; saccis undique c-stis dormire, Hor.; tela in alqm, Ct.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. om materialier till byggnad l. byggnaden sjelf:</text:span> oppida manu c-sta, Vg.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.:</text:span> columbæ c-sere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hafwa byggt bo),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Samla, hopa, sammanföra;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i skrift) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sammanställa:</text:span></text:span> c-antur in unum omnia, ut idem auribus oculisque captus sit; turbam patronorum in hunc sermonem (i. e. in librum, qui inscribitur Brutus) c-si, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med abstracta object: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hopa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt på ngn = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">slösa, kasta, wräka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tilldela</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn ngt i mängd; spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">påbörda:</text:span></text:span> omnia ornamenta in alqm; non timendum est, ne plus æquo in amicitiam c-atur, C.; beneficia in aliquem, C.; causas rei in alqm, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congĕries</text:span>, ēi <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hopande; hop,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (oordnad) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">massa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (röra):</text:span> c. verborum ac sententiarum idem significantium (est amplificationis <text:soft-page-break/>(rhetoricæ) genus), Qu.; armorum, T.; c-em (mundi = chaos) deus dispositam in membra redegit; c. silvæ, Ov.; metalli, Luc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congĕro</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">samlare = tjuf:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congeste</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congestim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i massa:</text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congestīcius</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Congestitius), <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hopförd, -kastad:</text:span></text:span> materia, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congestio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congestus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hopbärande, samlande:</text:span></text:span> herba avium c-u, non humano satu (orta), C.; fossarum c-io, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= igenfyllning),</text:span> Vitr. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hop, massa:</text:span></text:span> frondium c-us, Col.; stercoris c-io, Pall.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Accongĕro</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bära samman till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēgĕro</text:span>, gessi, gestum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bära bort:</text:span></text:span> pallam amicæ, ad amicam, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīgĕro</text:span>, gessi, gestum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bära, föra åt skilda håll; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sprida, fördela:</text:span></text:span> stercus in prata; crines, Col.; ex copia (argumentorum) in quodque genus causæ, quod cuique conveniet, d-emus, C.; Nilus in septem cornua d-itur, Ov.; vapor huc illuc d-itur, Pn.; annum in species, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sönderdela, upplösa;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om mat) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">smälta:</text:span></text:span> dentes d-unt cibum, Pn.; cibos mansos - demittimus, quo facilius d-antur, Qu.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Indela, ordna; utbreda:</text:span></text:span> jus civile in genera; alqd artificiose d-tum generatim componere; tabulas accepti d.; aliter illa ab aliis d-untur, C.; carmina non d-it Sibylla; ita d-it omina Calchas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utreder, tyder),</text:span> Vg.; tempora, Ov.; id suo loco d-emus, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīgesta</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ordnad samling:</text:span> liber d-orum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> l. conjectaneorum), Gell. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīgestio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fördelande:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. rhetorisk konstterm),</text:span> C. de Or.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Matsmältning:</text:span></text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ordnande, utredning:</text:span></text:span> annorum, Vell.; Italiæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(beskrifning),</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīgestus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fördelning, förwaltning:</text:span></text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Indīgestus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oordnad:</text:span></text:span> rudis i-aque moles (chaos), Ov.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">osmält:</text:span> Mcb.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Indīgeste</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oordnadt:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēgĕro</text:span>, gessi, gestum, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bära, föra, kasta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ut, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bortskaffa:</text:span></text:span> prædam ex tectis, L.; stercus ex loco, Col.; fons aquam, Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">poet. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uttömma:</text:span></text:span> castra rogis, Ppt. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utkasta, förslösa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngt:</text:span> bona, censum in alqd, T., Qu.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Utstöta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">yttra:</text:span></text:span> querelas, Sil.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillbringa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> exigo): diem, Vfl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēgestio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēgestus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bortförande, -skaffande:</text:span></text:span> ruderum, T.; ventris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= afföring),</text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ingĕro</text:span>, gessi, gestum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bära, föra,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> kasta, wräka, ösa i, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">in i, på:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> in urnam aquam, Pt.; saxa in subeuntes, L.; tela, T.; <text:soft-page-break/>thura aris; semen solo, Pn.; stercus vitibus, Col.; contumulare i-tā humo, Ov.; medicamentum equis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gifwa in),</text:span> Pn. - se aliquo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(störta in, hän),</text:span> Js.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kasta, hopa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på -:</text:span> sceleri seelus, Sen.; i-bat carpe, carpe <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(upprepade),</text:span> Petr. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">muntligen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Framhålla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">förehålla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> någon uppmanande; oftare förebrående </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ösa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer ngn (förebråelser l. smädelser), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillwita:</text:span></text:span> i-o præterita: vides, quæso igitur, ea, quæ restant, C.; magnitudinem (Germanici) militibus i.; quorum tandem nomina prius parentes liberis suis i-unt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ss. lysande exempel)?,</text:span> T.; cum ea expostulem? mala multa i-am?, Ter.; probra in alqm, L.; eadem a tribunis præfectisque (militibus) i-bantur, T.; alicui convicia, Hor.; incesse nunc et cuncta flagitia i-e, Sen. tr.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i otid l. mot ngns wilja) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Erbjuda, nödga på, påtruga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn ngt;</text:span> se i. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tränga sig fram l. på ngn:</text:span> Tiberius patris patriæ nomen a populo sæpius i-tum repudiavit, T.; osculum alicui; postulationes, Su.; non i. se, sed subtrahere, Pn.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Påföra, tillfoga:</text:span></text:span> funus i-tum patri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. i fadrens hus infördt),</text:span> Sen. Med. 132.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ingestābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">omöjlig att bära:</text:span> onus, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sŭperingĕro</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ofwan påföra; kasta öfwer:</text:span></text:span> alqd alicui, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Intergĕrium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mellanfyllning, -lägg:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Intergĕrīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: paries, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mellanwägg:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Oggĕro</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bära, framräcka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emot ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bringa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> truga på ngn:</text:span> osculum alicui; amor amarum, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Praegĕro</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bära framför</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> speculum sub oculis alicujus, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōgĕro</text:span>, gessi, gestum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bära, föra ut, fram:</text:span></text:span> oleum, Col.; defunctos, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕgĕro</text:span>, gessi, gestum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Återföra, -kasta:</text:span></text:span> afferre et r., Pn.; ignem in focum bis, ter, Sen.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppkasta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ngt ur deß naturliga läge; jfr</text:span> recludo, refigo): tellurem, Ov.; humum; culmos in acervum, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn ngt igen (ss. swar, lön); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">kasta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tillbaka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngn:</text:span> pro Catio tibi proxima epistola tot rusticos Stoicos r-am, ut - C. ep.; convicia, Hor.; invidiam in alqm, Qu.; crimen alicui, Sen. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Införa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (på sin plats; jfr</text:span> referre): in commentarios alqd, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕgestum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppkastad jordhög:</text:span></text:span> Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T4">plur.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Register:</text:span></text:span> Vop.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Suggĕro</text:span>, gessi, gestum, 3.: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bära,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">lägga inunder:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> flammam costis aëni, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bringa, gifwa, anföra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ss. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">stöd, fyllnad, näring;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bereda, skaffa:</text:span></text:span> firmamenta causæ infirmandis contrariis et tuis confirmandis, C., invidiæ flammam ac materiam criminibus, L.; <text:soft-page-break/>sumptum rebus, Ter.; rationes sententiæ, C.; si indulseris ebrietati s-do, quantum concupiscunt, vitiis vincuntur, T.; tellus alimenta, Ov. - verba, quæ desunt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i en text),</text:span> s-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ifylla, supplera),</text:span> C.; famem alicui, Pt. = <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">(Bära), foga intill, till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (efter i st. för):</text:span> Bruto statim Horatium consulem s-unt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(insätta efter -),</text:span> L.; singulis generibus causarum copiam argumentorum; damna aleatoria s-bantur (i. e. accedebant), C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Uppkasta, -resa:</text:span></text:span> humo s-tā castra coronare, Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Suggestio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tillfogande; ingifwelse:</text:span></text:span> Qu.; Vop.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Suggestum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upphöjning,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spec. ss. plats för en talare: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tribun:</text:span></text:span> in communibus s-is Dionysius consistere non audebat; illud s-um, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Suggestus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hög, upphöjning, upphöjd plats,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sersk. ss. plats för talare l. ordförande: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">tribun:</text:span></text:span> lapideus, Col.; s-um in foro exstructum rostris adornare; in s-u jura reddere (prætorem), L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sŭpergĕro</text:span>, gestum, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bära på, skyffla öfwer:</text:span></text:span> terra s-ta, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kasta till l. igen:</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕrōnium, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Apulien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gerrae,</text:span> ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Strunt, prat, sladder:</text:span></text:span> germanæ, Pt.; g. est in Latina cratis, Varr. (vid. Muellerum ad Paul. Diac. pag. 40).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gerro</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pratmakare, dagdrifware:</text:span></text:span> Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Congerro</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kamrat i upptåg:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gerul . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gero.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ēry̆on, ŏnis l. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ēry̆ŏnes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rese, hwars oxar Hercules bortförde:</text:span> tricorpor, Vg.; ter amplus, Hor. <text:line-break/>Gēry̆ŏnācĕus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gest . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Gero.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕtes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĕtæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Geter,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> thraciskt folkslag, stamslägtad</text:span>t <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med Dacerne (norr om Donau); jemte</text:span> Davus (= Dacus) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl. slafnamn i Athen och derifrån i comedien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gĕtĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">getisk; thracisk:</text:span> Vg. <text:line-break/>Gĕtĭce, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gibber,</text:span> ĕra, ĕrum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gibbus,</text:span> a, um, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hwälfd, pucklig, puckelryggig:</text:span></text:span> calvaria g-ba, Ce.; fullo g-er Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gibbus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gibba</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gibber</text:span>, ĕris, (<text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">n</text:span>?); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Knöl, puckel:</text:span></text:span> in naribus g-us, Juv.; g. pone cervicem, Su.; g-er in dorso, Pn.; aucto g-re, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gibbĕrōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Puckelryggig:</text:span></text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ĭgas, antis, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oftast</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pl.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gĭgantes, tum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gigant,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mythologiska widunder, Jordens himlastormande söner, genom hwilkas besegrande Zeus grundat werldens ordnade skick:</text:span> G-um modo bellare cum diis, C.; cælum suo servire Tonanti non nisi sævorum potuit post bella G-um, Luc. <text:line-break/>Gĭgantēus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. har afseende på Giganterne:</text:span> triumphus G. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwer G.),</text:span> Hor. <text:line-break/>Gĭgantŏmăchĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Giganternes strid, titel på en dikt af Claudianus.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gigno <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Geno.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gilbus</text:span> l. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gilvus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Waxgul, black, blackig:</text:span></text:span> equus, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gingīva,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tandkött:</text:span></text:span> Catl., Juv. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gingīvŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gingrio,</text:span> 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snattra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om gäß):</text:span> Fs. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gingriātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span> = tibicen: Fs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gingrīna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags flöjt:</text:span> Fs., Sol.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Ginnus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Hinnus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Git,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">Indecl. n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swart kummin:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glăber,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kal, skallig, glatt</text:span></text:span> (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skägg l. hårlös), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">bar:</text:span></text:span> bovis collum, Col.; homo, Mt.; g-ior, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glăbellus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glăbrārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. älskar skägglösa:</text:span> Mt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glăbresco</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bli kal, bar:</text:span></text:span> area, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glăbrētum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bart ställe på åkren:</text:span> Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glăbro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Göra kal; skålla:</text:span></text:span> sues flammā, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glăcies,</text:span> ēi, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Is:</text:span></text:span> aspera; Hyperboreæ (<text:span text:style-name="T4">pl.</text:span>), Vg.; in lubrica g-e volutari, L. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> æris g. flammā liquescit, Lucr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glăciālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Isig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (iskall):</text:span> hiems, Vg.; frigus, Ov.; polus, Sen.; Oceanus, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glăcio</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förwandla till is;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">frysa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">stelna:</text:span></text:span> Jupiter nives, Hor.; humor g-atur in grandines, Pn.; - caseus, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intr.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stelna:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conglăcio</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T4">trans.,</text:span> i <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Isas, frysa till is:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T4">intr.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hopfrysa, isas:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> aqua frigoribus, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> alicui tribunatus c-at <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= uträttar intet; jfr</text:span> frigeo), C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glădius,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glădium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span> (Pt):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swärd:</text:span></text:span> g-o se cingere, accingi, C.; stringere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(draga),</text:span> C., Vg., L.; destringere, C.; cominus g-o pugnare, Cs.; alicui g-um jugulo defigere, L.; fulgens; cruentus; in vaginam recondere; g-orum impunitas, licentia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i bruket af -),</text:span> C.; ad g-um se locare (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till gladiator),</text:span> Sen. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildliga uttryck:</text:span> suo (sibi) g-o jugulari, confici <text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(falla för egna wapen),</text:span> Ter., C.; plumbeo g-o jugulari, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med slöa wapen</text:span> i. e. facili negotio), C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Plogjern:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swärdfisk:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glădiātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">legd </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kämpe</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fäktare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wid offentliga skådespel; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">gladiator:</text:span></text:span> bonus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dugtig);</text:span> emere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lega);</text:span> dare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(låta uppträda, bekosta),</text:span> C.; edere, Su.; g-bus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid gladiatorsspelen),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glădiātōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. rör l. liknar gladiator, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gladiators-:</text:span></text:span> familia g-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(trupp);</text:span> pugna; ludus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skola),</text:span> C.; munus g-um dare (= dare gladiatores), Su. - animus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af slagskämpe),</text:span> Ter.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glădiātōrium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gladiatorslön:</text:span> L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glădiātōrie</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på gladiatorswis:</text:span> Lpd. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glădiātūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gladiatorskamp:</text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glădiŏlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Litet swärd:</text:span></text:span> Gell., Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīglădior</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fäkta; kifwa, rifwas:</text:span></text:span> sicis inter se; inter se de aliqua re, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glaeba</text:span> l. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glēba,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Jordklimp; torfwa:</text:span></text:span> nulla agri g.; injectā g-ā humare alqm, C.; rastro versare g-as, Hor.; supinatæ g-æ; uber g-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jordens fetma);</text:span> duræ g-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= hård jordmån),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stycke, klump</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm., </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">block:</text:span></text:span> marmoris, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glaebārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: bos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dragoxe),</text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glaebōsus</text:span>, sior, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. består af stora stycken l. torfwor:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glaebŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: (terræ), Col.; ex metallo, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glaebŭlentus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span> = glebosus: Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Glæsum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Glesum.<text:line-break/>Gland . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Glans.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glans,</text:span> dis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ollon:</text:span></text:span> sues g-e pascuntur, C.; quæ (quercu) deciderant g-es, iis (aurea ætas vescebatur), Ov.; inventis frugibus g-e vesci, C.; quernea, Col.; fagea; castaneæ, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kula, lod</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. slungwapen):</text:span> g-e pugnare, Sa.; g-es fundere, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glandārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: silva <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ollonskog),</text:span> Cato. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glandĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. bär ollon:</text:span> quercus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glandium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Körtelfullt, läckert stycke af wildswin:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glandiōnĭda</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: id.: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glandŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Körtel; körtelfullt köttstycke:</text:span></text:span> Ce., Pn., Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glandŭlōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">full af körtlar:</text:span> cervix suis, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glārea,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grus, småsten:</text:span></text:span> pulvis, non g. invecta est, C.; g-ā viam sternere extra urbem, silice in urbe, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glāreōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: saxum, L.; rivus, Pn.; arva, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glaucus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Blågrå, isblå:</text:span></text:span> salix; oliva; equus, Vg.; undæ, Lucr.; oculi, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>laucus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>laucē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grekiska namn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glaucēum</text:span>, i,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glaucium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en blå blomma:</text:span> Col., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glaucōma</text:span>, ătis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(Glaucōma, æ, f.: Pt.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fläck i ögat-, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Starr,</text:span></text:span> Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> alicui - dolis g-am ob oculos objicere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(slå blå dunster i ögonen),</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gleb . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Glæba.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glēsum</text:span> <text:line-break/>(glessum, <text:line-break/>glæsum), i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bernsten:</text:span></text:span> Pn., T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glēsāriæ</text:span>, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: (insulæ) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bernstensöar,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i Östersjön:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glīs,</text:span> glīris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ätlig) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skogsråtta:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glīrārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Råttstall,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> muradt kar, hwari ätliga råttor hållas och fetas:</text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glisco,</text:span> ĕre, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Frodas; bli frodig, fet:</text:span></text:span> asellus paleis g-it; terra exilis fabā stercorata eo quasi pabulo g-it, Col. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. om eld, och om abstracta subj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Taga fart, frodas, tilltaga; wäxa:</text:span></text:span> ignis oleo, C.; invidiam sua sponte g-ntem unius insignis calamitas accendit; seditio, L.; rabies, Pt.; adulatio; fama; potestas, T. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upptändas, intagas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fröjd; åtrå:</text:span></text:span> numero; regnare, St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conglisco</text:span>, ĕre. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tändas; komma sig upp:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perglisco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bli riktigt fet:</text:span> gallina saginata p-it, Col. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> reglesco).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glŏbus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klot:</text:span></text:span> terræ; stellarum, C.; lunæ, Lucr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Massa, hop, flock, liga:</text:span></text:span> flammarum, Vg.; navium, Cs.; armatorum, L.; nobilitatis, Sa.; consensionis, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glŏbo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Runda, sammantränga, skocka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ett klot l. i allm. till en massa:</text:span> in rotunditatem g-ri, guttæ g-antur parvis orbibus; nubes g-antur, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glŏbātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hopwis; i slutna massor:</text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conglŏbo</text:span>, 1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rulla, hopa, skocka, sluta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> tillsammans, i synn. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med reflexiv betyd.:</text:span> corpus in pilæ modum c-re, Pn.; mare undique c-atur; terra in sese c-ta, C.; milites se in unum c-ant, L.; ut fors quosque c-verat -, Sa.; sanguis c-tus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lefradt),</text:span> Pn. - definitiones c-tæ, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conglŏbātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanskockning:</text:span></text:span> nubium, Sen.; militum, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glŏbōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klotrund:</text:span></text:span> Fortunam saxo g-o instare ajunt, Pac.; forma mundi; stella, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glŏbōsĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Klotrund form:</text:span></text:span> terræ, Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glŏbŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Litet klot:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glōcio,</text:span> 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skrocka:</text:span></text:span> gallina, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glōcĭdo</text:span>, 1.: id.: Fs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gloctŏro,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Snattra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om storken):</text:span> Philom.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glŏmus,</text:span> (Hor.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glōmus</text:span> (Lucr.), ĕris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nystan:</text:span></text:span> in lanæ glōmere, Lucr.; Hor.; lini, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glŏmĕro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nysta, hoprulla:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span>lanam in orbes, Ov.; offas, Varr.; deus terram in speciem orbis, Ov. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span> equus gressus g-at superbos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med afs. på benets krökning),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hopa, samla, sammanföra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i massor, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">skocka:</text:span></text:span> grandinem g-tam venti in terras agunt, L.; apes g-antur in orbem; manum bello (<text:span text:style-name="T4">dat.</text:span>) g-re, Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glŏmĕrābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rund:</text:span> Man.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glŏmĕrāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nystan, klot:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glŏmĕrāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glŏmĕrātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanträngdt, i massa:</text:span></text:span> Aus., Mcb.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glŏmĕrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: equi, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">galoppering,</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Agglŏmĕro</text:span> <text:line-break/>(adglŏmĕro), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nysta, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Foga, sluta till:</text:span></text:span> addunt se socios et lateri a-ant nostro, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conglŏmĕro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hoprulla, -weckla; hopa:</text:span></text:span> Lucr., Enn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Inglŏmĕro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hopa, sammanföra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på l. öfwer:</text:span> Auster noctem, St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glŏmĕrōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rund som ett nystan:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glōria,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ära</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= ryktets lof; stort l. berömdt namn):</text:span> g. eum ad caelum tollit, Acc.; vita Scipionis talis fuit vel fortunā vel g-ā, ut nihil posset accedere; vera g. est consentiens laus bonorum: ea virtuti resonat tamquam imago; g. belli et rerum gestarum; nemo, qui fortitudinis g-am consecutus est insidiis et malitia, laudem est adeptus; g-æ cupiditas; mercedem rerum gestarum g-am desiderare; dimicare pro g-a et honore; g-æ servire; g-am quærere, parere aliqua re; capere g-am ob rem; comparare, adipisci, reperire, alere, retinere, tueri; refringere alicujus g-am, adimere; g-ā duci, trahi, affici, C.; spernere, C., L.; ea belli g. est pop. Romani, ut -, L.; id nomen, ea g. est, si (quis) numero et virtute comitatus emineat, T.; g. quantalibet quid erit, si g. tantum est?, Juv. - <text:span text:style-name="T4">plur.</text:span>: veteres Gallorum g-as <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ärorika bedrifter)</text:span> memorare, T.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Prydnad:</text:span></text:span> Proca Trojanæ gloria gentis, Vg.; ne armentis quidem suus honor aut g. frontis, T.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ärelystnad; skryt:</text:span></text:span> deridere alicujus g-am, C., homo g-arum plenus, Pt.; quem tulit ad scenam ventoso g. curru, exanimat lentus spectator, sedulus inflat, Hor.; flare inanes g-as, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glōriŏla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liten ära, ”en smula ära”:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span> ut vivi nostrā g-ā perfruamur, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glōrior</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Berömma sig, skryta:</text:span></text:span> licet mihi apud te g-ri, Marce fili; jure; nimis g.; contra fortunam; in virtute recte g-amur; de gestis; de se senum more; nominibus veterum, C.; victoriā insolenter, Cs.; vellem idem posse g-ri, quod Cyrus; beata vita g-da est; g-batur, se omnes provincias peragrasse, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glōriābundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skrytande, -sam:</text:span></text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glōriātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sjelfberöm:</text:span></text:span> g-e digna est beata vita, quod non potest sine honestate contingere, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glōriātor</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skrytare:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glōriōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ärofull, ärorik:</text:span></text:span> consilia, facta illustria et g-a; dies; mors; illa in privatis g-a sunt, C.; g-um in vulgus, famā populari; mihi g-um est te florere laudibus, C.; honores, N.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skrytsam, äredryg, stolt:</text:span></text:span> Ἀλαζών - nos Latine g-um dicimus, Pt.; Ter. (prol. Eun. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">m. fl.);</text:span> Gnathones non essent, nisi essent milites g-i; præpotens illa et g-a philosophia, C.; nihil fuit in eo g-um, N.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glōriōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ärofullt; med stor ära:</text:span></text:span> g. triumphare, conficere alqd; g-sime, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skrytsamt, stortaligt:</text:span></text:span> loqui, mentiri, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Inglōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oberömd; bragd-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">namnlös:</text:span></text:span> vita inhonorata et i-a; i-um et ignobilem ad senectutem pervenire, C.; positis i-us armis exigat ævum, Vg.; militiæ i-us, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glōs,</text:span> glōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: v. gr. (γάλως): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swägerska,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mans syster:</text:span> Aus., Fs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glōssa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. tunga, tungomål): owanligt och dunkelt ord hos en förf. och deß uttydning, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Glossa:</text:span></text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glōssārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ordbok öfwer sådana ord:</text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glossēma</text:span>, ătis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span> = glossa: Varr., Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glossēmătĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: Diom.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glūbo,</text:span> ĕre:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skala, sprita; flå:</text:span></text:span> salictum, Cato; ramos, Varr.; pecus, Fs. <text:line-break/>b. materies g-et <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Codd.</text:span> g-ebit), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">få skal l. bark?,</text:span> Cato.; - Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glūma</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skal, hylsa, balja:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēglūbo</text:span>, ptum, 3.. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afskala, flå:</text:span></text:span> granum folliculo, Varr.; maena d-ta, Pt.; pecus, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glūs,</text:span> glūtis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: Aus. = gluten.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glūtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Seg:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Glūten,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glūtĭnum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kåda, lim, klister:</text:span></text:span> Vg.; apes lentum g-en de cortice colligunt; taurinum, fidelissimum, vulgare g-num, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glūtino</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hoplimma, -fästa:</text:span></text:span> bitumen g-at; chartam g-re; vulnus g-atur, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glūtĭnāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Limwerk, limmadt arbete:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glūtĭnātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bokbindare:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Agglūtĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Limma, löda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> fast wid ngt:</text:span> prooemium libro, C.; aurum, Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> a. se = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">hänga sig fast</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wid, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">sluta sig till ngn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">ngt:</text:span></text:span> alicui, ad rem, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conglūtĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Hoplimma, -foga, -sluta, -fästa, -sätta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sinl. men.:</text:span> calx optime c-at, Vitr.; folia, vitium, vulnus, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> hominem eadem optime, quæ c-avit, natura dissolvit; homo ex audacia, libidine - c-tus; si utilitas amicitias c-ret, eadem <text:soft-page-break/>dissolveret; vitæ dissimilitudo non passa est voluntates nostras consuetudine c-ri, C.; meretricios amores nuptiis c-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förena med),</text:span> Ter.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Conglūtĭnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hoplimning), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sammanfogning, -sättning:</text:span></text:span> omnis c., si recens est, ægre, si inveterata, facile divellitur; circuitus c-oque verborum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēglūtĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Upplösa:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕglūtĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lossa:</text:span></text:span> Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glūtĭnōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Limaktig, klibbig:</text:span></text:span> terra, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Glutio, Gluttio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Glutus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. Glutus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Glus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Glūtus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(gluttus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Swalg, strupe:</text:span></text:span> g-o sorbere salivam, Ps.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Glūtio</text:span> <text:line-break/>(gluttio), 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Sluka, swälja:</text:span></text:span> epulas, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēglūtio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nedswälja:</text:span></text:span> Fronto.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sugglūtio</text:span>, 4.: Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ly̆cĕra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ly̆cĕrĭum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ly̆con, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grekiska namn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gnæus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cnæus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gnăphălĭum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en blomma: kattfötter .</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gnārus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(narus), <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kunnig</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">= </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Förfaren; wäl wetande, förstående, kännande:</text:span></text:span> reipublicæ, C.; militiæ, Col.; Pericles g. fuit, quibus modis animi pellerentur, C.; loci, Pt.; temporis; se peti, Pn.; g. sub Nerone temporum, quibus inertia pro sapientia fuit, T.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Känd, bekant:</text:span></text:span> g-um id Cæsari; palus ipsis g-a, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gnārĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kännedom, bekantskap med -:</text:span> Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gnārŭris</text:span> = gnarus: Pt., Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ignārus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Okunnig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> uti ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">oerfaren, okunnig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om något; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">owetande, obekant</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med -:</text:span> i. faciendæ et poliendæ orationis, C.; artis, Ter.; malorum, Vg.; non sumus i-i, multos contra nos dicturos esse; me i-o et inopinante; pueri sæpe alqm indicaverunt, i-i, quo pertineret, C.; morum, Ter.; viæ, Vg.; urbis, L.; causæ, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Obekant</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">okänd:</text:span></text:span> regio hostibus i-a, Sa.; non i. alicui, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ignōro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Icke känna, icke weta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (någon, något, hwem l. hurudan, hwad, hurudant, hwar o. s. w. ngn l. något är); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">wara i okunnighet, wara okunnig om</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">icke förstå:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> jus Pt.; me <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till characteren)</text:span> vehementer, Ter., C.; Lepidus i-at de filio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sonens beteende l. öde);</text:span> Archimedis sepulcrum i-tum a <text:soft-page-break/>Syracusanis ego indagavi; dei faciem et locum i.; haec sunt i-antis, de mente dici, non de iis partibus, in quibus libidines versentur; i-ante rege, uter esset Orestes, Pylades se esse Oresten dixit, C.; i-atur enim, quae sit natura animāi, Lucr.; fugam suam occultari aut omnino i-ri posse <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(blifwa obekant)</text:span> existimabant; eventus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wäl</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">acc. pl.</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kanske</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T4">gen. sing.</text:span>) belli i-ans, Cs.; i-bat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kände ej till utseendet)</text:span> Aristiden, N.; neve i-ate (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kommen att lära känna)</text:span> Latinos; mene - fluctus quietos i-re (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bete mig så, som om jag ej förstode mig på)</text:span> jubes?, Vg.; petat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om han skall angripa)</text:span> hunc, i-at, an illum, Ov.; descriptas servare vices operumque colores cur ego si nequeo ignoroque poēta salutor?, Hor.; servili habitu per tenebras i-atur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(igenkännes icke),</text:span> T. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">prægnant = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Icke känna igen; icke wilja kännas wid</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> quia egens relicta est misera, i-atur parens, Ter. (Ppt. II. 2. 4?)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ignōrābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Omöjlig att igenkänna:</text:span></text:span> homo i. oculis meis objicitur, Pt. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Obegriplig:</text:span></text:span> res, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ignōrābĭlĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Obegripligt:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ignōrantia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Okunnighet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wanl. klanderwärd och såsom ständig egenskap):</text:span> literarum C.; loci, Cs.; veri, Ov.; mutua; arcanus terror sanctaque i., quid sit illud, quod tantum perituri vident, T.; per i-am scripturæ multa commissa fiebant, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ignōrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Owetenhet, okunnighet, bristande kännedom om, obekantskap med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> causarum; in rebus usitatis i.; maximarum rerum; sui; decori; in hominum i-e versari <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wara okänd af -),</text:span> C.; excusat i-em regis (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">att han ej kände konungen),</text:span> Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Pergnārus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kunnig om, wäl bekant med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> locorum, Sa. fragm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōgnārĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: indica p. (pretium - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">klart? öppet?),</text:span></text:span> Pt. Pers. 588. (prognaviter - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">raskt, Lamb.).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>nātho, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn på en parasit hos</text:span> Ter. <text:line-break/>Gnāthōnĭci, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">parasiter.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>nātia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Apulien</text:span> (Egnatia).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gnatus, Gnavus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Nascor, Navus. <text:line-break/>Gnidus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cnidus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gnōmē,</text:span> es, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sentens:</text:span> Front.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gnōmon</text:span>, ŏnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wisare på ett solur:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gnōmŏnĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dertill hörande:</text:span> Vitr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gnōmŏnĭcē</text:span>, es l.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gnōmŏnĭca</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gnomonik, timstens-wetenskap:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gnosus, Gnossus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Cnosus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gōbio,</text:span> ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: l.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gōbius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fiskart, gös:</text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>omphi, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Thessalien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gomphenses, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">deß inwånare.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gomphus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Plugg:</text:span></text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gongy̆lis,</text:span> ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Rofwa:</text:span></text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>onni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">thessalisk stad. –</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ordĭum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Phrygien. –</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ordy̆æi montes, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i Armenien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gordy̆æi, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inw. der. –</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>orgĭas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grekiskt namn; berömdt genom Sophisten G. på Socrates’ tid, efter hwilken en dialog af Plato är benämnd:</text:span> C. – </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>orgo, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Medusa. <text:line-break/>Gorgŏneus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span> – </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ortyn, ȳnos, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gortȳnē, es, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gortȳna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad på Creta.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gortȳnius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gortȳnĭăcus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gortȳnis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gortynisk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Gorytus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Corytus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gossypĭon,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Gossympĭnus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bomulls-plantan:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ŏthi, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Goter (Göter):</text:span> Amm. <text:line-break/>Gŏthĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Gŏthia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">deras land. -</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ŏthīni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span> - <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>ŏthōnes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkslag i nordöstra Germanien:</text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăbātus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Låg säng; tältsäng:</text:span></text:span> C., Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Grăbātŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dem.</text:span>: Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>racchus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn på en romersk familj, af semproniska slägten, hwars berömdaste medlemmar woro Tib. Gracchi söner Tib. och C. Gracchus,</text:span> tribuni plebis 621 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> 633 a. U. C. <text:line-break/>Gracchānus, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och cognomen.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăcĭlis</text:span> <text:line-break/>(gracilus, Ter.), <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Spenslig, smärt, tunn, smal, klen:</text:span></text:span> virgines g-æ, Ter.; puer, Hor.; corpus; artus; capella, Ov.; g-limum crus, Su.; arundo, Sen.; libellus, Mt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Torftig, mager:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om jord och deß producter:</text:span> clivi, Col.; vindemia; nucleus, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om föredrag: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Torftig, mager,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> enkel:</text:span> orator; oratio, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Grăcĭlens</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Grăcĭlentus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span> = gracilis: Naev., Enn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Grăcĭlesco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bli smärt, afsmalna:</text:span></text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Grăcĭlĭtas</text:span>, ātis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Grăcĭlĭtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis (<text:span text:style-name="T4">Acc.</text:span>), <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smärthet, spenslighet, smalhet:</text:span></text:span> corporis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> opimitas), C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Enkelhet, simpelhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i föredrag:</text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Grăcĭlĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Tunnt; enkelt:</text:span></text:span> Ap., Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Pergrăcĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ganska spenslig:</text:span></text:span> caulis, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Praegrăcĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Owanligt spenslig, klen:</text:span></text:span> proceritas, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăcillo,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Skrocka:</text:span></text:span> Phil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grăcŭlus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Kaja:</text:span></text:span> Pn.; g-i vo - cantur, quod gregatim volant, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">etymol.</text:span> ap. Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Grădior,</text:span> gressus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gå, wandra:</text:span></text:span> fidenti animo ad mortem; alia animalia serpunt, alia g-untur, C.; lente g-ens asellus, Ov.; viam, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fara:</text:span></text:span> per adversi g-iēris cornua Tauri (curru), Ov.; vox foras, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T1">G</text:span>rādīvus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i de Umbr.</text:span> Tabb. Iguv. Grabōvis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> Krapufis): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tillnamn för Mars, af de gamle etymol. förklaradt med:</text:span> in pugna gradiens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> gramine ortus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> gravis deus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr Corssen,</text:span> Origg. poēsis Romanæ p. 29 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.):</text:span> Nymphas venerabar agrestes Grādivumque patrem, Vg.; genus a magno ducentem forte Grădivo, Ov. Met. VI. 427; Numa Marti G-o Salios legit, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Grădus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gång,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (marsch); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">steg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som tages):</text:span> celeri g-u, grandibus g-bus ire, Pt.; ingredi pleno g-u; quin prodis, ut, quotiescunque g-um facias, toties tibi tuarum virtutum veniat in mentem, C.; citato g-u in hostem ducere; g-um accelerare, L.; g-um celerare studio anili; revocare g-um, Vg.; corripere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(påskynda),</text:span> Hor.; errare incertis g-bus; g-um sistere, continere, Ov.; g-um inferre, conferre, T. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Steg,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. är taget = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">fotfäste, ställning:</text:span></text:span> obnisum stabili g-u impetum hostium excipere; g-u moveri, demoveri, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Steg,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarpå man träder, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">trappsteg; afsats:</text:span></text:span> scalarum g-us tollere, incīdere; g-bus ascendere in locum, C.; Tarpeja rupes centum g-bus aditur, T.; coma in g-us formata, Su.; templi, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gång:</text:span></text:span> spondēus habet stabilem et non expertem dignitatis g-um, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Steg, fotfäste:</text:span></text:span> constantis est non tumultuantem de g-u dejici, C. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Steg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngt:</text:span> g. imperii factus est a Romanis e Sicilia in Africam; g. ad rempublicam; hic mei reditus g-us fuit, C.; primus g. capessendæ reipublicæ, N.<text:line-break/>d. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ståndpunkt, ställning, rum,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> rang:</text:span> altissimus dignitatis g.; summus g. honoris; summum, g-um tenere dignitatis et gratiæ; g. senatorius; fortunæ g.; altiorem g-um assequi; in aliquo g-u locari, collocari; de dignitatis g-u demoveri, C.; tenere secundum g-um imperii, N.<text:line-break/>e. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Led</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i slägtskap, förbindelse, utweckling (stadium), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">steg;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sällan och blott i bild) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">grad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af egenskaper, wärde m. m.:</text:span> g-us plures sunt societatis hominum; non iidem erunt necessitudinum g-us, qui temporum; g-us ætatis, oratorum, officiorum, peccatorum, sonorum; <text:soft-page-break/>magnitudine et quasi g-bus, non genere differre, C.; per g-us <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gradwis);</text:span> amoris, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Grădārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">går</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lugnt och jemnt, ej springer):</text:span> equus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(paßgångare),</text:span> Lucil. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> Cicero quoque noster, a quo Romana eloquentia exsiluit, g. fuit - : tardiloquum te esse jubeo, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Grădātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Steg för steg, gradwis; hwart i sin ordning:</text:span></text:span> pervenire aliquo; g. ascendere vocem utile est; g. ab humilioribus verbis ad superiora ascendere; quum minutatim et g. additur aut demitur aliquid, fit sorites; prima (officia) diis, secunda patriæ, tertia parentibus, deinceps g. reliquis debentur, C.; consulere (senatores) g., Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Grădātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Afsats; upphöjning i terraßform:</text:span></text:span> Vitr. <text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Stegring, climax</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i uttrycket:</text:span> C., Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Grădātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">trappwis l. i terraßform ställd:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Grădĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T4">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">försedd med trappgång:</text:span> templum, Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Grallæ</text:span>, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T4">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Styltor:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Grallātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T4">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. går på styltor:</text:span> Varr., Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Grassor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T4">Dep. Frequ.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wandra, ströfwa omkring,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ofta med bibet.: under owäsende och ofog:</text:span> palantes solæ libere, Pt.; juventus in Subura g-ns, L.; Cæsar (Nero in urbe noctu), T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Wandra, sträfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ett mål; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">gå till wäga, förfara;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ofta med bibetydelse af wåld l., fräckhet (angripa, rasa, ”drifwa sitt ofog l. spel”):</text:span> ubi animus ad gloriam virtutis viā g-atur, potens est,</text:p>
  </office:text>
 </office:body>
</office:document>